\id GEN
\h R…®ghenda
\toc1 Genesis
\toc2 R…®ghenda
\toc3 R…®gh
\mt1 R…®ghenda
\c 1
\s1 R…®ghendako moli
\p 
\v 1 E r…®ghendako moli, mbaŇčaniye Loi va i vakathaŇčgiya buruburu na yambaneke;
\v 2 yambaneke va kokowae moli na mava bigi regha inawe. Vambe njigh…® eŇčge vara ghawoke lagh…®ye na ina e momouwo t…®ne, na Loi Une vama ina e njigh…®ko vwatae, i rorololoŇčga.
\li1 
\v 3 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúManjamanjala u yomara e val…®vaŇčgake iyake,‚ÄĚ na e mbaŇčako iyako manjamanjala i yomara.
\v 4 Loi i thuwe manjamanjalako na i warari kaiwae; amba i vakatha manjamanjala na i meghaghath…® weya momouwo.
\v 5 Loi i rena manjamanjalako idae ‚Äúghararagh…®ye‚ÄĚ na momouwo ‚Äúgougou.‚ÄĚ I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča regha.
\li1 
\v 6 Iyako e ghereiye Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúLughawoghawo u yomara e mbaŇčake iyake, na i yomara, na i lighale mbwa yavoro na mbwa bodeke.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Me vakatha lughawoghawoko iyako na i mwanaghaghath…® mbwake bodeke na mbwako yavoroko. Na i yomara Ňčgoreiyeko.
\v 8 Loi i rena lughawoghawoko idae ‚Äúburuburu.‚ÄĚ I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča mbaŇčaiwoniye.
\li1 
\v 9 Iyako e ghereiye Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbwa bodeke u voruvavatha e val…®vaŇčga regha, na bwadabwada u yomara.‚ÄĚ Na i yomara Ňčgoreiyeko.
\v 10 Loi i rena thelau momoe ‚Äúyambane,‚ÄĚ na mbwa ve voruvavathama na reghama ‚Äúnjigh…®.‚ÄĚ Loi i thuwe iyako na i warariŇča.
\pi1 
\v 11 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúBigibigike wolagh…®ye, hu mbuthu e thelauko.‚ÄĚ Vavana th…® rau na e mbombounji e t…®nenjiko. Nana na umbwaumbwa tomethi ghanjiyamoyamo, na kaero Ňčgoreiye.
\v 12 E yambaneke kaero nana na umbwaumbwa th…® mbuthu na th…® rau tomethi uneunenji na ghanjiyamoyamo. Loi i thuwe iyako na i warariŇča.
\v 13 I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča mbaŇčatoniye.
\li1 
\v 14 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúManjamanjala hu yomara e buruburuko na i lighale ghararagh…®ye weya gougou, na th…® giya thuwai na theghathegha ghanjinono thaga kaiwanji, na mbaŇča na theghathegha regha na regha.
\v 15 Manjamanjalako thiyako th…® yaku e buruburuko na th…® giya manjamanjala e yambaneke.‚ÄĚ Na i yomara Ňčgoreiyeko.
\v 16 Loi i vakathaŇčgiya manjamanjala lagh…®lagh…®ye theghewo, regha varae i mbaroŇča ghararagh…®ye na regha manjala i mbaroŇča gougou, na vambe i vakathaŇčgiva gh…®tara.
\v 17 I bigirawevaoŇčgi e buruburuko na th…® giya manjamanjala e yambaneke.
\v 18 Thiye th…® mbaroŇča ghararagh…®ye na gougou na tembe th…® lighaleva ghararagh…®ye na gougou. Loi i thuwe iyako na i warariŇča.
\v 19 I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča mbaŇčavar…®niye.
\li1 
\v 20 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúNjigh…® na mbwa matemateko wolagh…®ye hu yomara e njigh…®ko t…®ne na e mbwako t…®ne, na maa hu yomara na hu yoyo e buruburuko na yambaneke ghanjilughawoghawo.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Loi i vakathaŇčgiya borogi lagh…®lagh…®ye na njigh…®ko matemate wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji na th…® nyiv…®nyiv…®, na maake wolagh…®ye. Na budakaiya va i thuwe Loi i warariŇčaŇčgi.
\v 22 Loi i giya ghanjimwaewo na i dage weŇčgi na th…® ghamb…® rake na th…® riyevanjara njigh…®ko t…®ne, na i dage weŇčgiya maako na tembe th…® vakathava Ňčgoreiye.
\v 23 I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča mbaŇčalimaniye. \fig MaaŇčgi na borogi|src="CO00600B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="1:21"\fig*
\li1 
\v 24 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúE yambaneke thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye hu yomara. Thetheghan mbwaeva na thetheghan th…® li e gharenji vwatae na mbe vavanava th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e thelau vwatae; thetheghan thiye mbwanjam…®Ňčgi inanji e njamnjam, tomethi ghanjiyamoyamo.‚ÄĚ Na i yomara Ňčgoreiye.
\v 25 Loi va i vakathaŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko thiyako na mbe tomethi ghanjiyamoyamo, thetheghan mbwaeva na mbwanjam…®Ňčgi na thiye th…® loŇčga e gharenji vwatae. Na Loi i thuwe iyako na i warariŇča.
\pi1 
\v 26 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúRa vakatha lolo e ghandayamoyamoke na Ňčgoreiya ghinda, na mbala i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya borogi e njigh…®ko na maa th…® yoyo, Ňčgoreiya thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye, mbwaeva na mbwanjam, na thetheghan th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e gharenji vwatae inanji e yambaneke.‚ÄĚ
\q1 
\v 27 Iya kaiwae Loi i vakatha lolo,
\q2 na loloko iyako i vakatha ghamberegha e ŇčgaliŇčgaliya;
\q2 i vakathaŇčgiya gh…®moru na wevo.
\pi1 
\v 28 Loi i giya ghanjimwaewo iŇča, ‚ÄúHu ghamb…® rake na hu riyevanjara yambaneke na hu mbaroŇča. Hu mbaroŇčaŇčgiya borogi e njigh…®ko, maa th…® yoyo na thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e thelauke vwatae.‚ÄĚ \fig Loi i vakatha lolo, i vakathaŇčgiya gh…®moru na wevo|src="co00604b.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="1:27"\fig*
\p 
\v 29 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče! Kaero ya vatomwe e ghemi the nana i mbuthu na ghan…®Ňčga na manjemanje th…® rau na e uneunenji e yambaneke ghemi kaiwami na lemi ghamba ghan…®Ňčga.
\v 30 Thetheghan, maa, na thetheghan th…® li e gharenji vwatae na the bigi e yawayawaliye kaero ya vatomwe weŇčgiya nana na umbwaumbwa ndamwandamwanji na thiye ghanji.‚ÄĚ Na i yomara Ňčgoreiye.
\pi1 
\v 31 Loi i thuweŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va i vakathaŇčgiko na i warariŇča. I gou na kaero i gh…®viyava, na iyako mbaŇča mbaŇčawonaniye.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako Loi kaero i vakathavaoŇčgiya buruburu na yambane na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e t…®nenjiko.
\li1 
\v 2 MbaŇča mbaŇčapir…®niye e t…®ne Loi i towowe kaiwae kaero i vakathavaoŇčgi vara le vakathako wolagh…®ye.
\v 3 Iya kaiwae Loi i vabobomaŇča mbaŇča mbaŇčapir…®niye kaiwae e mbaŇčako iyako t…®ne va i towowe ele kaiwoko iyava ele vakathako va i vakathaŇčgiko.
\s1 Adam na Ive utuutuninji
\p 
\v 4 Buruburu na yambaneke ghanjivakavakatha va Ňčgoreiye vara iyako.
\p MbaŇčaniye \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha yambane na buruburu
\v 5 ma vamba nana th…® mbuthu na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva karakarava, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* ma vamba i vakatha uye na i vatitiya thelauko, na mava lolo ina e yambaneke na i kaiwo e thelauko;
\v 6 ko iyemaeŇčge thelauko ghewo va i voroma e thelauko t…®ne na i vatitiya thelauko vwatae.
\v 7 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mbana thelauko na i monje lolo gh…®moruwe, ko amba i worawa ghae e mbothiye na i valawe ghandewendewekowe na e mbaŇčako iyako loloma kaero e yawayawaliye.
\p 
\v 8 \nd Giya Loi\nd* vama i vakatharawa uma regha e boimako, idae Iden, na i vaŇčgurawa loloma me vakathama e umako t…®ne.
\v 9 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha umbwaumbwake wolagh…®ye na th…® mbuthuwe, vavana ghanjithuwathuwa i thovuye na vavana uneunenji i thovuye ghan…®Ňčga kaiwae. E umako t…®ne yamoe moli, umbwaumbwa umboiwo th…® ndeghath…®we. Umbwara uneune i giya yawal…® memeghabananiye na umbwara uneune i giya ghareghare thovuye na thar…® kaiwanji.
\p 
\v 10 Walagh…®ta dura va i voru vagh…®liya na i vanjigh…®njigh…®ya umako iyako. I voruraŇčgi na i voru ghavwala na duvar…®.
\v 11 Dura idae Pison, i vorureŇča na i ru vanautuma idae Havila. Gol inawe.
\v 12 Gol e val…®vaŇčgako iyako i thovuye na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva bigi regha Ňčgoreiye meŇčghwi na butiye thovuye moli na var…®var…® ghanjiyamoyamo thovuye moli na modanji lagh…®ye.
\v 13 Mbwako ghavwalarava idae Gihon, i voru na i ru e vanautuma idae Kus.
\v 14 Walagh…®take ghavwalatonji idae Taigris; i voru reŇča e vanautuma Asiriya val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. Na mbwako ghavwalavar…®niye idae Yupreitis.
\p 
\v 15 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vaŇčgwa amalama na i vaŇčgurawe e uma Iden, i kaiwoŇča na i njimbukiki.
\v 16 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya amalama iŇča, ‚ÄúUmbwaumbwake wolagh…®ye e umake t…®ne i vatomwe, uneunenji mbema u ghan…®Ňčga eŇčge;
\v 17 ko iyemaeŇčge umbwana vara iya i giya ghareghare budakaiya i thovuye na budakaiya i thar…®, ne u ndeghana une, kaiwae thembaŇča ne u ghan, e mbaŇčako vara iyako ne u mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa i thovuye amalake mbe ghamberegha eŇčge i yaku. Mbema ya vakatha eŇčge gharathalavu thovuye regha val…®kaiwae i thalavu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero va i mbana thelau na i monjeŇčgiya thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye na maa th…® yoyo. I bigimenaŇčgi weya amalama na mbala i rena idaidanji. The ida amalako va i ren iyako thetheghan na maako idaidanji.
\v 20 Amalako kaero i rena thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye na maa idaidanji na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mbwanjam wolagh…®ye, ko iyemaeŇčge maa regha mun ina e t…®nenjiko gharathalavu thovuye inawe.
\p 
\v 21 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha amalako i ghenetena nuwa na e mbaŇčako iyako i woraŇčgiya amalako ŇčgaŇčgaiye regha na kaero i monjenjoghava e mbun…®maniyeko.
\v 22 Amba i monje wevo amalama e ŇčgaŇčgaiye iya me woraŇčgiyama na i vaŇčgumena weya amalama.
\p 
\v 23 Amalama iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúKo ambama ghino woyamoyamo vara iyake
\q2 Wok…®niye i mena e wak…®niŇčgu na mbun…®maniye i mena e mbun…®maniŇčgu.
\q1 Ya rena idae ‚Äėwevo‚Äô
\q2 kaiwae Ňčginauye na mbun…®maniye i mena weya gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ
\m 
\v 24 Iya kaiwae gh…®moru ne i iteteŇčgiya t…®nae na ramae na i tubwe weiye levo na th…® tabo na mbun…®ma regha.
\p 
\v 25 Mbe thenjighewoko vara th…® bukabuka, ko iyemaeŇčge mava th…® vemonjina wanaŇčgi.
\c 3
\s1 Lolo le dobu utuniye
\p 
\v 1 Thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye e t…®nenji, iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vakathaŇčgiko, mwata iye i thimba moli e kwan. I dage weya wevoma iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru Loi mendava i dageten e ghemi na mane hu ndeghan mun umbwa regha une e umake iyake t…®ne?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Wevoma i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema wo ghan…®Ňčga eŇčge vara iya umbwaumbwake wolagh…®ye e umake t…®ne uneunenji,
\v 3 ko iyemaeŇčge Loi mendava iŇča, ‚ÄėUmbwako iya vara i ndeghath…® yamoeko moli ne hu ndeghana une, o ne hu ndev…®ghath…®; ne iwaeŇčge hu mare.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Mwatama i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa emunjoru Ňčgoreiye; maane hu mare.
\v 5 Kaiwae Loi i ghareghare, mbaŇča ne hu ghana umbwako iyako une, marami ne i bowoutu na ne Ňčgoramiya amalagh…®niye, ne hu ghareghare thovuye na thar…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča wevoma i thuwe umbwako ghayamoyamo i thovuye moli na maraeko i loghelogheŇča uneko na val…®kaiwae ghan…®Ňčga na tembe i wova nuwae na i renuwaŇča nuwaiya i thimba, iya kaiwae i mbana vavana na i ghan. Te vambe i giyava vavana weya le gh…®moru na i ghan.
\v 7 MbaŇča kaero th…® ghan mbe thenjighewoko vara maranji i manjamanjala na th…® vemonjina wanaŇčgi. Th…® Ňčgiya umbwa idae fig ndamwandamwa na th…® yabo riwanjikowe.
\p 
\v 8 Vama i ghanjigh…®ye amba amalama na levo th…® loŇčwa \nd Giya Loi\nd* i loŇčga na laiye e umako t…®ne, iwaeŇčge th…® kubaro e umbwaumbwako r…®gher…®ghenji e umako t…®ne.
\v 9 Ko amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i kula weya amalama, ‚ÄúAŇčga inan?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa loŇčwa lain e umana t…®ne na ya mararuŇčge, kaiwae ya bukabuka.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThela me dage e ghen na iŇča u bukabuka. Kaero mo ghana umbwama mendava ya dageten…®ma e ghen une?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Amalama i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúWevoma mendava u vaŇčgugiyama e ghino, me giya umbwako une vavana e ghino na ya ghan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya wevoma iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mo vakatha iyake?‚ÄĚ
\p Wevoma i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMwata me utuyaroŇčgo na ya ghan.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Loi i woraweya ghanjimbaro
\p 
\v 14 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya mwatama iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae mo vakatha kamwath…®ke iyake, vuyowae tembene i njava e ghen:
\q1 Mbwaeva na mbwanjam…®ke wolagh…®ye e t…®nenji
\q2 mbe ghan…®mbereghana eŇčge vara ne u vaidiya vuyowoke iyake.
\q1 E mbaŇčake vara iyake na i ghaoko,
\q2 ne u li e gharen vwata na
\q2 ne u ghana thelau vughauye yawalin ghambaŇča i ri rogha.
\q1 
\v 15 Ne ya vakathaŇčge wein wevona
\q2 na hu veroghereiye wanaŇčga,
\q2 na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva orumburumbu na elagh…®niye
\q2 orumburumbuye weŇčgi mbaŇča muyaiko.
\q1 Nevole ghen u ghar…® orumburumbuye regha gheghe daŇčavwa,
\q2 ko iyemaeŇčge iye i tagaviya umbal…®n.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Weya wevoma, i dagewe iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúNe ya valagh…®yeŇča v…®r…® e ghen mbaŇča ne u ghamba Ňčgama,
\q2 na ne u ghataŇča v…®r…® mbaŇča ne u ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai.
\q1 Nuwan…®na mbene inawe vara len gh…®moru
\q2 ko iyemaeŇčge iye ne i mbaroŇčaŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 I dage weya Adam iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae mendava u loŇčweghath…®gha len wevona ghal…®Ňčae, na u ghana umbwako une iya va ya dageten…®ko e ghen, va yaŇčama, ‚ÄėNe u ndeghana uneko.‚Äô
\q1 Ne ya gura thelauke na le rauko i vuyowo kaiwae len vakathako kaiwae.
\q2 E mbaŇčake iyake na i ghaoko tembene u rovur…®ghegheva e kaiwo
\q2 mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ko amba hu ghan…®Ňčga.
\q1 
\v 18 E thelauke nana na nana e lenji kinkin ne th…® mbuthu,
\q2 na ne u ghan…®Ňčgiya umbwathaŇčar…®ke uneunenji.
\q1 
\v 19 Ghairo mbene i dobu eto i dobu e ghawo
\q2 amba ne u ghan valawe,
\q1 gheghada tene u njoghava e thelau,
\q1 kaiwae iyako va hu menawe
\q2 na tembene hu njogha na hu tabo na thelauva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Adam i rena levo idae Ive, kaiwae elagh…®niye ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji t…®nanji.\f + \fr 3:20 \ft Idake Ive gharumwaru ‚Äúe yawayawaliye‚ÄĚ.\f*
\p 
\v 21 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha kwama thetheghan e njimwanji na i vanjimboŇčgiya Adam na levowe.
\v 22 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbe ghambereghaeŇčge i renuwaŇča na iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya ghareghare, mbaŇčake thovuye na thar…® ghaghareghare kaero inawe Ňčgoreiya ghinda. Ne iwaeŇčge i vilawalawa na tembe ve wova umbwako iya yawal…®ko r…®ghe une na i ghan, ko amba i roghabana na maa i mare.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 Iya kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i variyeraŇčgiya e uma Iden t…®ne, i raŇčgi eto na i kaiwoŇča thelauko iyava i rikowe.
\v 24 MbaŇča i vakatha iyako na e ghereiye, amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i worawa buruburu nyaoniye regha idae ‚Äúserupim‚ÄĚ na ghalith…® maraeko i ravalaŇča na i vilama vagh…®liya val…®vaŇčgako iyako na i njimbukikiya umbwako iya yawal…®ko r…®ghe.
\c 4
\s1 Kein na Eibol utuninji
\p 
\v 1 Adam i ghenethaiya levo Ive, kaero i marabo na i ghamba nariye. Ive iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* le thalavu e ghino na ya vaidiya Ňčgama gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae i rena idae Kein.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft Idake Kein ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiye Hibru utu regha gharumwaru ‚Äúrawo‚ÄĚ.\f*
\v 2 Muyai amba te i ghamb…®va Kein ghaghae, idae Eibol.
\p Eibol iye va i mban…®Ňčgiya sip na Kein i kaiwo e uma.
\v 3 MbaŇča umako i tara, Kein i mbana umako une vavana na i bigimena na le mwaewo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge Eibol i mbana le sip vir…®viva vavana na ghanjitabo vond…®vond…®, na i vakatha le mwaewo. \nd Giya Loi\nd* i worawa Eibol na le mwaewo e ghamwae,
\v 5 ko Kein eŇčge na le mwaewo mava i warari kaiwae. Iya kaiwae Kein ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye moli na ghamwae i undu.
\p 
\v 6 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae gharen i gaith…®? Buda kaiwae nuwan i thar…®?
\v 7 ThoŇčgo u vakatha kamwath…® thovuye uŇča eŇčge maane ya wovatha len vakathana? Ko thoŇčgo ma u vakatha kamwath…® thovuye thar…® maiya vara evasiwan…®na; nuwaiya i ru e ghen, ko mbe ghen vara u njimbukikiŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Amba Kein i dage weya ghaghae Eibol iŇča, ‚ÄúWou, ra wa e njamnjam bwaga.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča inanji gheko, Kein i un…®gha ghaghae Eibol na i tagavamare. \fig Kein i un…®gha ghaghae Eibol na i tagavamare|src="CO00617B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="4:8"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vaito Kein iŇča, ‚ÄúGhagha Eibol aŇčga inae?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa ya ghareghare. Ghino maa Eibol gharanjimbunjimbu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMo vakatha budakai? Wo u vandeŇčeŇčgo! Ghagha Eibol mad…®bae i yawaru e thelauko t…®ne na ghal…®Ňčae kaero i voro e ghino.
\v 11 E mbaŇčake iyake vuyowo i vana e vwatan, na maa tene u kaiwova e thelauna iyana, kaiwae kaero i muna ghaghana mad…®bae, na raŇčaeŇčgeva me yoghatho na i wovoŇčgu mbaŇča mo un…®gh…®. Ne iwaeŇčge ya vambeleyathuŇčge e thivathivake iyake na ya vakatha ghanji ghakaiwo i vuyowo moli.
\v 12 MbaŇča ne u kaiwo e thelauna, maane ghan…®Ňčga i mbuthuwe. Ghen ma tene e ghambaghamban…®va. Yambaneke lagh…®ye gharandeloŇčga ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Kein i dage weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚ÄúVuyowoke iya u lith…®ke e ghino i lagh…®ye moli na i kivwalaŇčgo, maa val…®kaiwaŇčgu ne ya ghataŇčaghath…®.
\v 14 Noroke kaero u variyeyathuŇčgo na ma val…®kaiwangu ya thuweŇčge. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thelauke lagh…®ye gharaloŇčgatakwe, na thela ne i loŇčgavaidiŇčgo ne i tagavamareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMa val…®kaiwae. ThoŇčgo lolo regha i tagavamareŇčge ne modae i lagh…®ye kivwala mbaŇčapir…® na e vwataeova.‚ÄĚ Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha nono regha Kein e riwae na i giya vanuwov…®r…® weŇčgiya thavala ne th…® vaidi na thava th…® un…®gh…®.
\v 16 Kein i roiteta \nd Giya Loi\nd*, na i wa ve yaku e val…®vaŇčga regha idae Nod, Iden val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro.
\s1 Kein orumburumbuye
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča gheviyeva e ghereiye Kein i ghe na levo i marabo, i ghamba narinji regha idae Inok. Amba i vatada ghemba lagh…®ye regha na nariyeko le ghaida.
\v 18 Inok i ghamb…® weiye levo na narinji idae Irad, na Irad nariye Mehujael, Mehujael nariye Metuisela, na Metuisela nariye Lemeki.
\p 
\v 19 Lemeki le ovo theunyiwo, eunda idae Ada na eunda idae Jila.
\v 20 Ada nariye Jabal.
\v 21 Amalagh…®niye va i yakukai vara e Ňčgolo th…® vakatha e thetheghan njimwanji na th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya sip. Ghaghae nasiyeniye va idae Jubol, iye va i mwadiwokai vara hap na igo.
\v 22 Jila va i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru idae, Tubal-Kein, iye va i ŇčambuŇčambu brons na aiyan na i vakathaŇčgiya kaiwo bigibiginiye. Tubal-Kein louye Naama.
\p 
\v 23 Lemeki i dage weŇčgiya le ovo iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúAda na Jila, wo hu vandeŇčeŇčgo;
\q2 Lemeki le ovo wo hu vandeŇče lo utuke.
\q1 Kaero ma tagavamare amala regha kaiwae me vawonamboyaoŇča riwaŇčgu,
\q2 giya theghathegha kaiwae me vawonamboyoŇčaŇčgo.
\q1 ThoŇčgo Loi i lith…® weya Kein gharatagavamare mbaŇčapir…®,
\q2 
\v 24 thoŇčgo lolo regha i munje ne i tagavamareŇčgo, ne ya lith…®we mbaŇčaepir…® na mbaŇčapir…® na e vwataeva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Adam mbowo i ghenava weiye levo, i marabo na i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru na Ive i rena idae Set, iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi i vatomwe e ghino na mbowo ya vaidiva Ňčgama regha Eibol ghath…®gh…®th…®gh…®, kaiwae Kein kaero va i tagavamare.‚ÄĚ
\v 26 Set vambe e nanariyeva, na va i rena idae Inos.
\p Va e mbaŇčako iyako na i ghaoko, ghar…®ghar…® th…® kururukai vara weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* th…®Ňča ‚ÄúWo tarawe e ghen, Yawe.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 4:26 \ft Idake Yawe gharumwaru ‚ÄúGiya Loi‚ÄĚ. Idake iyake Loi idae moli.\f*
\c 5
\s1 Adam orumburumbuye
\p 
\v 1 Iyake Adam orumburumbuye ghanjiriuriu. MbaŇča Loi i vakatha lolo, va i vakatha tembe Ňčgoreiyeva amalagh…®niyeko ghayamoyamo.
\v 2 I vakathaŇčgi, gh…®moru na wevo, i mwaewo weŇčgi na i giya idanji ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®.‚ÄĚ
\li1 
\v 3 MbaŇča Adam ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® na hweto (130), na mbowo th…® ghamb…®va narinji regha. Ghayamoyamo mbe Ňčgora vara amalagh…®niye, na i rena idae Set.
\v 4 MbaŇča Set i vir…® na e ghereiye, Adam yawaliye molao, i yaku theghathegha hoseriyewa (800). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 5 Adam va i yaku vara theghathegha hoseriyesiwo na hweto (930), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 6 MbaŇča Set ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® na umbolima (105) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Inos.
\v 7 MbaŇča Inos i vir…® na e ghereiye, Set yawaliye vambe molaova, i yaku theghathegha hoseriyewa na umbopir…® (807). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 8 Set va i yaku vara theghathegha hoseriyesiwo na hoyaworo na umboiwo (912), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 9 MbaŇča Inos ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwesiwo (90) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Kenan.
\v 10 MbaŇča Kenan i vir…® na e ghereiye, Inos yawaliye vambe molaova, i yaku theghathegha hoseriyewa na hoyaworo na umbolima (815). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 11 Inos va i yaku vara theghathegha hoseriyesiwo na umbolima (905) ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 12 MbaŇča Kenan ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwepir…® (70) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Mahalalel.
\v 13 MbaŇča Mahalalel i vir…® na e ghereiye, Kenan yawaliye vambe molaova, i yaku theghathegha hweseriyewa na hwevar…® (840). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 14 Kenan va i yaku vara theghathegha hweseriyesiwo na hoyaworo (910) ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 15 MbaŇča Mahalalel ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwewona na umbolima (65) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Jered.
\v 16 MbaŇča Jered i vir…® na e ghereiye, Mahalalel yawaliye vambe molaova, i yaku theghathegha hweseriyewa na hweto (830). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 17 Mahalalel va i yaku vara theghathegha hweseriyewa na hwesiwo na umbolima (895), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 18 MbaŇča Jered ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® na hwewona na umboiwo (162) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Inok.
\v 19 MbaŇča Inok i vir…® na e ghereiye, Jered yawaliye vambe molaova, i yaku theghathegha hweseriyewa (800). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 20 Jered va i yaku vara theghathegha hweseriyesiwo na hwewona na umboiwo (962), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 21 MbaŇča Inok ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwewona na umbolima (65) ambama th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Metuisela.
\v 22 MbaŇča Metuisela i vir…® na e ghereiye Inok i yaku na ghamwae vanaora weiye Loi theghathegha hweseriyeto (300) e t…®ne na i ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 23 Va i yaku na yawaliye le molamolao Ňčgoreiya theghathegha hweseriyeto hwewona na umbolima (365).
\v 24 Inok i yaku na ghamwae vanaora weiye Loi ghaghad…® vambema i roghawe eŇčge kaiwae Loi vama i vaŇčgu.
\li1 
\v 25 MbaŇča Metuisela ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® hwewa na umbopir…® (187) ambama th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, idae Lemeki.
\v 26 MbaŇča Lemeki i vir…® na e ghereiye Metuisela i yaku mbaŇča molao, theghathegha hweseriyepir…® hwewa na umboiwo (782). E lughawoghawoko iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 27 Metuisela va i yaku vara theghathegha hweseriyesiwo hwewona na umbosiwo (969), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 28 MbaŇča Lemeki ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® hwewa na umboiwo (182) th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru,
\v 29 na iŇča, ‚ÄúE thelauke vara iya \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i gurake, Ňčgamake iyake ne i vatowoŇčainda e vuyowoke t…®ne,‚ÄĚ iya kaiwae i rena idae Nowa.\f + \fr 5:29 \ft Idake iyake Nowa ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiye utu regha i mena Hibru ghal…®Ňčanji gharumwaru ‚ÄúvatowoŇča‚ÄĚ.\f*
\v 30 Lemeki vambowo i yakuva theghathegha hweseriyelima hwesiwo na umbolima (595). E lughawoghawo iyako vambe th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\v 31 Lemeki va i yaku vara theghathegha hweseriyepir…® hwepir…® na umbopir…® (777), ko amba i mare eŇčge.
\li1 
\v 32 Nowa vama ghatheghathegha hoseriyelima (500) iko, ko amba th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi le ŇčgaŇčga thenjigheto, mbe gh…®mogh…®moruŇčgi eŇčge. Idaidanji Sem, Ham na Japet.
\c 6
\s1 Ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha thar…® lagh…®ye
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…® kaero lemoyo e yambaneke na th…® yala, th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiya wanakau lemoyo,
\v 2 buruburu nyaoniyeŇčgi th…® thuwe ghanjiyamoyamoko th…® thovuye moli, th…® numweŇčgi na th…® tuthigiya vavana na th…® vaŇčguŇčgi.
\v 3 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚ÄúYawaliŇčguke iyava ya valaweke weŇčgi mane ya vatomwe weŇčgi na lenji yaku molao kaiwae thiye mbun…®ma na madibe. E mbaŇčake iyake na i ghaoko yawalinji le molamolao mane i kivwala theghathegha hothaŇčar…® na hoiwo (120).‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 E mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako Nepilim ghar…®ghar…®niye (Ňčgoreiye Tuu na Var…®) va inanji e yambaneke. Yambaneke wanakauniye vambe th…® ghamb…®va weinjiyaŇčgiya buruburu nyaoniyeŇčgi na lenji gamagai th…® tabo na gh…®mbagh…®mbalaŇčgi, thiye Nepilim ghar…®ghar…®niye. Thiye va th…® vur…®gheghe na gaith…® mara mbouyeŇčgi.
\p 
\v 5 MbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* i thuwe ghar…®ghar…® lenji vakatha na lenji renuwaŇča e yambaneke mbema thar…® eŇčge vara mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye,
\v 6 i vakatha nuwae i thar…® na i renuwaŇča njogha kaiwae va i vakathaŇčgi na i bigiraweŇčgi e yambaneke.
\v 7 Iya kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚ÄúMbemane ya mukuwoŇčgi vara ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye iyava ya vakatha na ya bigiraweŇčgi e yambaneke na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thetheghan na maaŇčgi. Ne ya vakatha iyake kaiwae ya renuwaŇča njogha va ya vakathaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i warari Nowa ghathanavu kaiwae na i worawe e ghamwae.
\s1 Nowa na yambane i thotho
\p 
\v 9-10 Riuriuke iyake Nowa utuutuniye. Nowa le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru mbe thenjigheto eŇčge, Sem, Ham na Jepet. Nowa maava i vakatha mun thar…® na iye maa e ghawonjowe mun weya lolo regha. Va i yaku na ghamwae vanaora weiye Loi.
\p 
\v 11 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® lenji vakatha maava i thovuye Loi e marae. Vambema ghanjikaiwo eŇčge gaith…® na thar…® ghavakatha.
\v 12 Loi i thuwe yambaneke mbema thar…® eŇčge na ghar…®ghar…® yawalinji na lenji vakatha mbe Ňčgoreiye eŇčge.
\v 13 Iya kaiwae Loi i dage weya Nowa iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakowana yambaneke lagh…®ye. Ne ya mukuwo ghar…®ghar…®niye na matemate, kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® ghanjithanavu na lenji vakatha raraithar…® i riyevanjara. Emunjoru ne ya vakowana moli.
\v 14 Iyake kaiwae u vatada waŇčga regha kaiwan. U kanjiya umbwa thovuye na u vatad…®we. U vakatha woluwoluŇčgi e t…®ne na u ghabad…® e t…®ne na eto.
\v 15 Ne u vatad na Ňčgoreiya iyake: WaŇčgako le molamolao 150 mita, le magamagaga 25 mita na le yavoyavoro 15 mita.
\v 16 U vakatha waŇčgako vwatae ghaŇčgolo le didivoro hap mita. U vakatha mbwaŇčaŇčgila e ghadidiye na u vakatha yavweto, bode yamoe na yavoro.
\v 17 Wo u vandeŇče! Ne ya vakatha uye lagh…®ye i nja na yambane i thotho na i gaboŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji. Bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yambane ne thiya marevao.
\v 18 Ko ghino ne ya vakatha dagerawe regha weiŇčgu ghen. Ghen na len wevo, le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ovo ne weinaŇčgi hu rakatha e waŇčgana.
\v 19 Ne u bigi ruwoŇčgi e waŇčgake thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye, theghewo iya, gh…®moru na wevo; mbala th…® yaku na mbe e yawayawalinji.
\v 20 MaaŇčgike wolagh…®ye tomethi na tomethi, na thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye tomethi na tomethi, na thiye th…® loŇčgaloŇčga na th…® li e thelau vwatae tomethi na tomethi, theghewo iya ne th…® rakamena e ghen na weinaŇčgi e waŇčgana e yawayawalinji.
\v 21 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva u mbana ghan…®Ňčga thaŇčar…®ke, ghen na thiye kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Nowa i vakathaŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Loi me dagekowe. \fig Nowa i vakatha waŇčgako lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Loi me dagekowe|src="CO00625B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="6:22"\fig*
\c 7
\s1 Yambaneke i thotho
\p 
\v 1 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Nowa iŇča, ‚ÄúU tha e waŇčga, ghen, len wevo na len ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ovo, kaiwae kaero ya thuwe ghen vara ghan…®mbereghana u thovuye moli thake iyake e t…®nenji.
\v 2 U mban…®Ňčgiya thetheghan wevo na gh…®moru thenjighepir…® iya, iya va ya dage weŇčga ne ya wovatha vowo kaiwae. U mban…®Ňčgiya thetheghan yamoyamo wevo na gh…®moru, iya maa val…®kaiwae vowo, kaiwae th…® mbigh…®.
\v 3 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva maaŇčgi, wevo na gh…®moru thenjighepir…® iya. U vakatha Ňčgoreiyake mbala thetheghan na maa yamoyamo regha na regha mbe e yawayawalinji na tembe th…® rothirakava e yambaneke.
\v 4 MbaŇča mbaŇčapir…® e t…®ne ne ya variye uye na i nja e yambaneke. Ne i uyevoreŇča mbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® na gougouyevar…® e t…®nenji. Iyake kaiwae lo renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye bigibigike wolagh…®ye va ya vakathaŇčgi ne ya mukuwoŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Nowa i vakatha Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* i utugiyakowe.
\p 
\v 6 Nowa ghatheghathegha vama i wo hweseriyewona (600) ambama iya yambaneke i thotho eŇčge.
\v 7 Nowa na levo na le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ovo th…® tha e waŇčgako na mbala maa thothoko i gaboŇčgi.
\v 8 Thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye, th…® mbigh…® na maa th…® mbigh…® na tomethi yamoyamo, wevo na gh…®moru,
\v 9 th…® rakatha e waŇčgama weinji Nowa Ňčgoreiya Loi va i dagemawe.
\v 10 MbaŇča theghepir…® e ghereiye thothoma kaero i voro. \fig Thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye th…® rakatha e waŇčga|src="CO00622B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="7:8-9"\fig*
\p 
\v 11 MbaŇča Nowa ghatheghathegha hweseriyewona, manjala umboiwoniye ghambaŇča theyaworo na theghepir…®ninji e t…®ne, mbwake wolagh…®ye r…®ghenji e yambaneke raberabe thiya mavuvao na mbwa e buruburuko tembe Ňčgoreiyeva,
\v 12 ko amba uye i nja e yambaneke mbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® na gougouyevar…®.
\v 13 E mbaŇčako iyako vara e t…®ne Nowa na levo weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga, Sem, Ham na Jepet na lenji ovo th…® tha e waŇčgama.
\v 14 WeinjiyaŇčgi th…® rakatha e waŇčgama thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye, tomethi mbe ghanjiyamoyamo, mbwanjam na mbwaeva, thetheghan th…® loŇčga e gharenji vwata na maaŇčgi mbe Ňčgoreiyeva na bigibigi e vinevineinji.
\v 15 Thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji th…® rakamena weya Nowa, theghewo iya, wevo na gh…®moru na th…® rakatha e waŇčgama.
\v 16 Thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji, gh…®moru na wevo Nowa va i vamboromboroŇča Ňčgoreiya Loi le renuwaŇča, Nowa i rereghamba vara. MbaŇča i ru e waŇčgama amba Giya i kigh…® eŇčge waŇčgako ghambwaŇčaŇčgila.
\p 
\v 17 Thothoma kaero i thothovoreŇča mbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® na kaero i dumwaga na i vakatha waŇčgako i ghagha.
\v 18 Mbwako ma i vorovorowo eŇčge na kaero i ghagha loloŇčga e vwatae.
\v 19 Mbwako kaero ina yavoro moli na kaero i wovululuŇčgiya ououko wolagh…®ye e yambaneke.
\v 20 Vambema le didivoro eŇčge tembema i wo eŇčge mita theghepir…® le ghenevoro e ououko molamolao vwatanji.
\v 21 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji na inanji e yambaneke thiya marevaoma, thetheghan na ghar…®ghar…®.
\v 22 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye iya th…® liliya yawalinji e yambaneke thiya marevao.
\v 23 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i mukuwoŇčgi ‚ÄĒ ghar…®ghar…®, thetheghan th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e yambaneke vwatae na ma th…® yoyo, thiya marevao. Vama Nowa eŇčge na thavala weiyaŇčgi e waŇčgako t…®ne vambe nanjiwe.
\p 
\v 24 Thothoko va i voro na ghaghad…®ko va i wo vara mbaŇča mbaŇčathaŇčar…® na mbaŇčaelima (150). \fig Mbwako ma i vorovorowo eŇčge na kaero i ghagha loloŇčga e vwatae|src="CO00629B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="7:18"\fig*
\c 8
\s1 Thotho gheghad
\p 
\v 1 Loi vambe i renuwaŇčakiki vara Nowa na thetheghan…®ma wolagh…®ye, mbwanjam na mbwaeva, weiyaŇčgi e waŇčgako t…®ne. IwaeŇčge i variya ndewendewe na i rowa, ko ambama thothoma i njoghanjogha.
\v 2 Mbwake wolagh…®ye r…®ghenji e yambaneke raberabe na mbwa e buruburu kaero th…® vorutowo na uye tembe i uye towova
\v 3 na thothoko kaero i njoghanjogha na tembe i wova mbaŇča mbaŇčathaŇčar…® na mbaŇčaelima,
\v 4 na manjala umbopir…® ghe mbaŇča mbaŇčayaworo na mbaŇčapir…® e t…®ne, waŇčgama i rovala e ouou idanji Ararat regha vwatae.
\v 5 Mbwama mbema le didinja eŇčge gheghada manjala hoyaworoninji e t…®ne. MbaŇča i viva e t…®ne ouou vwatavwatanji kaero th…® yomara.
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča mbaŇčaevar…® e ghereiye Nowa i vugha dedele va i vakatha e waŇčgako
\v 7 na i variye waluwo manda. Vambema i yoyololoŇčga eŇčge gheghada mbwama i ma moli.
\v 8 Amba i variye bunebune manda na i wa ve thuwe thoŇčgo kaero thelauko i mwa.
\v 9 Ko kaiwae mbwa vamba i wovululu vara thelauko, bunebunema maava i ndevaidi mun le ghamba yovaro, iya kaiwae vama i yonjoghava weya Nowa e waŇčgako. I tagavamomoya n…®mae, i wo bunebunema na i woruwo e waŇčgako t…®ne.
\v 10 Nowa i roroghagha mbaŇča theghepir…® e ghereiye na mbowo i variyeva bunebunema.
\v 11 MbaŇča kaero yegh…®yegh…®yenja bunebunema i livutha oliv…® ndamwae amba i tagavwara eŇčge. Nowa i ghareghare thelau kaero i mwa.
\v 12 Mbowo i roroghaghava mbaŇča theghepir…® e ghereiye, na mbowo i variyeva bunebunema, ko iyemaeŇčge ande vama i yonjogha weya Nowa.
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča Nowa ghatheghathegha kaero i wo hweseriyewona na umbwara (601), mbaŇčaniye manjala i viva ghe mbaŇčako regha Nowa i rakayathu waŇčgako vwatae, na i thuwe i mena i ghawoko, na iŇča, ‚ÄúKo thelau kaero i mwa iyako!‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Va manjala umboiwoninji ghe mbaŇča theiwo na theghepir…® e t…®ne yambaneke vambema i mwavao vara.
\p 
\v 15 Amba Loi i dage weya Nowa iŇča,
\v 16 ‚ÄúKo ghen na len wevo na le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ovo, hu rakaraŇčgima e waŇčgana t…®ne.
\v 17 Hu bigi raŇčgiyaŇčgima thetheghan…®na wolagh…®ye na maaŇčgina, mbalama th…® ghamb…®va togha na th…® riyevanjara yambaneke lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Kaero Nowa i raŇčgi e waŇčgama weiyaŇčgiya levo, le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ovo.
\v 19 ThetheghaŇčgima wolagh…®ye na maaŇčgima th…® rakaraŇčgi e waŇčgama, thegheiwo iya na tomethi ghanjiyamoyamo. Thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye iya th…® loŇčgaloŇčga e yambaneke vwatae na maake wolagh…®ye ‚ÄĒ tomethi e lenji wabwi na e ghanjiyamoyamoko th…® rakarakaraŇčgi.
\s1 Nowa le vowo
\p 
\v 20 Amba Nowa i vatada ghamba vowo \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae. I mban…®Ňčgiya thetheghan na maa regha iya e wabwi regha na regha e t…®nenji, iya lenji kururu i vatomwe th…® thovuye, na i ŇčambuŇčgi e ghamba vowoko.
\v 21 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i warari butiyeko thovuye kaiwae na e ghareko iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa tene mbaŇča reghava ya vakowana yambaneke lolo le thar…® kaiwae. Ya ghareghare lolo le renuwaŇča i thar…® ghe mbaŇča Ňčgama na i ghaoko. Ma tene mbaŇča reghava ya vakowanaŇčgiya thetheghan e yawayawalinji Ňčgoreiya mendava ya vakathako. \fig Nowa i vakatha ghamba vowo weya Giya Loi|src="CO00635B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="8:20"\fig*
\q1 
\v 22 Yambaneke mbene Ňčgora vara iyake na i ghaoko,
\q1 mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne ghan…®Ňčga ghakabu ghe mbaŇča na ghalolo ghe mbaŇča,
\q1 ne njigh…®njigh…® ghe mbaŇča na meme ghe mbaŇča,
\q1 ne varae i ndeghath…® na uye ghe mbaŇča
\q1 na ghararagh…®ye na gougou.
\q1 Thiyake mane mbaŇča regha th…®ko.‚ÄĚ
\c 9
\s1 Loi le dagerawe weya Nowa
\p 
\v 1 Loi i mwaewo weya Nowa na le ŇčgaŇčga na iŇča, ‚ÄúHu ghamb…® na lemi ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ŇčgaŇčgaova na th…® riyevanjara yambaneke.
\v 2 Thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye, maa th…® yoyo na borogi e njigh…®ko, na bigibigike wolagh…®ye th…® lili e gharenji e thelau vwatae ne th…® mararuŇčga. Kaero ya bigirawe e n…®mami ghare.
\v 3 Bigibigike wolagh…®ye th…® nyiv…®nyiv…® na e yawayawalinji ya vatomwe weŇčga ghami, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva umbwaumbwa na nana ndamwanji vwivwivu, kaero ya vatomwevao weŇčga na ghami.
\p 
\v 4 ‚ÄúKo iyemaeŇčge ne hu ndeghana thetheghan mbun…®maniye thoŇčgo mad…®bae mbe ina e t…®neko kaiwae madibe i giya yawal…®.
\v 5 Kaiwae madibe iye i vakatha bigi regha e yawayawaliye. Iya kaiwae thoŇčgo thela i vakowana lolo yawaliye na i mare, vuyowae loloko iyako wone i mare, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thetheghan i vakowana lolo yawaliye na i mare, thetheghan…®ko iyako wone i mare.
\q1 
\v 6 Kaiwae va ya vakatha lolo mbe
\q2 ghino vara e ŇčgaliŇčgaliyaŇčgu,
\q1 iya kaiwae thoŇčgo lolo i un…®gha lolo regha
\q2 loloko iyako tembene th…® un…®gh…®va.
\m 
\v 7 Ko Nowa ghen na len ŇčgaŇčga, hu ghamb…®raka mbala orumburumbumi th…® yala na th…® riyevanjara yambaneke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Loi i dage weŇčgiya Nowa na le ŇčgaŇčga iŇča,
\v 9 ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake ya vakatha lo dagerawe e ghemi na weŇčgiya orumburumbu mbaŇča muyaiko,
\v 10 na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji, maake wolagh…®ye na thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye ‚ÄĒ mbema bigibigike wolagh…®ye vara va hu rakaraŇčgi e waŇčgana weinaŇčgi.
\v 11 E utuutuŇčgike thiyake ya vakatha lo dagerawe e ghemi: Ya dagerawe maa tene mbaŇča reghava ya vakatha yambaneke i thotho na i vakowana yawal; maa tene mbaŇča reghava thotho i vakowana yambaneke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúDageraweke iya ma vakatha e ghandalughawoghawoke na thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji, tha na tha kaiwanji ghanono iyake,
\v 13 ya worawa bwawo e Ňčgal…®l…®ko na iyake i tabo na nono lo dageraweke ghino na yambaneke ghandalughawoghawo.
\v 14 MbaŇča ya vakatha uye ghaŇčgal…®l…® na th…® yomara e buruburuko na bwawo i thowo,
\v 15 ne i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgo lo dageraweko weiŇčgu ghemi na thetheghan…®ke wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji na tomethi wabwi e ghandalughawoghawoke. Maa tene mbaŇča reghava mbwa th…® thotho na th…® vakowana yawal.
\v 16 Nevole the mbaŇča ya thuwe bwawoko i thowo e Ňčgal…®l…®ko, ne ya renuwaŇčakikiya dageraweko iya memeghabananiyeko ghino na bigibigike wolagh…®ye e yawayawalinji na tomethi wabwi e yambaneke e ghandalughawoghawo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Loi i dage weya Nowa iŇča, ‚ÄúDageraweke iya ma vakathake ghino na yawal e yambane ghandalughawoghawo iya ghanono iyake.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Nowa na le ŇčgaŇčga
\p 
\v 18 Nowa na le ŇčgaŇčga va i raŇčgi weiyaŇčgi e waŇčgako t…®ne thiyake: Sem, Ham na Jepet. (Ham nariya Keinan.)
\v 19 Nowa le ŇčgaŇčgake thenjighetoke thiyake iya orumburumbunji vara ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke.
\p 
\v 20 Nowa, iye va rakakaiwo e uma, va i kabukai vara waen.
\v 21 MbaŇča i muna waen, i wovaghawa umbaliye, i bigiyatho ghakwama na i ghena bukabuka ele yoŇčathowathowa t…®ne.
\v 22 MbaŇča Ham, Keinan ramae, i thuwe ramae i ghena bukabuka, i njogha eto na ve utugiya weŇčgiya oghaghaema thenjighewoma.
\v 23 Amba Sem na Jepet th…® liya kwama ghayaboyabo, th…® lirawe e vwatanji, th…® loŇčgaloŇčgaŇča ghereinji na th…® ru, ko amba th…® liyabo ramanji. Ghamwanji va i njogha e ghereinji na mbala thava th…® thuwe i ghenebukako.
\p 
\v 24 MbaŇča Nowa i thuweiru na le renuwaŇča i rumwaru, i loŇčwevaidiya budakai nariye me wo vala uyewe le vakathawe,
\v 25 iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúVuyowo ne i mena weya Keinan!
\q1 Iye nevole Sem na Jepet lenji rakakaiwobwagaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Mbowo i dageva,
\q1 ‚ÄúTarawa i voro weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iye Sem le Loi!
\q2 Keinan nevole Sem le rakakaiwobwagaŇčgi.
\q1 
\v 27 Loi nevole i vakatha Jepet na le ghamba mbaro i lagh…®ye!
\q2 Orumburumbuye nevole th…® yaku na regha weinji Sem le wabwi!
\q2 Keinan iye nevole Jepet le rakakaiwobwagaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Thothoko e ghereiye Nowa mbowo i yakuva theghathegha hweseriyeto na hwelima (350).
\v 29 Gha theghathegha vama i wo hweseriyesiwo na hwelima (950) amba i mare.
\c 10
\s1 Nowa le ŇčgamaŇčgama na orumburumbunjiŇčgi
\p 
\v 1 Riuriuke iyake Nowa le ŇčgaŇčga ‚ÄĒ Sem, Ham na Jepet orumburumbunji utuutuninji. Thenjighetoke iyake va th…® ghamb…® na lenji ŇčgamaŇčgama thothoko e ghereiye.
\s1 Jepet orumburumbuyeŇčgi
\li1 
\v 2 Jepet le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Goma, Magog, Madai, Javan, Tubal, Mesek na Tiras.
\li1 
\v 3 Goma le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 As…®kenas, Ripat na Togama.
\li1 
\v 4 Javan le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Ilaisa, Tasis, Kiti na Roda.
\v 5 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake orumburumbunji thiya yaku e njigh…® ghadidiye na e raurauŇčgi Meditareiniyan Njigh…® ele val…®vaŇčga. (Thiyake Jepet orumburumbuyeŇčgi.) Tomethi u na u na vanautumaŇčgi thiya yaku, na wabwi na wabwi mbe ghal…®Ňčanji.
\s1 Ham orumburumbuyeŇčgi
\li1 
\v 6 Ham le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Kus, Ijipt, Put, na Keinan.
\li1 
\v 7 Kus le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Siba, Havila, Sabta, Rama na Sabteka.
\li1 Rama le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Siba na Didan.
\p 
\v 8 Ko Kus nariye regha Nimrod. Iye va lolo vur…®vur…®ghegheniye na ragagaith…® e yambaneke.
\v 9 Kaiwae Loi va i thalavu, iye va rawowoidi lagh…®ye na thovuye moli, iya kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® mbaŇča th…® utuŇča lolo regha, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúIye Ňčgoreiya Nimrod rawowoidi lagh…®ye na thovuye moli iye Loi va i thalavu.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Va i viva le ghamba mbaro Babilon, Uruk, Akad na Kalne inanji Babiloniya e t…®ne.
\v 11 I ri e val…®vaŇčgako iyako amba i wa Asiriya na ve vatad…®Ňčgiya ghembaghembake thiyake: Ninive, Rehobot Ir…®, Kala
\v 12 na Risen, ina Ninive na Kala e ghanjilughawoghawo, iye ghemba lagh…®ye regha.
\li1 
\v 13 Ijipt orumburumbuye iya ghar…®ghar…®niye thiya yaku e ghembaghembake thiyake: Lud, Anam, Lehab, Nep…®tu,
\v 14 Pat…®rus, Kaslu na Kurit. Pilistiya ghar…®ghar…®niye thiye th…® rimbun Kaslu.
\li1 
\v 15 Keinan nariye vir…® viva Saidon na Hiti i vir…® reghamba.
\v 16 Keinan vambe orumburumbuyeŇčgiva ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgike thiyake: Jebusi, Amori, Gigasi,
\v 17 Hivi, Aki, Saini,
\v 18 Aved, Jemari na Hamati.
\p Va muyai amba Keinan ghe u th…® meila
\v 19 na lenji val…®vaŇčga, i ri Saidon ve wo Gera ele val…®vaŇčga na ve wo Gaja, e boimako i wa Sodom, Gomora, Adma na Seboyim na gheghad Lasa.
\p 
\v 20 Ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgike thiyake Ham orumburumbuyeŇčgi. UuŇčgike thiyeke vambe e lenji ghambayaku na mbe tomethi ghal…®Ňčanji.
\s1 Sem orumburumbuyeŇčgi
\p 
\v 21 Sem iye ghaghae lagh…®yeninji Jepet. Sem orumburumbuyeŇčgiya Eba ghar…®ghar…®niyeŇčgi.
\li1 
\v 22 Sem le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Ilam, Asur, Apaksad, Lud na Aram.
\li1 
\v 23 Aram orumburumbuyeŇčgiya:
\li2 Us, Hul, Gethe na Mes.
\li1 
\v 24 Apaksad nariya Sila na Sila nariya Iba.
\li1 
\v 25 Iba le ŇčgamaŇčgama thenjighewo:
\li2 Regha idae Peleg, kaiwae amalagh…®niye va ghe mbaŇča e t…®ne yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® meghaghath…® na th…® yala; na nariye theghewoniye idae Joktan.
\li1 
\v 26 Joktan orumburumbuyeŇčgiya:
\li2 Almoded, Selep, Hesamavet, Jera,
\v 27 Hadoram, Usal, Dikla,
\v 28 Obal, Abimael, Siba,
\v 29 Opi, Havila, na Jobab. Thiyake th…® rimbun weya Joktan.
\m 
\v 30 Ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgike thiyake va veth…® yayaku Mesa na Sepa e ghanjilughawoghawo, inanji e boimako na val…®vaŇčgako iyako mbe bobokulu eŇčge.
\p 
\v 31 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake Sem orumburumbuyeŇčgi. Th…® yaku tomethi wabwi na u, na tomethi mbe lenji val…®vaŇčga na ghal…®Ňčanji.
\p 
\v 32 Ghar…®ghar…®Ňčgike vara thiyake Nowa mbe orumburumbuyeŇčgi eŇčge, tomethi mbe ghambanji, tomethi mbe lenji wabwi na uu. Thothoko va e ghereiye vanautumake wolagh…®ye e yambaneke va th…® rimbun weŇčgi vara Nowa le ŇčgaŇčga.
\c 11
\s1 Ňägoloko molao moli ina Babel
\p 
\v 1 Va e mbaŇčako iyako yambaneke lagh…®ye ghal…®ghal…®Ňčaniye va regha na lenji utuutu ghe loŇčwaloŇčwa regha.
\v 2 MbaŇča th…® raka na i vorowoko veth…® vaidiya malamo regha Babiloniya e t…®ne na th…® vatada ghambanjiwe.
\p 
\v 3 Kaero th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo hu rakamena! Ra vakathaŇčgiya brik na ra ŇčambuŇčgi na th…® vur…®gheghe.‚ÄĚ Th…® mbana brik (thelau) na th…® vatavatad…®we na th…® monje valaweŇčgi na i vur…®gheghe.
\v 4 Amba th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake ra vatada ghemba lagh…®ye na Ňčgolo regha i loŇčga na i voro na molao, mbala ve wo buruburuko, mbala idanda ne i lagh…®ye. Ňägoloke iyake i vakathainda thava ra meila e yambaneke lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i njama na i thuwe ghembako lagh…®ye na Ňčgoloko molao th…® vatavatad…®ko.
\v 6 \nd Giya Loi\nd* iŇča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke thiyake kaero thiya mevathavatha na regha na ghal…®Ňčanji regha. Kaero th…® worawa lenji vakathako iyako r…®ghe. Nevole val…®kaiwanji budakaiya nuwanjiya th…® vakatha.
\v 7 Ra nja na vara vauneuneŇčaŇčgi na tomethi mbe ghal…®Ňčanji, mbala maa th…® veloŇčwa ghal…®Ňčanjiko gharumwaru.‚ÄĚ
\v 8 Iya kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakathaŇčgi na th…® meila e yambaneke lagh…®ye na th…® viyatho ghembama lagh…®ye ghavatavatad.
\v 9 Iya kaiwae ghembako lagh…®ye iyako idae Babel, kaiwae gheko \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vauneuneŇča ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye e yambaneke na gheko i vakathaŇčgi na th…® meila e yambaneke lagh…®ye. \fig Giya Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúRa nja na vara vauneuneŇčaŇčgi na tomethi mbe ghal…®Ňčanji gharumwaru.‚ÄĚ|src="co00639b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="11:7"\fig*
\s1 Sem orumburumbuye utuutuninji
\p 
\v 10 Riuriuke iyake Sem orumburumbuye utuutuninji.
\p Thothoko e ghereiye, theghathegha umboiwo vama iko na mbaŇčaniye Sem ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwethaŇčar…® (100), i vaidiya nariye regha idae Apaksad.
\v 11 Iyako e ghereiye Sem mbowo i yaku va theghathegha hweseriyelima (500) na e t…®ne mbowo th…® laghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 12 Apaksad ghatheghathegha vama i wo hweto na umbolima (35) amba th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Sila.
\v 13 Iyako e ghereiye Apaksad i yaku theghathegha hweseriyevar…® na umboto (403) na e t…®ne mbowo th…® laghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča Sila ghatheghathegha vama i wo hweto (30), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Eba.
\v 15 Iyako e ghereiye Sila i yaku theghathegha hweseriyevar…® na umboto (403), na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® laghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča Eba ghatheghathegha hweto na umbovar…® (34), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Peleg.
\v 17 Iyako e ghereiye Eba i yaku theghathegha hweseriyevar…® na hweto (430) na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 18 MbaŇča Peleg ghatheghathegha hweto (30), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Riu.
\v 19 Iyako e ghereiye Peleg i yaku theghathegha hweseriyeiwo na umbosiwo (209) na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 20 MbaŇča Riu ghatheghathegha hweto na umboiwo (32), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Serug.
\v 21 Iyako e ghereiye Riu i yaku theghathegha hweseriyeiwo na umbopir…® (207) na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 22 MbaŇča Serug ghatheghathegha hweto (30), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Naho.
\v 23 Iyako e ghereiye Serug i yaku theghathegha hweseriyeiwo (200) na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 24 MbaŇča Naho ghatheghathegha hoiwo na umbosiwo (29), th…® ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha idae Tira.
\v 25 Iyako e ghereiye Naho i yaku theghathegha hwethaŇčar…®, hoyaworo na umbosiwo (119) na e t…®nenji mbowo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiva gamagai vavana.
\p 
\v 26 MbaŇča Tira vama ghatheghathegha hwepir…® (70) e ghereiye amba th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiya Eibram, Naho na Haran.
\s1 Tira orumburumbuye utuutuninji
\p 
\v 27 Iyake Tira orumburumbuye utuutuninji.
\p Tira le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Eibram, Naho na Haran. Haran nariya Lote.
\v 28 MbaŇča Tira vamba e laghalagha nariye Haran kaero i mare e ghambae moli, Ur Babiloniya e t…®ne.
\v 29 Eibram na ghaghae Naho va th…® ghe. Eibram levo idae Serai na Naho levo idae Milika. Milika iye Haran yawarumbuye na ghaghae nasiyeniye Iska.
\v 30 Serai mava i ghamb…®, va i kwama.
\p 
\v 31 Tira i vaŇčguŇčgiya nariye Eibram na rumbuye Lote, iye Haran nariye, na ghendiyae Serai, Eibram levo, na weiyaŇčgi th…® iteta Ur Babiloniya e t…®ne na th…® raka e val…®vaŇčga regha idae Kenan. Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® raka gheghad Haran na th…® yayaku gheko.
\v 32 Tira va i mare gheko. Ghatheghathegha le ghanaghanagha hweseriyeiwo na umbolima (205).
\c 12
\s1 Giya Loi i kula weya Eibram
\p 
\v 1 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Eibram iŇča, ‚ÄúU iteteya vanautumana iya u rinawe, rama na len bodaboda na u wa e val…®vaŇčga regha ne ya vatomwe e ghen.
\q1 
\v 2 Ne ya vakathaŇčge na vanautuma lagh…®ye regha ghen
\q2 na ne ya mwaewo e ghen.
\q1 Ne ya vakatha idan i lagh…®ye moli,
\q2 na e ghen thovuyeke wolagh…®ye ne i mena weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.
\q1 
\v 3 Ne ya mwaewo weŇčgiya thavala th…® mwaewo e ghen,
\q2 na ne ya gura thavala th…® guraŇčge,
\q1 na yambaneke lagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…®niye
\q2 ghanjimwaewoko ne i mena kaiwae ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Iya kaiwae Eibram i iteteya Haran Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* le utuwe, weiye Lote. E mbaŇčako iyako Eibram ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwepir…® na umbolima (75).
\v 5 Eibram va i vaŇčguŇčgiya levo Serai, rumbuye Lote, na lenji bigibigi na thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva lenji rakakaiwoŇčgiko wolagh…®ye va th…® vaŇčguŇčgi mbaŇča inanji Haran. Th…® loŇčga gheghad veth…® vutha Kenan.
\p MbaŇča th…® vutha Kenan,
\v 6 Eibram i ru vanautumako t…®ne gheghad ve vutha e umbwa lagh…®ye regha inawe. Val…®vaŇčgako iyako idae More, ghemba Sekem e t…®ne. E mbaŇčako iyako Kenan ghar…®ghar…®niye vambe th…® yaku gheko.
\v 7 E val…®vaŇčgako iyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* i yomara weya Eibram na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúVanautumake iyake iya ne ya wogiya weŇčgiya orumburumbu.‚ÄĚ Amba Eibram i vatada ghamba vowo \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae, Ňčgora va i yomaramawe. \fig Amba Eibram i vatada ghamba vowo Giya Loi kaiwae, Ňčgora va i yomaramawe|src="co00640b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="12:7"\fig*
\p 
\v 8 Iyako e ghereiye Eibram i loŇčga na i wa bobokulu e lenji val…®vaŇčga, Betel val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. I vatada le yoŇčathowathowa gheko. Betel va ina val…®vaŇčga i njanja na Ai ina val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. Gheko i vatada ghamba vowo na i kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.
\p 
\v 9 Eibram mbowo i wareriva na i loŇčga i ghemba Kenan val…®vaŇčga yaghalako idae Negev.
\s1 Eibram na Serai inanji Ijipt
\p 
\v 10 Kenan e t…®ne vunuvu lagh…®ye regha va i yomara. Iyako i vakatha Eibram i wa Ijipt na wo ve yaku gheko mbaŇča ubotu.
\v 11 Amba inanji e loŇčga mborowa, ko vama th…® vur…®thai eŇčge Ijipt, Eibram i dage weya levo Serai iŇča, ‚ÄúYa ghareghare, kaiwae wevo man…®uneya ghen,
\v 12 mbaŇča Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye ne th…® thuweŇčge amba th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėLevo iyako.‚Äô Amba bayanbayan th…® un…®gh…®Ňčgo na th…® ghakuŇčge.
\v 13 Mbala u dage weŇčgi na uŇča loun…®na ghino, na mbala ghen kaiwan na thava th…® un…®gh…®Ňčgo na th…® njimbukiki wagiyaweŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča th…® vutha Ijipt, ghar…®ghar…® e vanautumako th…® thuwe Serai emunjora wevo man…®une eunda.
\v 15 MbaŇča Pero le rakakaiwo e raberabe th…® thuwe elagh…®niye, th…® mena Pero e marae na mbe th…® taratarawa vara; iwaeŇčge th…® vaŇčgumenawe ele Ňčgoloko t…®ne.
\v 16 Serai kaiwae, Pero i njimbukiki wagiyaweya Eibram na i giya sip, gout, kau, doŇč…®ki, rakakaiwo na kamel we.
\p 
\v 17 Ko kaiwae Pero va i vaŇčguya Serai na i munjeva levo, iya kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha na ghambwera i yomara weya Pero na le Ňčgoloko gharayakuyaku.
\v 18 Amba Pero i wodu weya Eibram na wo i menawe. MbaŇča i vuthawe kaero i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúMendava u vakatha budakai e ghino? Buda kaiwae mava u govambwara e ghino na uŇča len wevo?
\v 19 Buda kaiwae mendava uŇča loun, iwaeŇčge mendava ya vaŇčgu na yaŇčava lo wevo? E mbaŇčake iyake u vaŇčgunjoghao len wovoke na mbema hu wareri vara!‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Pero iŇča na ragagaith…® vavana veth…® i yathu e kamwath…® mborowa weiye levo Serai na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye th…® iteta vanautumako iyako.
\c 13
\s1 Eibram na Lote th…® vemeghaghath…® weŇčgi
\p 
\v 1 Eibram na levo th…® iteta Ijipt na th…® njogha e ghereinji Negev e t…®ne weinji Lote na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye.
\v 2 E mbaŇčaŇčgiko thiyako Eibram iye va mbema giya vwenyavwenya moli vara. Le sip, gout na kau lemoyo na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva silva na gol.
\p 
\v 3 WeiyaŇčgiya ghamband…®mband…® th…® roiteta val…®vaŇčgako iyako, th…® mena th…® yaku, th…® ghao th…® yaku, gheghad veth…® vutha Ňčgora va th…® yakuma, Betel na Ai e ghanjilughawoghawo
\v 4 Ňčgorava i vatada ghamba vowoma. Na gheko i kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.
\p 
\v 5 Lote vambe Ňčgoreiyeva. Va ele sip, gout na kau. Vambe ele ŇčgamaŇčgamava na ele rakakaiwo.
\v 6 Kaiwae lenji thetheghan va lemoyo moli na nana mava i poku e val…®vaŇčgako iyako na val…®kaiwae thenjighewoko th…® yaku na regha.
\v 7 Iya kaiwae gaith…® i yomara Eibram le thetheghan gharanjimbunjimbu na Lote le thetheghan gharanjimbunjimbu weŇčgi. Eibram na Lote maava th…® yaku na regha kaiwae nana maava i poku e val…®vaŇčgako iyako lenji thetheghan…®ko kaiwanji. (E mbaŇčako iyako Kenan na Perisi ghar…®ghar…®niyeŇčgi vambe th…® yakuva gheko.)
\p 
\v 8 Iya kaiwae Eibram i dage weya Lote iŇča, ‚ÄúThava me vathar…® regha ina e ghanda lughawoghawoke o la thetheghan…®ko ghanjiranjimbunjimbu e ghanjilughawoghawoko kaiwae rumbuŇčgu moliya ghen.
\v 9 Wo ra vemeghaghath…® weinda. U tuthiya the val…®vaŇčga nuwaniya, u wa e val…®vaŇčgana iyena na ghino ya wa e val…®vaŇčga regha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Lote i gh…®maratakwe na i thuwe malamo Jor…®dan ele val…®vaŇčga na ve wo Sowa mbwa var…®ve Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* le uma Iden e t…®ne na Ňčgoreiyeva Ijipt thivathivaniye. (\nd Giya Loi\nd* maa vamba i ŇčambuŇčgiya Sodoma na Gomora.)
\v 11 Lote i tuthiya Jor…®dan malamoniyeko lagh…®ye. Kaero i wareri, i loŇčga na i ghemba boimako. E mbaŇčako iyako th…® veiteteŇčgi.
\v 12 Eibram vambe i reyaku Kenan e t…®ne na Lote i wa na i vatada le yoŇčathowathowa Sodom evasiwae.
\v 13 Sodom ghar…®ghar…®niye va th…® thar…® moli na th…® vakatha thar…® \nd Giya Loi\nd* e marae.
\s1 Eibram i wa Hebron
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča Lote kaero i wareri, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Eibram iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägora vara iya inan…®nawe, u gh…®mara ruwoko, u gh…®mara raŇčgiwoko, u gh…®mara vorowoko na u gh…®mara njaoko.
\v 15 Iya vara val…®vaŇčgana lagh…®ye iya u thuwena ne ya wogiya e ghen na orumburumbu, na nevole ghen len ghamba mbaro mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye.
\v 16 Ne ya vakathaŇčgiya orumburumbu th…® mbuthu na lemoyo moli Ňčgoranjiya yambaneke vughauye na maa val…®kaiwae lolo regha ne i vaona.
\v 17 E mbaŇčake iyake u loŇčga vagh…®liya val…®vaŇčgake lagh…®ye t…®ne, kaiwae ne ya vatomwe e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Eibram i rake le yoŇčathowathowama na ve yakuva e umbwaumbwa lagh…®lagh…®ye evasiwanji Memri ghadidiye Hebron e t…®ne, na gheko i vatada ghamba vowo \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae.
\c 14
\s1 Eibram i vamora Lote gaith…® e t…®ne
\p 
\v 1 KiŇč theghevar…®, Babiloniya ghakiŇč Amrapel, Ilasa ghakiŇč Ariyok, Ilam ghakiŇč Kedolaoma, na Goyim ghakiŇč Taidol.
\v 2 Thiyake veth…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya Sodoma ghakiŇč Bera, Gomora ghakiŇč Besa, Adma ghakiŇč Saineb, Jeboyim ghakiŇč Simeba na Sowa (mbaŇčake th…® uno Bela) ghakiŇč.
\v 3 KiŇč…®ke theghelimake thiyake th…® wabwi na regha e malamo regha idae Sidim (noroke idae Njigh…® Maremareniye Malamoniye).
\v 4 Theghathegha hoyaworo na umboiwo e t…®ne kiŇč…®ke theghelimake va th…® yaku KiŇč Kedolaoma ele mbaro t…®ne, ko iyemaeŇčge theghathegha hoyaworo na umbotoninji e t…®ne kaero th…® botewo na maa th…® giya ghamwaewowe.
\p 
\v 5 Theghathegha hoyaworo na umbovar…® e t…®ne Kedolaoma na le wabwiŇčgi th…® wabwi na regha, th…® rakawa weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…® na th…® kivwalaŇčgiya Repa ghar…®ghar…®niye Asterot Kanaim e t…®ne, Susa ghar…®ghar…®niye Ham e t…®ne, Emi ghar…®ghar…®niye e malamo idae Kirayathaim,
\v 6 na Hor ghar…®ghar…®niye e bobokulu inanji Seir ele val…®vaŇčga. Va th…® mbeleŇčgi gheghad El Paran e vuruvuru vwatavwata ghadidiye.
\v 7 Amba th…® rakavagh…®le na th…® rakamena Mispat (mbaŇčake th…® uno Kades). Th…® kivwalaŇčgiya Amalek ghar…®ghar…®niye na lenji ghamba mbaroko, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yayaku Heisason Tama.
\p 
\v 8 Amba Sodom ghakiŇč Bera, Gomora ghakiŇč Besa, Adma ghakiŇč Saineb, Seboyim ghakiŇč Simeba na Sowa (o Bela) ghakiŇč th…® rakaraŇčgi na th…® vivatha gaith…® kaiwae e malamo idae Sidim,
\v 9 weinjiyaŇčgiya Ilam ghakiŇč, Goyim ghakiŇč, Sina ghakiŇč na Elasa ghakiŇč, kiŇč theghevar…® weinjiyaŇčgiya kiŇč theghelima.
\v 10 E malamoko iyako t…®ne gogoga va lemoyowe na va th…® riyevanjara e kol…®ta, na mbaŇča Sodom na Gomora ghanjikiŇč weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…® th…® rakavo vavana th…® dimban e gogogako t…®nenji, na ghanji uneko wolagh…®ye th…® rakavo na i ru e bobokuluko r…®gher…®ghenji.
\v 11 Amba kiŇč…®Ňčgima theghevar…®ma th…® vur…®gheghema weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ragagaith…® th…® rakaru Sodoma na Gomora e t…®nenji na th…® bigivao bigibigiko thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye, ko amba th…® rakanjogha e ghambaghambanji.
\v 12 Vambe th…® vaŇčguva Eibram rumbuye Lote na le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, kaiwae e mbaŇčako iyako va ina i yaku Sodoma e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 13 Amala regha, iyava th…® rakavoma, i mena i vutha weya Eibram iye Hibru na i giya totowe budakai kaero me yomara. E mbaŇčako iyako Eibram vambe i yaku e umbwaumbwa lagh…®lagh…®ye r…®gher…®ghenji ghadidiye. Umbwaumbwake thiyake tanuwaganjiya Memri iya Amori loloniye regha, na weiyaŇčgiya oghaghae Eskol na Ana va th…® wabwi na regha weinji Eibram. Ko lenji renuwaŇča regha na th…® vethalathalavuŇčgi gaith…® gha mbaŇča.
\v 14 MbaŇča Eibram i loŇčwe rumbuye kaero meth…® vaŇčguŇčgi na veth…® mbaroŇčaŇčgi e vanautuma regha, i kulavathaŇčgiya ragagaith…® e ghayayaoko t…®ne, lenji ghanaghanagha hoseriyeto na theyaworo na theghewa (318), na Memri na oghaghae. Amba th…® rakareghamba weŇčgi gheghad veth…® vuthavaleŇčgi e ghemba regha idae Den ghadidiye.
\v 15 GougoueŇčge iyena Eibram i bigiraweŇčgiya le ragagaith…®ko e wabwiŇčgi na th…® gaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya ghanjith…®gh…®yako na th…® kivwalaŇčgi. Th…® mbeleŇčgi na veth…® mbeleyathuŇčgi Hoba Damasiko e ghaiwabuniyeko.
\v 16 Eibram i biginjoghavao bigibigiko wolagh…®ye mendava th…® kaiv…®Ňčgi na i vaŇčgunjogha rumbuye Lote na le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wanakau vavana na mbe ghar…®ghar…® vavanava.
\s1 Melkisedek i mwaewo weya Eibram
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča Eibram i kivwala kiŇč Kedolaoma na vavanako va weiyaŇčggiko na i njogha, Sodom ghakiŇč i raŇčgi na th…® lavolevole e malamo idae Save (idae regha KiŇč le Malamo).
\p 
\v 18 Amba Melkisedek, iye Salem ghakiŇč, i bigimena bred na waen weya Eibram. Amalagh…®niye vambe Loi Ramevoro Moli le ravowovowova.
\v 19 I mena na i mwaewo weya Eibram iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúEibram, Loi Ramevoro Moli ne i mwaewo e ghen.
\q2 Iye buruburu na yambaneke ghanji ravakatha.
\q1 
\v 20 Na tarawa i voro weya Loi Ramevoro Moli,
\q2 iye me vatomweŇčgiya ghan th…®gh…®yaŇčgina e n…®man…®na ghare.‚ÄĚ
\m Amba Eibram i mban…®vathavathaŇčgi vara bigibigiko wolagh…®ye menda ve kivwalaŇčgiya kiŇč…®ma theghevar…®ma, i vakatha vara wabwi yaworo, ko amba i giya wabwi regha weya Melkisedek.
\p 
\v 21 MbaŇča Eibram i vakathavao iyako, amba Sodom ghakiŇč iŇča, ‚ÄúU vatomweŇčgi eŇčge ghar…®ghar…®na e ghino, ko bigibigina eŇčge mbe len bigibigiwo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Ko iyemaeŇčge Eibram i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa livaira n…®maŇčgu na ya dagerawe weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* Ramevoro Moli, iye buruburu na yambaneke ghanjiravakatha, na ya tholo,
\v 23 maa tene ya wova bigi regha ghen kaiwan, othembe bigi nasi moli Ňčgoreiya ghegha ghae ghathiyo, mbala maane u dage e ghino na uŇča, ‚ÄėGhino menda ya vakatha Eibram na i vwenyavwenya.‚Äô
\v 24 Mane ya wo bigi regha ghino kaiwaŇčgu, ko kaero ya wovatha eŇčge budakaiya ragagaith…® kaero menda th…® ghan. Ko nuwaŇčguiya eŇčge wouneke mendava ya wabwike weiŇčguyaŇčgi, Ana, Eskol na Memri th…® mbana budakai val…®kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\c 15
\s1 Loi le dagerawe weya Eibram
\p 
\v 1 VakathaŇčgiko thiyako e ghereiye, \nd Giya Loi\nd* ghal…®Ňčae i mena weya Eibram e vavaghare ghenelolo e t…®ne. \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúEibram, ne u ndemararu bigi regha,
\q2 ghino len yagogha
\q2 na ne ya giya modan lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Ko iyemaeŇčge Eibram i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúO Loi Giya Lagh…®ye, ne u wogiya budakai e ghino, e mbaŇčake iyake amba ma e lo ŇčgaŇčga? Eliyesa rara Damasiko iye mbe ghambereghaeŇčge ne i rombaro e woyayaoke.
\v 3 Amba maa u vakathaime na e lama ŇčgaŇčga, iya kaiwae lo rakakaiwoke regha ne i roth…®Ňčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* ghal…®Ňčae mbowo i menaweva iŇča, ‚ÄúNandere! Iya len rakakaiwona Eliyesa mane i mbaroŇča ghan yayaona, mbe ghen vara mad…®ban iye ne ghan th…®gh…®th…®gh…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vaŇčguraŇčgiya eto na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u gh…®maravoro e buruburuko na u mando na u vaonaŇčgiya gh…®tarako, thoŇčgo val…®kaiwan; orumburumbu nevole lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgora thiyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Eibram i worawa \nd Giya Loi\nd* ghamidi, na le vakathako iyako kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i warari lagh…®ye kaiwae na i wovarumwarumwaruŇča.
\p 
\v 7 Na tembe i dageweva iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino \nd Giya Loi\nd* iyava ya vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgena Ur Kal…®diya thivathivaniye e t…®ne, na ya vatomwe val…®vaŇčgake iyake na ghamban.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Ko Eibram i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúO \nd Giya Loi\nd* Lagh…®ye, ŇčgoroŇčga ne yaŇča na ya ghareghare val…®vaŇčgake iyake ghino ne ya mbaroŇča?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u bigimenaŇčgiya thetheghan…®ke thiyake: kau botuwo umbwara, gout umbwara na sip gh…®moru umbwara, ghanjitheghathegha umboto na maa manyiwo, bunebune manda na mbo manda.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Eibram i bigimenaŇčgiya thetheghan…®ma na maaŇčgima, i bigimena weya Loi, i tagaviyaŇčgi na geth…®wo iya, geth…®ra val…®vaŇčga, geth…®ra val…®vaŇčga, ko iyemaeŇčge maaŇčgima maa i tagaviyaŇčgi.
\v 11 Amba maa thetheghan gharaghan…®Ňčgi th…® yonja weŇčgiya borogima, ko iyemaeŇčge Eibram i vagegeyathuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 12 MbaŇča Ňčgoreiya tauya wovoŇčgu, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha Eibram i ghenetena nuwa, amba mouwo e maramararuwae regha i yomarawe.
\v 13 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru na val…®kaiwae u ghareghare iyake: orumburumbu nevole veth…® mebwabwari e vanautuma regha. Nevole ghar…®ghar…®ko gheko th…® vakathaŇčgi na th…® kaiwo weŇčgi na th…® vaidiya vuyowo lagh…®ye moli theghathegha hweseriyevar…® e t…®ne.
\v 14 Ko ghino tene ya lith…®gha iya vuyowoko iyako weŇčgiya vanautumako iyako ghar…®ghar…®niye, iya th…® giya vuyowoko weŇčgi, na ne e ghereiye ko amba th…® rakaraŇčgi weiyaŇčgiya madimadinjiko wolagh…®ye.
\v 15 Ko iyemaeŇčge, ghen ne yawalin molao moli, amba u garalawa wein len vanevane.
\v 16 Orumburumbu ne tha theghevar…®ninji e t…®ne amba th…® rakanjoghamake gheke, kaiwae i viva wone ya thuwe vara Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji thar…®ko i lagh…®ye moli na ya giya vuyowo weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča varae vama ve ronja na kaero i momouwo na e mbaŇčako iyako uye vwarara weiye ŇčiŇči munduwae i voro na theŇčgi i ra na th…® yomara na th…® reŇča thetheghan…®ma e ghanjilughawoghawo.
\v 18 E mbaŇčako iyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vaemunjoruŇča le dagerawema weya Eibram na iŇča, ‚ÄúWeŇčgiya orumburumbu ya vatomwa thivathivake iyake weŇčgi. I ri Ijipt e walagh…®ta i mena i wa ve wo walagh…®ta Yupreitis.
\v 19 Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiya inanji e val…®vaŇčgake iyake, Keni ghar…®ghar…®niye, Kenis ghar…®ghar…®niye, Kadmon ghar…®ghar…®niye,
\v 20 Het ghar…®ghar…®niye, Perisi ghar…®ghar…®niye, Repa ghar…®ghar…®niye,
\v 21 Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye, Keinan ghar…®ghar…®niye, Gigasi ghar…®ghar…®niye na Jebusi ghar…®ghar…®niye.‚ÄĚ
\c 16
\s1 Heiga na Ismel utuninji
\p 
\v 1 Serai, Eibram levo, mava val…®kaiwae i ghamb…® gamagai le gh…®moruko kaiwae. Ko iyemaeŇčge le rakakaiwo eunda, t…®nan Ijipt, idae Heiga,
\v 2 iwaeŇčge i dagewe le gh…®moru Eibram iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakathaŇčgo ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya ghamb…®. Wo u ghena wein lo rakakaiwoko, mbwata ne i ghamb…® gamagai ghino kaiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p Eibram i varaeŇčna levo Serai le renuwaŇčako na i vakatha Ňčgoreiye.
\v 3 Lenji yakuyaku Kenan e t…®ne vama i wo theghathegha hoyaworo, iwaeŇčge Serai i vaŇčgugiya le rakakaiwoma t…®nan Ijipt, Heiga, weya le gh…®moru Eibram na levo eunda.
\v 4 MbaŇča Eibram i ghenethaiya Heiga kaero i vaidiya Ňčgama.
\p MbaŇča i ghareghare kaero e tete i vakatha i wovoreŇča ghamberegha na maa i yavwatatawana tanuwagae Serai.
\v 5 Amba Serai i dage weya le gh…®moru Eibram iŇča, ‚ÄúVuyowoke iya i voroke e ghino r…®ghethora ghen. MbaŇča mendava ya vaŇčgugiya lo rakakaiwoko e ghen, na mbaŇčake i ghareghare kaero e tete, i vakatha i wo vorevoreŇča na maa i yavwatata wanaŇčgo. \nd Giya Loi\nd* ghamberegha tembe i tuthi thela le thar…® yake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Amba Eibram i dage weya Serai iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, ghen u mbaroŇča iya len rakakaiwo wevona iyena. The renuwaŇča nuwaniya u vakathawe, ko u vakathawe.‚ÄĚ Serai ghathanavu i thar…®we moli, iya kaiwae Heiga i voitete.
\p 
\v 7 \nd Giya Loi\nd* le nyao thovuye i vaidiya Heiga e mbwarowou regha ghadidiye ina e vuruvuru vwatavwata. Mbwarowouke iyake ina e kamwath…® i wa Sur.
\v 8 Nyaoma thovuye i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúHeiga, Serai le rakakaiwo ghen, ko aŇčga mo ri na ghamwan aŇčga i yere?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguiya ya voiteta tanuwagaŇčguko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* le nyao thovuye i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU njogha weya tanuwaga Serai, na u ghambugha le mbarona.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Nyaoma thovuye mbowo i dageweva iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* nevole i vakathaŇčge na orumburumbu lemoyo moli na mane val…®kaiwae lolo regha i vaonaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 \nd Giya Loi\nd* le nyao thovuye tembe i dageweva iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúŇägamana iya e Ňčgamoin…®na Ňčgama gh…®moru.
\q1 MbaŇča ne i vir…® ne u rena idae Ismel,
\q2 kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i loŇčwe iya len gharev…®r…®na.
\q1 
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge iya naruna iyena nevole le yakuyaku Ňčgoreiya mbwanjam
\q2 na maa val…®kaiwae ra th…®n…®ra murumuru e ghamwa.
\q2 Nevole th…® vegaith…® wanaŇčgi weiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye,
\q2 i meghaghath…® weŇčgiya le bodaboda.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Heiga i unogiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* iya me utuma weiye idae iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen Loi u thuwathuwa e ghino,‚ÄĚ iya kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ma thuwe iya loloke i thuwathuwake e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Iya kaiwae mbwarowouko iyako idae Beya Lahai Roi, gharumwaru mbwarowouke iyake tanawagaya lolo e yawayawaliye i thuwathuwa e ghino. Ina Kades na Bered e ghanjilughawoghawo.
\p 
\v 15 Heiga i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru na Eibram i rena idae Ismel.
\v 16 E mbaŇčako iyako Eibram ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwewona.
\c 17
\s1 Loi i utugiya weya Eibram le dageraweko ghanono
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Eibram vama ghatheghathegha i wo hwesiwo na umbosiwo, \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbowo i yomaraweva na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye. Len yakuyaku mbe i thovuye vara e maraŇčgu na thava thar…® regha i mwenja riwan…®na.
\v 2 Amba ne ya vaemunjoruŇča lo dagerawema e ghen na nevole ya vakathaŇčgiya orumburumbu lemoyo moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Eibram i dipoumu e thelauko vwatae na Loi i dagewe iŇča,
\v 4 ‚ÄúGhino e lo val…®vaŇčga lo dagerawe iyake e ghen, ghen vanautuma lemoyo rumbunjiya ghen.
\v 5 Idan…®na mama ne mbaŇča regha th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėEibram‚Äô, mbema ne th…®Ňča vara ‚ÄėEibraham,‚Äô\f + \fr 17:5 \ft Eibraham gharumwaru, ‚Äúvanautuma lemoya ramanji‚ÄĚ.\f* kaiwae ne ya vakathaŇčge na orumburumbuŇčgiya vanautuma lemoyo.
\v 6 Ne ya vakathaŇčge na orumburumbu lemoyo moli. Nevole ya vakathaŇčgi na th…® vakatha vanautuma lemoyo na kiŇč…®Ňčgi ne th…® rimbun e ghen.
\v 7 Ne ya renuwaŇčakiki iya dageraweke iyake gha mbaŇča i ri rogha, ghino na ghen e ghanda lughawoghawoke, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva orumburumbu thako muyaiko na thiye orumburumbunjiva tha na tha mbaŇča muyaiko. Len Loi ghino mbe wombereghaeŇčge na orumburumbu tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.
\v 8 Val…®vaŇčgake iya u mebwabwarikewe, mbema Kenan lagh…®yeke vara, kaero ya vatomwe e ghen na orumburumbu mbaŇča muyaiko na lenji ghamba mbaro memeghabananiye, na ghino ne lenji Loi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Loi i dage weya Eibraham budakai wone th…® vakatha
\p 
\v 9 Loi mbowo i dageweva Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ghen e len val…®vaŇčga, u njimbukiki wagiyawe iya lo dageraweke e ghen na orumburumbu tha na tha mbaŇča muyaiko nevole th…® vakatha iya budakaiya noroke ya utugiya e ghen na u vakatha.
\v 10 Ghen na orumburumbu tha na tha mbaŇča muyaiko ne hu ghambugha lo dageraweke, ne hu vakatha Ňčgoreiye vara iyake: Ňägama gh…®moru regha na regha ne hu kiten…®yatho riwae mbothiye njimwae.
\v 11 Gh…®mogh…®moruna, mbema taulagh…®na vara ghemi, hu vakatha kamwath…®ke iyake. Na iyake ne lo dageraweke, ghen na ghino e ghanda lughawoghawo, ghanono.
\v 12 Tha na tha mbaŇča i menamenako, gamagai gh…®mogh…®moru ne th…® vir…® na kaero th…® yaku mbaŇča theghewa, ne hu kitena riwanji mbothiye njimwae. Len rakakaiwo th…® vir…® e ghan yayaona t…®ne na len rakakaiwo u vamodaŇčgi weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana, na maa th…® rimbun e ghen, tembe u vakathava Ňčgoreiye weŇčgi.
\v 13 Th…® vir…® e ghan yayaona t…®ne o u vamodaŇčgi e mani, ne u kitena riwanji mbothiye njimwae. Vakathake iya u vakatha e riwan…®na ne i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčge na u renuwaŇčakikiya dageraweke iyake ghe mbaŇča i ri rogha.
\v 14 The gh…®moru regha thoŇčgo ma th…® kitena riwae mbothiye, loloko iyako ne i meraŇčgi moli e wabwiko iyako t…®ne, kaiwae kaero i rake dageraweko iyake ghe mbaro.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Loi tembe i dageweva Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúWeya len wevo Serai, mane te u unova idae Serai, idae togha ne u uno Sera.
\v 16 Mbene ghareŇčguwe vara na ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru kaiwan. Ne ya vakatha elagh…®niye na orumburumbuye th…® vakatha vanautuma lemoyo, na kiŇč vavana ne th…® rimbun weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Eibraham i dipoumu e thelauko vwatae, i vav…®ra utuko iyako na tembe i dagewe ghamberegha iŇča, ‚ÄúNe val…®kaiwaeya amalagh…®sar…® ghatheghathegha kaero i wo hothaŇčar…®? Ne val…®kaiwae Sera, kaero i thanja moli, na ghatheghathegha kaero hwesiwo na tembe i laghamb…®va Ňčgama?‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Iya kaiwae Eibraham i dage weya Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo u worawe eŇčge naruŇčguko Ismel e ghamwan!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoreiye, ko len wevo Sera ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru regha na ne u rena idae Aisake.\f + \fr 17:19 \ft Aisake ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiye Hibru utu regha gharumwaru ‚Äúi vav…®r…®‚ÄĚ.\f* Ne ya vaemunjoruŇča lo dagerawe weiŇčgu. Dageraweke iyake ghe mbaŇča i ri rogha, amalagh…®niye na orumburumbuye mbaŇča muyaiko weŇčgi.
\v 20 Ko naruna Ismel kaiwae, kaero ma loŇčwe iya len renuwaŇčana. Tembene ya renuwaŇčakikiva. Ne ya vakatha na i ghamb…® lagh…®ye, na ne ya mwaewowe na ya vakatha na orumburumbuye lemoyo. Le ŇčgaŇčga theyaworo na theghewo, thiye ne th…® tabo na giyagiyaŇčgi e lenji wabwiŇčgi, na tembene ya vakathana orumburumbuye th…® tabona vanautuma lagh…®ye reghava.
\v 21 Ko iyemaeŇčge lo v…®ghath…®ke weiŇčgu Aisake, iya Sera ne i ghamb…®na e mbaŇčake iyake theghatheghako i menamenake, mbene ya vinjimb…® vara.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 MbaŇča i utuvao weiye Eibraham, kaero i njoghava.
\p 
\v 23 E mbaŇčako iyako t…®ne, Eibraham i vaŇčguya nariye Ismel na gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye va th…® vir…® e gheuko t…®ne na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva le rakakaiwo va i vamodaŇčgi; gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye na i kitena riwanji mbothiye njimwae, Ňčgoreiya Loi me dagemawe.
\v 24 Amalagh…®niye Eibraham ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwesiwo na umbosiwo ko amba th…® kiten eŇčge riwa mbothiye njimwae,
\v 25 na nariye Ismel ghatheghathegha vama i wo hoyaworo na umboto amba th…® kiten eŇčge riwae mbothiye njimwae.
\v 26 Eibraham na nariye Ismel mbe thenjighewo vara th…® kitena riwanji mbothiye njimwae e mbaŇča iyako e t…®ne.
\v 27 Gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye Eibraham e ghayayaoko t…®ne na thavalava Ňčgoreiya va i vamodo e mani e mbaŇčako iyako t…®ne th…® tena riwanji mbothiye njimwae.
\c 18
\s1 Bwabwari thegheto th…® vutha weya Eibraham
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča regha theghatheghako iyako e t…®ne mbaŇča varae mbema i vur…®gheghewe vara, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i yomara weya Eibraham e umbwaumbwa lagh…®lagh…®ye r…®ghenji Memri e t…®ne; mbaŇčaniye Eibraham i roraŇčgi ele yoŇčathowathowa ghath…®n…®mba th…® taterawe.
\v 2 Eibraham i tagath…®na marae na i vaidiŇčgiya amaamala thenjigheto th…® ndeghath…® e ghamwae. MbaŇča i vaidiŇčgi i yondovir…® ele yoŇčathowathowama t…®ne, i raŇčgi na ve thuweŇčgi. Ghanji yavwatata kaiwae i kururu e ghamwanji.
\p 
\v 3 Amba iŇča, ‚ÄúGiyagiyana, thoŇčgo u worawaweŇčgo e ghamwami, thava hu iteta ghambaŇčguke.
\v 4 Wo hu ndeghath…® vara gheke na wo vath…®na mbwa na hu thavwiya gheghemina ko amba hu ronja e umbwana riburibuwae.
\v 5 Wo va bigimena ghan…®Ňčga seiwo na hu laghan na i thalavuŇčga ko amba hu waova. Kaiwae mo hu yavwatata wanaŇčgo na hu vutha e ghino iya kaiwae yala thalavuŇčga.‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúI thovuye moli, u vakatha Ňčgoreiya len renuwaŇčana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Eibraham mbema ghena n…®maeŇčge, i njogha ele yoŇčathowathowa t…®ne na i dage weya Sera iŇča, ‚ÄúN…®man i maiya na u bigiya pwalawa ghayamoyamo thovuye mbambato, mbwata 20 kilo, na u vakatha bred.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 I yoruku weŇčgiya le thetheghan na ve tuthiya kau nariye ghe tabo vond…®vond…®, i vatomwe weya le rakakaiwo regha, i yoruku na ve vakatha ghan…®Ňčga kaiwae.
\v 8 Eibraham i bigimena mil…®k kaero i lad, mil…®k na kauma nariye meth…® vivatharawema na i bigirawe bwabwarima e maranji. MbaŇča th…® ghan…®Ňčga Eibraham mbe i ndeghath…® evasiwanji e umbwako r…®ghe.
\p 
\v 9 Th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLen wevo Sera aŇčga inae?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe ina e Ňčgoloko t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Amba ghanjiuma regha i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake vara noroke theghatheghake i menamenake tembene ya njoghamava e ghen na ne e mbaŇčako iyako Sera ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ
\p E Ňčgoloko ghaghambaru, Sera vambe i ndegath…®we vara, e ghereinji na i vandeŇče th…® utuko.
\v 11 Eibraham na Sera vama th…® thanja moli na Sera vama i kivwala ghatheghathegha val…®kaiwae i vaidiya Ňčgama.
\v 12 Utuutuko iyako kaiwae Sera tembe i vav…®r…®va ghamberegha kaiwae va i renuwaŇča na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake kaero maa elo vur…®gheghe na amalako kaero i amalagh…®sar…®. Maa val…®kaiwae wo vaidiva ghamb…® warawaraniye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae Sera i vav…®r…® na iŇča, ‚ÄėNe val…®kaiwae ya vaidiya Ňčgama mbaŇčake iya kaero ya thanjake?‚Äô
\v 14 Thare bigi regha i vuyowo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*? MbaŇča ne ya njoghama e ghen e mbaŇčake iyake theghatheghake i menamenake, Sera ne i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Ko kaiwae Sera va weiye le mararu i kwan na iŇčava maa me vav…®r…®. Ko \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mbwana, mo vav…®r…®.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Eibraham i naŇčgo Sodom kaiwae
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča giyagiyama th…® yondovir…® na th…® wareri, th…® loŇčga na ghamwanji i ghemba Sodom. Eibraham weiyaŇčgi na ve ndeiyathuŇčgi. Th…® mena e val…®vaŇčga regha e kamwath…® mborowa amba maranji i nja Sodom.
\v 17 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* mbe ghamberegha iŇča, ‚ÄúMane ya wothuwele weya Eibraham budakaiya lo renuwaŇča ne ya vakatha.
\v 18 Kaiwae Eibraham orumburumbuye, nevole th…® tabo na vanautuma lagh…®ye na vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha. Na weya amalagh…®niye ne ghareŇčgu weya vanautumake wolagh…®ye e yambaneke vwatae.
\v 19 Kaiwae ghino va ya tuthiya Eibraham na amalagh…®niye mbala i vavaghare mbaro weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga na orumburumbuye, mbala th…® ghambugha ghino lo renuwaŇča na th…® reŇča e kamwath…® thovuye na budakaiya ghino ya warari kaiwae. ThoŇčgo th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyako ne ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya budakai va ya dagera weya Eibraham.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dage weya Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya loŇčwe Sodom na Gomora ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji vakatha vathar…® weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana na lenji randa kaero i voro e ghino.
\v 21 Mbowo ghino vara ya nja na va thuweŇčgi na ya vaemunjoruŇča thoŇčgo mbema emunjora lenji vakatha vathar…®ko iyako, na mbala ya ghareghare mbema emunjora lenji vakathako i thar…® moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Amaamalama thenjighewo th…® loŇčga na ghamwanji i ghemba Sodoma, ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe i rondeghath…® vara weiye Eibraham.
\v 23 Eibraham i ndemena evasiwae na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjora ne u mukuwoŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® raraithar…®?
\v 24 ŇägoroŇčga, thoŇčgo iyelima ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye inanji e ghembako t…®ne, mbema ne u mukuwoŇčgi vara ghembarako? Ko maane gharen i njao weŇčgi iyelimako iya thovuthovuyeŇčgiko inanjiko gheko?
\v 25 Mbwana maa val…®kaiwae ne u gaboŇčgiya thovuthovuye weinjiyaŇčgiya raraithar…®. Maa val…®kaiwae moli! Maane u vakatha iyako. ThoŇčgo u vakatha Ňčgoreiye thovuthovuye ne th…® vaidiya vuyowo weinjiyaŇčgiya raraithar…®. Mbema ma val…®kaiwae vara. Ghen ghan…®mbereghana yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niyeke wolagh…®ye ghanjiratuthi. Mbene u thuwe na i thovuye e maran amba u vakatha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ya vaidiŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye iyelima inanji gheko, thiye ne kaiwanji mane ya mukuwo ghembako iyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Eibraham mbowo i naŇčgoweva iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae kaero ya gham…®no lo vur…®ghegheke val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya utu e ghen renuwaŇčako iyako kaiwae, nuwaŇčguiya mbowo ya utuva e ghen, othembe ghino mbema lolo eŇčge ya vwara e mbun…®ma na madibe.
\v 28 Naka thoŇčgo mbe iyevar…® na theghelima eŇčge ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye, ne u mukuwo ghembarako kaiwae thovuthovuye theghelima kaero th…® roraŇčgi?‚ÄĚ
\p \nd Giya Loi\nd* i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúOthembe ne ya vaidiya thovuthovuye mbe iyevar…® na theghelima eŇčge, mane ya mukuwo ghembako iyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Eibraham mbowo i dageweva iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ŇčgoroŇčga thoŇčgo mbe iyevar…® eŇčge thovuthovuye inanji e ghembako t…®ne?‚ÄĚ
\p I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMane ya mukuwo ghembako iyako othembe ne ya vaidi mbe iyevar…® eŇčge thovuthovuye inanji gheko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, \nd Giya Loi\nd* thava u gaith…® wanaŇčgo, ko u vatomwe eŇčge e ghino na mbowa ya vaitova. Ne u vakatha budakai thoŇčgo mbe iyetoeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® thovuthovuye inanji gheko?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMane ya vakatha bigi regha thoŇčgo iyeto thovuthovuye inanji gheko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, giyana, u ghataŇčaghath…®Ňčgo na mbowo ya utuva e ghen. ThoŇčgo raŇčama mbe theiwoko kaiwanji eŇčge inanji gheko?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúTheiwoko mane ya mukuwo ghembako iyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Eibraham mbowo i naŇčgoweva iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, ne u ndegaith…® wanaŇčgo, ko ma u vatomwe eŇčge na ya lavaito vara mbaŇčara. Naka mbema theyaworo eŇčge thovuthovuye inanji Sodom t…®ne?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúTheyaworoko e idanji mane ya mukuwo ghembako iyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 MbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i utuvao weiye Eibraham kaero i itete na iwa na Eibraham i njogha e ghambae.
\c 19
\s1 Sodom ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji thar…® i lagh…®ye moli
\p 
\v 1 Vama yegh…®yegh…®ye moli amba nyao thovuye theghewo veth…® vutha Sodom. Lote va ina i yaku e ghembako ghamba ru. MbaŇča i thuweŇčgi, i yondovir…® na i mena i kururu e thelauko vwatae e ghamwanji.
\v 2 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGiyagiyana, aee wo hu mena vara ru elo Ňčgoloko na hu latowowe. Ne hu thavwiya gheghemi na wo ra laghena noroke gougou, na evole mbaŇčambaŇča ko amba hu wava.‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMaa val…®kaiwae, mbema wo ghena vara eto gheke Ňčgora ghar…®ghar…®ke lenji ghamba mevathavatha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge Lote mbe i rovur…®gheghe vara weŇčgi gheghad th…® varaeŇčna le renuwaŇčako na th…® wa weinji ele Ňčgolo. MbaŇča veth…® ru, Lote i vivatha ghan…®Ňčga, i Ňčambu bred ma weiye is…®t na th…® ghan.
\v 4 Giyagiyama theghewo vamba e laghalaghanji kaero gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye Sodom e ghembako lagh…®ye t…®ne, tabwagha na amalagh…®sar…®, th…® rakamena th…® ndegh…®liŇča Ňčgoloko.
\v 5 Kaero th…® kularu weya Lote th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGh…®mogh…®moruma theghewo iya me yegh…®yegh…®yenja na th…® menama e ghen aŇčga inanji? U vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgima etoke na mbala wo vakatha yathima thanavuniye weimaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Lote i raŇčgi eto na i th…®kiya th…®n…®mbama e ghereiye,
\v 7 na iŇča, ‚ÄúAee wouna, thava hu utuŇča thanavu raithar…® Ňčgoreiyena.
\v 8 Ko thoŇčgo lemi renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiyena, lo ŇčgaŇčga theunyiwo, amba maa th…® vavaghena. Wo ya vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi e ghemi na the renuwaŇča nuwamiya hu vakatha weŇčgi. Ko thava hu utuŇča thar…® utuniye na i ghembeŇčgiya giyagiyake thiyake, kaiwae kaero meth…® ru elo Ňčgoloke na inanji elo gana t…®ne.‚ÄĚ \fig Lote iŇča, ‚ÄúAee wouna, thava hu utuŇča thanavu raithar…® Ňčgoreiyena.‚ÄĚ|src="CO00651b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="19:7"\fig*
\p 
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® gonjogha weya Lote th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU roiteta th…®n…®mbana. Ghen bwabwariya ghen! Thela ghen u munjekeva ne u utuveime the thanavuya ne wo vakatha? Nuwaniya wo vakatha vuyowo lagh…®ye e ghen na i kivwala ne wo vakatha weŇčgi?‚ÄĚ Th…® mwanavewo Lote na th…® ndethaiya th…®n…®mbama na th…® munjeva th…® tagaraka.
\p 
\v 10 Ko iyemaeŇčge nyaoma thovuthovuye e Ňčgoloko t…®nema th…® lawe Lote, th…® mwana vaŇčguruwo e Ňčgoloko t…®ne na th…® tagatumo th…®n…®mbama.
\v 11 Amba th…® vakathaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruma, tabwagha na amalagh…®sar…®, iya inanjima e mbwaŇčaŇčgilako na maramaranji thiya kwaghe, na mbala maa th…® thuwe mbwaŇčaŇčgilako.
\s1 Lote i roiteta Sodom
\p 
\v 12 Nyaoma thovuye theghewoma th…® vaito Lote th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare ghan mband…®mband…® reghava ina e ghembake t…®ne ‚ÄĒ Ňčgoreiya len ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau, oghendiya o thelava e ghanuke t…®ne? ThoŇčgo Ňčgoreiye e mbaŇčake vara iyake u vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi,
\v 13 kaiwae noroke wo mukuwo ghembake iyake. \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i loŇčwe ghar…®ghar…® gharenji le v…®r…®, ghembake iyake ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji thar…® i lagh…®ye moli, iya kaiwae menda i variyeime na wo mena wo mukuwo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Lote i wa na ve dage weŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruma, iya le ŇčgaŇčga theunyiwoma th…® munje th…® vaŇčguŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu yoruku na ra iteta ghembake iyake, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* noroke i mukuwo ghembake iyake.‚ÄĚ Ko iyemaeŇčge oghendiyaya th…®Ňčava i vakatha goron.
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇča kaero i ghere buruburuko r…®ghe, nyaoma thovuthovuye thenjighewo th…® vavothaŇča Lote th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU yoruku! U vaŇčguŇčgiya len wevo na len ŇčgaŇčga theunyiwo iya inanjina gheke na hu vo, ne iwaeŇčge hu vaidiya vuyowoke iya ghembake iyake ne th…® vaidi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Lote va i roroghagha seiwo, ko iyemaeŇčge kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* va ghare i njaweŇčgi, nyaoŇčgima thovuthovuye th…® vaŇčgu Lote, levo na le ŇčgamaŇčgama theunyiwo e n…®man…®manji na th…® vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi e ghembako t…®ne.
\v 17 MbaŇča kaero inanji eto, amalama regha i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu yoruku hu voiteta val…®vaŇčgake iyake na hu vamora yawal…®mi. Ne hu ndegh…®maranjogha e ghereimi na ne hu ndetowo e malamona t…®ne. Hu ruku na i wa e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji mbala maa hu vaidiya mukuwoko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Ko iyemaeŇčge Lote i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúAee wogiyagiya thovuthovuye, thava Ňčgoreiyako.
\v 19 Kaero ghemi gharemi i nja weŇčgo na ya vaidiya lemi thalavu lagh…®ye mohu vamora yawaliŇčgu. Ko maa val…®kaiwaŇčgu eŇčge ya vo na i ruwoko e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji, mbwatane mukuwoko i lavaidiŇčgo na ya mare.
\v 20 Mbe u thuwe ghemba nasiye iyako? Maa i bwagabwaga, val…®kaiwae ya vowawe na ya vamora yawaliŇčguwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Nyaoma thovuye i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye, ne ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya len renuwaŇčana. Mane ya mukuwo iya ghemba ne vorunawe.
\v 22 Ko mbema u wa eŇčge, n…®man i maiya, kaiwae amba mane ya vakatha bigi regha gheghad vo vutha gheko.‚ÄĚ (Kaiwae Lote va iŇča nasiye iya kaiwae ghembako idae Jowa.)
\s1 Giya Loi i mukuwoŇčgiya Sodom na Gomora
\p 
\v 23 MbaŇča Lote ve vutha Jowa varae kaero i yovoro.
\v 24 Amba \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha var…®var…® ndaŇčaŇčanje na sulpa i rara Ňčgoreiya uyema i nja Sodom na Gomora.
\v 25 E kamwath…®ko iyako mbema i mukuwoŇčgi vara ghembaghemba e val…®vaŇčgako iyako. Ma tembe lolo reghava e yawayawaliye na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva nana na umbwaumbwa.
\v 26 Ko iyemaeŇčge Lote levo i gh…®maranjogha e ghereiye na kaero i gharav…® na var…® Ňčgoreiya njigh…®.
\p 
\v 27 Eibraham i gheneiru yan…®mbaŇčambaŇča na tembe i njoghava Ňčgora menda i ndeghath…® \nd Giya Loi\nd* e ghamwae.
\v 28 I tagath…®na marae na i nja Sodom na Gomora na ghawoko lagh…®ye e malamoko t…®ne. I thuwe mundu i Ňčgothighevir…® e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, Ňčgoreiya th…® r…®mba njam…®ra.
\p 
\v 29 Ko mbaŇča Loi i mukuwoŇčgiya ghembaghemba e malamoko iyako t…®ne, i renuwaŇčakikiya Eibraham na i vaŇčguraŇčgiya Lote vuyowoko e t…®ne, na i mukuwoŇčgiya ghembaghembako Lote va i yakuko weŇčgi.
\s1 Lote na le ŇčgaŇčgama theunyiwoma
\p 
\v 30 Kaiwae Lote va weiye le mararu Jowa e t…®ne, weiyaŇčgiya oyawarumbuyeŇčgima theunyiwo, th…® wa e ououko r…®gher…®ghenji na veth…® yaku e maŇčgavar…®.
\v 31 MbaŇča regha yawarumbuye lagh…®yeniye i dage weya nasiyeniyema iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae ramanda kaero i thanja, na ma gh…®mogh…®moru nanji gheke na val…®kaiwae ra vaŇčguŇčgi, kaiwae yambaneke thanavuniye iyako, na ra ghamb…® weindaŇčgi.
\v 32 Ra vakatha ramanda na i muna waen lagh…®ye moli na i vakatha numounounowe, ko amba ra ghena weinda mbala ra ghamb…® weinda na gheuke mbe i mbele vara amalagh…®niye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 Gougouko iyako th…® giya waen weya ramanji na i mun. Lagh…®yeniye i ghena weiye. Kaiwae me muna waen lagh…®ye moli, maa ele ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga yawarumbuye le vakathawe.
\p 
\v 34 MbaŇčambaŇčavena yawarumbuye lagh…®yeniye i dage weya nasiyeniye iŇča, ‚ÄúMe gougou ma ghena weiŇčgu ramanda. Noroke mbowo ra vakatha na i mun…®va waen lagh…®ye, ko amba ghen vo ghena wein, mbala ra ghamba gamagai weinda na gheuko mbe i mbele vara amalagh…®niye.‚ÄĚ
\v 35 Na gougouko iyako th…® vakatha ramanji tembe i mun…®va waen lagh…®ye moli, ko amba nasiyeniye i wa na ve ghena weiye. Kaiwae me muna waen lagh…®ye moli, maa ele ghareghare ŇčgoroŇčga yawarumbuye le vakathawe.
\p 
\v 36 Lenji vakathako iyako une mbe theunyiwo vara th…® th…®n.
\v 37 Yawarumbuye lagh…®yeniye i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, na i rena idae Mowab. Iye orumburumbuyeŇčgiya Mowab ghar…®ghar…®niye
\v 38 Yawarumbuye nasiyeniye vambe i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru, na i rena idae Ben-Ami.\f + \fr 19:38 \ft Ben-Ami gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye ‚Äúlo boda nariye‚ÄĚ kaiwae rumbuye tembe i tabo na ramaeva.\f* Iye orumburumbuyeŇčgiya Amon ghar…®ghar…®niye.
\c 20
\s1 Eibraham na Abimelek utuninji
\p 
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako Eibraham i ri Memri na i loŇčga na i wa Kenan e yaghalaniyeko, na ve yaku vara Kades na Sur e ghanjilughawoghawo, e ghemba regha idae Gera.
\v 2 MbaŇča va ina gheko i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® iŇčava louya iya levo Sera. IwaeŇčge Abimelek, Gera ghakiŇč iŇča na Sera i menawe na i munjeva levo.
\p 
\v 3 Gougou regha Loi i yomara weya Abimelek ghenelolo e t…®ne na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru ne u mare kaiwae menda uŇča na th…® vaŇčgumena wevoke iyake e ghen. Elana iyana kaero i ghe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge Abimelek amba maa i ghenethaiya elako, iya kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi, maa ya vakatha mun thar…®. Ne uŇča na ya mare weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® ya mbaroŇčaŇčgike?
\v 5 Mbe Eibraham ghamberegha mendava i dage weŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄėLouya elako‚Äô, na elagh…®niye tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄėLouya amalako‚Äô. Menda ya vakatha iyako weiye lo renuwaŇča thovuye na menda yaŇčaeŇčge lo vakathako i thovuye moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Amba Loi i dagewe ghenelolo e t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúYa ghareghare mo vakatha iyana weiye len renuwaŇča thovuye, iya kaiwae ma vakathaŇčge ma val…®kaiwan u vakatha thar…® e maraŇčgu, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ma vakathaŇčge na ma mo ghena wein.
\v 7 E mbaŇčake iyake u vaŇčgunjogha elana weya le gh…®moru, kaiwae amalagh…®niye ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu gharautu. Tene i naŇčgo kaiwan mbala ma u mare. Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo maa u vaŇčgu njogha weya le gh…®moru, ghen na ghan…®yayaona ne huya mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča Abimelek kaero i thuweiru, i kulavathaŇčgiya le rakakaiwo e raberabe, na i utu giya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye meth…® yomarawe, na i vakathaŇčgi th…® mararu lagh…®ye.
\v 9 Amba Abimelek i kularuwo Eibraham na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbala thava mo vakatha Ňčgoreiyake weime. Ma vakatha vathar…® the bigi e ghen, iya i vakathaŇčge na u womena vuyowoke iyake e ghino na elo ghamba mbaroke t…®ne? Budakaiya mo vakatha maa lolo regha ne i vakatha e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Abimelek i vaito Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mo vakatha Ňčgoreiyake?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMenda lo renuwaŇča yaŇčaeŇčgeva maa lolo regha ina gheke i yavwatatawana Loi, na ne iwaeŇčge th…® un…®gh…®Ňčgo lo wevoke bayae.
\v 12 Emunjoru elagh…®niye louŇčgu. Ramame regha weiŇčgu, ko t…®nae eŇčge mbe regha, na iyava ya vaŇčguke.
\v 13 Na mbaŇča Loi va i dage e ghino na ya iteta bwebwe ghambae na ya wa e val…®vaŇčga regha, iwaeŇčge ya dagewe yaŇča, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo gharen e ghino, mbaŇča regha na regha ra vaidiŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, mbala mbe uŇča vara, ‚ÄúLouŇčgu.‚ÄĚ ‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Amba Abimeleki i vaŇčgunjogha Sera weya Eibraham na tembe i giyava ghamwaewa sip, kau na rakakaiwoŇčgi gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau.
\v 15 Abimeleki i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u thuwe lo ghamba mbaroke, the val…®vaŇčga nuwaniya u wa na vo yakuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 I dage weya Sera iŇča, ‚ÄúYa giya weya lou Eibraham silva geth…®serithaŇčar…® na i vaemunjoruŇča weŇčgiya thavala weiŇčji, mbema emunjoru maa e len thar…® na taulagh…®ke mbala th…® ghareghare ma menda u vakatha thar…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amba Eibraham i naŇčgo weya Loi na Loi i vamoruŇčgiya Abimeleki levo na le rakakaiwo wanakau na mbala val…®kaiwae mbowo th…® ghamb…®va gamagai,
\v 18 kaiwae Abimeleki mendava i vaŇčgwa Sera Eibraham levo, na ve ghena ele Ňčgolo iya kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* i gokiŇčgiya wanakau ele Ňčgoloko t…®ne, mbala maa val…®kaiwae th…® ghamb…®.
\c 21
\s1 Aisake ghembaŇča i vir…®
\p 
\v 1 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i worawa Sera e ghamwae Ňčgoreiya va le dagerawe, na i vamboromboroŇča ŇčgoroŇčga va le dagerakowe.
\v 2 Sera i th…®n na kaero gha mbaŇča i ghamb…®. I ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru weiye Eibraham, mbaŇča kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli, Ňčgoreiya Loi va le dagerakowe.
\v 3 Eibraham i rena Ňčgamako Sera i ghamb…®ko idae Aisake.
\v 4 MbaŇča theghewa e t…®ne Eibraham i kitena Aisake riwae njimwae mbothiye Ňčgoreiya Loi va i utugiyawe.
\v 5 MbaŇča Aisake i vir…® Eibraham ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…®.
\p 
\v 6 Sera iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi kaero i vakathaŇčgo na Ňčgoreiye, i woveŇčgwa warari weiye lo vav…®r…® na thavala ne th…® loŇčwa iyako ne th…® vav…®r…® budakai menda i yomara e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Na mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúThela mbala va i dage weya Eibraham na iŇčava Sera val…®kaiwae i vathu Ňčgama? IyemaeŇčge kaero ya ghamb…® weiŇčgu mbaŇča kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Eibraham i variyeyathuŇčgiya Heiga na Ismel
\p 
\v 8 MbaŇča Aisake kaero i lagh…®ye na i r…®tena thu, Eibraham i vakatha vawarari ghathaga lagh…®ye regha.
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge e vawarariko t…®ne Sera i thuwe Heiga, t…®nan Ijipt, nariye weiye Eibraham, i vakatha goron weya Aisake,
\v 10 iwaeŇčge i dage weya Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúU variyeyathuŇčgiya rakakaiwoko iyako weiye nariyeko. Ghino yaŇča nariyeko mane te i wova bigi regha e ghen. NaruŇčguke Aisake ghamberegha moli ne i mbaroŇča ghan…®yayaona.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 RenuwaŇčako iyako i vakatha Eibraham i rerenuwaŇča lagh…®ye moli, kaiwae amalagh…®niye mbe nariyeva Ismel.
\v 12 Ko amba Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u rerenuwaŇča Sera le utuko e ghen kaiwae. U vakatha Ňčgora iya le renuwaŇčana, kaiwae orumburumbuma va ya dagerawema e ghen ne th…® mena weya Aisake.
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge iya Heiga nariyena ne ya vakathana orumburumbuye tembe lemoyova, kaiwae ghen mbe narun reghava.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča Eibraham kaero i thuweiru, i mbana ghan…®Ňčga na mbwa ina e begi thetheghan njeniye, i bigirawe Heiga e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le na i variyeyathu weiye nariyema. Heiga na nariye Ismel mbema th…® loŇčga takwe eŇčge vara Beyasiba vuruvuruko vwatavwata.
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇča kaero th…® mun…®vao mbwama e begima, Heiga kaero i worawa Ňčgamama e riburibu nasiye
\v 16 na ve yaku seiwo bwagabwaga weya Ňčgamama, kaiwae va le renuwaŇča iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya thuwe naruŇčguke i mare.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča ve yakuyaku gheko, kaero i randa.
\p 
\v 17 Ko mbaŇča Loi i loŇčwe Ňčgamama i randaranda, amba le nyao thovuye regha i kula na i njama weya Heiga iŇča, ‚ÄúHeiga, buda i ghar…®Ňčge? Tha u mararu. Loi kaero i loŇčweya iya Ňčgamana i randa.
\v 18 U wa na vo mwanavaira Ňčgamako e n…®mae, kaiwae nevole ya vakathaŇčgiya orumburumbuye th…® tabo na vanautuma lagh…®ye regha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Amba Loi i vakatha na i thuwe mbwarowou evasiwae. I wa iyana ve ghend…®vanjara mbwama ghabegi na i giya weya nariyema i mun.
\p 
\v 20 MbaŇča Ňčgamako i tabo Loi vambe weiye vara. Lenji yakuyaku Paran e vuruvuru vwatavwata, Ismel i tabo na rawowoidi thovuye regha e mbwenara.
\v 21 Lenji yakuyaku e val…®vaŇčgako iyako e t…®ne, t…®nae i vaŇčguya t…®nan Ijipt eunda na levo.
\s1 Eibraham na Abimeleki th…® vakatha tubwe mbwarowou regha kaiwae
\p 
\v 22 Va e mbaŇčako iyako Abimeleki weiye le ragagaith…® lenji randeviva idae Pikol, th…® wa weya Eibraham na Abimeleki iŇča, ‚ÄúWein Loi e len vakathake wolagh…®ye e t…®ne.
\v 23 Iya kaiwae u tholo e maraŇčgu Loi e marae, mane u vakatha thar…® regha e ghino, lo ŇčgaŇčgake na orumburumbunji. Ňägoreiye va ghino ya vakatha valaŇča vakatha thovuye weiye emunjoru e ghemi, ko ghen u dagerawe e ghino noroke tembene u vakatha Ňčgoreiyeva e ghino na vanautumake iya u mebwabwarikewe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya dagerawe Loi e marae.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Amba Eibraham i ghatiwogiya weya Abimeleki mbwarowou regha amalagh…®niye va i t…®gh…®, ko iyemaeŇčge Abimeleki le rakakaiwo th…® wogaith…®ten.
\v 26 Abimeleki i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa ya ghareghare thela i vakatha thanavuna iyana. Ma mbaŇča regha u giya yanawaŇčgu. Ambama iya vara noroke ma loŇčwevaidike.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Iyake kaiwae Eibraham i bigimena sip na kau na i giya weya Abimeleki na mbe thenjighewoko vara th…® vaemunjoruŇča lenji tubweko.
\v 28 Eibraham i ghethevakatha sip nanariye umbopir…® wanakauŇčgi,
\v 29 na kaiwae Abimeleki i vaito Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mo vakatha Ňčgoreiyako?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúU mbana sip…®ke iya umbopir…®ke weŇčgo na i vaemunjoruŇča mbwarowouko iyako ghino va ya do.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Iya kaiwae ghembako iyako idae Beyasiba, kaiwae va gheko giyagiya thenjighewo th…® vakatha lenji tubwekowe.
\p 
\v 32 MbaŇča th…® vakatha lenji tubweko iyako Beyasiba e t…®ne na e ghereiye, Abimeleki weiye Pikol, iye le ragagaith…® lenji randeviva, th…® njogha Pilistiya ghar…®ghar…®niye e lenji ghamba mbaro t…®ne.
\v 33 E ghereinji Eibraham i kabwa umbwa regha idae isel Beyasiba. Na gheko i kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iye Loi Memeghabananiye.
\v 34 Eibraham i yaku Pilistiya e t…®ne mbaŇča molao.
\c 22
\s1 Loi i mandoya Eibraham
\p 
\v 1 Theghathegha umboviye e ghereiye Loi i mandoya Eibraham. I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúEibraham!‚ÄĚ
\p Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe ghinoke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Amba Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčwa naruna, mbereghanaeŇčge, Aisake, iya mbe gharen…®nawe vara, na wein hu wa e val…®vaŇčga idae Moraiya. Vo vowoŇča gheko e ou regha ne ya vatomwe e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča Eibraham kaero i thuweiru, i getha nd…®ghe vowoko kaiwae, i dowe e doŇč…®ki vwata, i vaŇčwa Aisake na le rakakaiwo theghewo weiyaŇčgi. Kaero th…® wareriŇča ghembako iya Loi menda i govatomwekowe.
\v 4 MbaŇča theghetoninji e t…®ne Eibraham i tagath…®na marae kaero i thuwe ouko amba bwagabwaga e ghamwanji.
\v 5 Kaero i dage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwoma iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe hu yaku vara gheke weimi doŇč…®kike na ghinoeŇčge na Aisake vwo voro e ouko, na vwo kururuwe amba wo njoghama e ghemi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Eibraham i th…®na vowoma ghand…®ghe na i th…®n…®rawe Aisake e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le na amalagh…®niye i wo kaina na i yeŇčge nd…®ghe. E lenji loŇčga t…®ne
\v 7 Aisake i vaitoya ramae Eibraham iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe?‚ÄĚ
\p Ramae i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga naruŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p Aisake iŇča, ‚ÄúNd…®ghe und…®und…®ye na nd…®ghe une maiyake, ko naka sip nariye vowoko kaiwae?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi ghamberegha tene i wogiya regha weinda.‚ÄĚ Kaero veth…® loŇčgaloŇčgaova.
\p 
\v 9 MbaŇča veth…® vutha e val…®vaŇčgako iya Loi mendava i vatomwekowe, kaero i vatad ghamba vowoma na i ghara nd…®ghe und…®und…®ye e vwatae. I Ňčgara nariye Aisake gheghe na n…®man…®mae na i wo na i worawe e nd…®ghema vwatae.
\v 10 Eibraham i mwanavaira kainama na i munje i votena nariye nuwae.
\v 11 Ko iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* le nyao thovuye i kulanjamawe e buruburu iŇča, ‚ÄúEibraham! Eibraham!‚ÄĚ \fig I Ňčgara nariye Aisake na i munje i votena nariye nuwae|src="CO00663b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="22:9-10"\fig*
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe ghinoke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 IŇča, ‚ÄúNe u ndevakatha bigi reghawe. MbaŇčake kaero ya ghareghare u yavwatatawana Loi, kaiwae maa mo vaghareghare naruna iya gharen…®nawe e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Eibraham i gh…®mara ghewo i thuwe sip gh…®moru i wona e ghasokisoki. I wa ve wo na i roth…®gha nariye Aisake, i vowo weya Loi.
\v 14 Iya kaiwae Eibraham i rena val…®vaŇčgako iyako ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* Ne i Wogiya.‚ÄĚ Othembe mbaŇčake noroke ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* ele ou vwatae ne i wogiya.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇčaiwoniye \nd Giya Loi\nd* le nyao thovuye mbowo i kulaweva Eibraham e buruburu
\v 16 iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino \nd Giya Loi\nd* ya tholo e idaŇčgu na ya dagerawe e ghen, emunjora ne ghareŇčgu e ghen kaiwae mo vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na maa mo vaghareghare naruna ghamberegha moli.
\v 17 Emunjoru mbene ghareŇčgu vara e ghen, na ne ya vakathaŇčgiya orumburumbu lemoyo moli Ňčgoranjiya gh…®tara e buruburuko na kerakera e njigh…®ko ghadidiye. Orumburumbu ne th…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghanjith…®gh…®yaŇčgi na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghambaghambanji lagh…®lagh…®ye.
\v 18 Orumburumbu weŇčgi ne ya mwaewo weŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye e yambaneke, kaiwae menda u ghambu lo renuwaŇčake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Amba Eibraham na nariye th…® njogha weŇčgiya rakakaiwoma, na th…® rakanjogha na regha Beyasiba na Eibraham mbowo i yaku vara gheko.
\s1 Neiho orumburumbuye
\p 
\v 20 Bigibigiko thiyako e ghereinji amba Eibraham i loŇčwevaidiya ghaghae Neiho na levo Milika mbe th…® ghamb…®va.
\v 21 Uj…® iye vir…® viva, ghaghae Baj…®, Kemuwel (nariya Aram),
\v 22 Keised, Heijo, Pildas, Jidlap na Betuwel,
\v 23 iye Rebeka ramae. Milika va i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruke iya theghewake weiya Neiho Eibraham ghaghae.
\v 24 Neiho le rakakaiwo na levo vaŇčgavaŇčga idae Riyuma vambe i ghamb…®va weiye. Le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Teba, Gaham, Tahas na Maka.
\c 23
\s1 Sera i garalawa utuniye
\p 
\v 1 Sera yawaliye le molamolao theghathegha hothaŇčar…® hoiwo na umbopir…® (127).
\v 2 Va i mare Kiriyat Aba (mbaŇčake th…® uno idae Hebron) Kenan e t…®ne, na Eibraham i nuwathar…® lagh…®ye moli le mareko kaiwae.
\p 
\v 3 Amba Eibraham i roiteta levo riwae na ve thuweŇčgiya Het ghar…®ghar…®niye na iŇča,
\v 4 ‚ÄúBwabwariya ghino ya yaku e t…®nemike. Hu vakuneŇča thelauke vuvura e ghino na mbala ya beku lo wevokowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Het ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča,
\v 6 ‚ÄúAmalana, wo u vandeŇčeime. Wo worawa ghan midi na ghen randeviva vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha. The ghabubu thovuye regha ina gheke u tuthi na u bekwa len wevowe. Maa lolo regha ina gheke ne i vaghareghara le ghabubu e ghen na u bekwa len wevowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Amba Eibraham i yondovir…® na i kururu e maranji,
\v 8 na iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo hu warariŇča ya bekwa lo wevoke e lemi thelauke, ghino e idaŇčgu wo hu utu weimi Eipron Soha nariye, ghino kaiwaŇčgu
\v 9 na mbala i vakuneŇča eŇčge maŇčgavar…® regha e ghino ina Makpela. MaŇčgavar…®ko iyako amalagh…®niyewe ina ele umako mbothiye. ŇägoroŇčga modae, ne ya vamoda Ňčgoreiye na lo ghamba beku kaka e t…®nemike.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 E mbaŇčako iyako Eipron vambe ina gheko weiyaŇčgiya ghauneko i vandeŇče Eibraham le utuko. Giyagiyako wolagh…®ye meth…® rakamenako weiyaŇčgi e ghamba mevathavatha Ňčgora ghamba ruko, e maranji Eipron i thombeya Eibraham le renuwaŇčako iŇča,
\v 11 ‚ÄúAmalana, maa val…®kaiwae mbema ya vatomwe eŇčge maŇčgavar…®, mbema weiye vara thelauna iya inan…®nawe. Wouneke wolagh…®ye e maranji ya vatomwe e ghen na u bekwa len wevowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Eibraham mbowo i kururuva Het ghar…®ghar…®niye e maranji,
\v 13 na i dage weya Eipron gheuneko e maranji iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇčeŇčgo. Mbemane ya vamoda vara thelauko iyako. U wovatha lo renuwaŇčake na mbala ya wo lo wevo na va wobeku gheko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Eipron i gonjoghawe iŇča,
\v 15 ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇčeŇčgo, wo giya lagh…®ye, thelauko modae le ghanaghanagha silva geth…®seriyevar…® (400). Ko buda kaiwae ghen na ghino ra rerenuwaŇča modo kaiwae. U vamodo e ghino na mbema u wa eŇčge na vo bekwa len wevona.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Eibraham i warariŇča iya modoko Eipron me woraŇčgiyako. I wa ve sikeliya silvama geth…®seriyevar…® (400) Ňčgoreiya Eipron me woraŇčgiyama ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e maranji. Th…® sikeli Ňčgoreiya rakunekune na ra vavamodo lenji vakatha e maket.
\p 
\v 17 Iyako ra thuwe va ŇčgoroŇčga na Eipron le thelau weiye maŇčgavar…® na umbwaumbwa nanji e t…®ne ina Makpela, Memri val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro, va i vakuneŇča
\v 18 weya Eibraham na kaero le ghamba mbaro, le ghaval…® Het e maranji iya vath…® raka e ghamba mevathavathako.
\p 
\v 19 Vamodoko e ghereiye, Eibraham i bekwa levo Sera e maŇčgavar…®ko. MaŇčgavar…®ko ina Hebron Kenan e t…®ne Memri val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro.
\v 20 Iyako ra thuwe ŇčgoroŇčga na Eibraham va i wo thelauko iyako weiye maŇčgavar…®ko ina e t…®ne na le ghabubu. Het loloniye i vakuneŇčawe.
\c 24
\s1 Aisake na Rebeka utuninji
\p 
\v 1 Eibraham vama i amalagh…®sar…® moli na \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe weiye vara ele vakatha nasiye na lagh…®ye e t…®ne.
\v 2 MbaŇča regha i dage weya le rakakaiwo, iye val…®ghareghare, e ghayayaoko t…®ne, iŇča, ‚ÄúU lirawa n…®man e vavaŇčguke raberabe.\f + \fr 24:2 \ft ‚ÄúU lirawa n…®man e vavaŇčguke e raberabe.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča vavana vakathake iyake th…® vakatha mbaŇča th…® vakatha tholo.\f*
\v 3 NuwaŇčguiya u tholo na u dagera weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, iye buruburu na yambane ghanji Loi, na mane u vaŇčgwa t…®nan Kenan na naruŇčguke levo.
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge tembene u wa e ghambaŇčgu moli weŇčgiya lo bodaboda na vo vaŇčgwa naruŇčguke Aisake levo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Eibraham le rakakaiwo i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúKo thoŇčgo wevoko maa nuwaiya i njoghama weiŇčgu? Ne ŇčgoroŇčga? Ne ya njoghama na ya vaŇčgwa naruna na ya yovaŇčgu e vanautumako iya u menakowe?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Eibraham i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúU mando na thava u yovaŇčgwa naruŇčguke gheko.
\v 7 \nd Giya Loi\nd* buruburu gha Loi, iye va i vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgo weŇčgiya lo bodaboda na e vanar…®gheŇčgu, amalagh…®niye va i dagerawe e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄėWeŇčgiya orumburumbu ne ya vatomwe val…®vaŇčgake iyake weŇčgi.‚Äô Amalagh…®niye tene i variye le nyao thovuye regha na i viva e ghen, amba ne val…®kaiwae u vaŇčgwa naruŇčguke levo gheko.
\v 8 ThoŇčgo wevoko maa le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye na u njoghamake wein, amba ne len dageraweke weŇčgo mane e gharerenuwaŇča e ghino. Ko iyemaeŇčge ma tembe gharerenuwaŇča na ne u yovaŇčgwa naruŇčguke gheko.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 Ko e mbaŇčako iyako rakakaiwoma i lirawa n…®mae e ghagiyama vavae raberabe, amba i dagerawe na i tholo renuwaŇčako iyako kaiwae.
\p 
\v 10 Kaero rakakaiwoma i vivathaŇčgiya ghagiyama le kamel hoyaworo na i wareri. I mban…®Ňčgiya tomethi bigibigi thovuthovuye weya ghagiyama. I wareriŇča ghembama Neiho i yakumawe, ina Mesopoteimiya e ghaiwabuko.
\v 11 MbaŇča i vutha e ghembama e ghanjimbwa marae, i vakathaŇčgiya kamel…®ko th…® ronja e thelauko vwatae. Iyako vama yegh…®yegh…®ye na wanakau kaero ghanjimbaŇča th…® mena th…® guda mbwa.
\p 
\v 12 Amba i naŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, \nd Giya Loi\nd*, wo giyama Eibraham le Loi, u thalavuŇčgo na noroke ya vamboromboroŇča lo renuwaŇčake na u worawa wo giyako e ghamwan.
\v 13 Kaero u thuweŇčgo ya ndeghath…® e mbwake ghadidiye na gagamaina e ghembako ne th…® mena th…® guda mbwa.
\v 14 MbaŇča ne ya dage weya eunda na yaŇča, ‚ÄėAee, wo u ronja na ya muna ghan mbwana mun,‚Äô na iŇča, ‚ÄėU mena u mun na wo ya vamun…®Ňčgiva len kamel…®na‚Äô ‚ÄĒ mbala ya ghareghare wevoko iyako kaero mendava u tuthi Aisake levo. Iyake ne i vaghareŇčgo emunjoru u worawa wo giyako e ghamwan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Rakakaiwoma vamba i naŇčgonaŇčgo, Rebeka kaero i wovutha ghe mbwa variye. I worawe e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le. Elagh…®niye Betuwel yawarumbuye. Amalake iyake Eibraham ghaghae Neiho nariye weiye Milika.
\v 16 Rebeka iye wevo man…®une eunda na th…®nabwethubwethuru. Va i wa ve guda mbwa e mbwarowouko na kaero i njoghava. \fig Eibraham le rakakaiwo i thuwe Rebeka kaero i wovutha ghe mbwa variye|src="CO00667B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="24:15"\fig*
\p 
\v 17 Eibraham le rakakaiwoma iwaeŇčge i rukureghambawe na iŇča, ‚ÄúU giyama ghan mbwana mun ya mun e ghan mbwana variye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, u mun,‚ÄĚ kaero n…®mae i maya na i th…®n njoŇča e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le, i ndeghath…® na i mun.
\v 19 MbaŇča i mun…®vao kaero Rebeka iŇča, ‚ÄúWo va guduva len kamel…®ke ghanjimbwa na ya vamun…®Ňčgiwe na val…®kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Mbema ghena na n…®maeŇčge kaero i liŇčgimban vuna mbwama thetheghan…®ma e ghanjimbwa ghambae, i rukunjogha e mbwarowouma na mbowo ve guduva kamel…®ko kaiwanji.
\v 21 Amalama mbe i vonjimbughath…® vara le vakathako, na i rerenuwaŇča thoŇčgo emunjora \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vamboromboroŇča le renuwaŇčako.
\p 
\v 22 MbaŇča kamel…®ko kaero th…® munvao, rakakaiwoma kaero i woraŇčgiya gol, mboth…®mboth…® ghaghavatha, le vuyovuyowo grem ghewona, na n…®mae ghaghavatha tembe gol…®va mbambaiwo th…® lagh…®ye na i giyawe.
\v 23 Amba i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThela yawarumbuya ghen? Thare val…®kaiwae ne wo ghena rama e le Ňčgolo gougouke?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe idae Betuwel. Ramaya Neiho na t…®naya Milika.‚ÄĚ
\v 25 Na mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúGhamba ghena i lagh…®ye mbe inawe na thetheghan ghanji mbe inaweva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Amba rakakaiwoma i ronja e gheghe vuvuye na i kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*,
\v 27 iŇča, ‚ÄúTarawa i voro weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*, wo giya Eibraham le Loi. Kaero u vamboromboroŇča len dagerawe na weiye len ghare vatomwe u vamboromboroŇča wo giyako le naŇčgo. Ghino kaiwaŇčgu \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero mo viva e ghino elo loŇčga na u vaŇčgugh…®dagh…®daŇčgo wo giyako le bodaboda weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Rebeka le bodaboda th…® warari Giya Loi le tuthi Rebeka iye Aisake levo
\p 
\v 28 Wevoma i rukunjogha e ghemba na i giya t…®nae le Ňčgoloko gharayakuyaku yanawanji budakai me yomarawe.
\v 29 Rebeka louye idae Leiban. MbaŇča i loŇčwe totoma, i yoruku na ve thuweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ma e mbwako ghadidiye.
\v 30 MbaŇča me thuwe mbothiye ghae na n…®mae ghae e n…®mae na me loŇčwe budaiya louyeko me utuŇča amalako ghal…®Ňčae, i wa weya Eibraham le rakakaiwoko i ndeghath…® kamel…®ko evasiwanji e mbwako ghadidiye,
\v 31 na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena ra wa e ghemba, amalana, ghen \nd Giya Loi\nd* i woraweŇčge e ghamwae. Buda kaiwae mbe u ndendeghath…® vara gheke? Kaero ma vivatharaweya Ňčgolo kaiwami na thetheghan…®na ghambanji.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 MbaŇča veth…® vutha e Ňčgolo amalama na ghaune th…® rakamwand…® e Ňčgolo na Leiban le rakakaiwo th…® biginjoŇča bigibigi kamel…®ko e vwatanji. Th…® giya kamel…®ko ghanji na th…® guda mbwa amaamalama th…® thavwiya ghenjiwe.
\v 33 Kaero th…® bigirawa ghan…®Ňčga e marae, ko iyemaeŇčge Eibraham le rakakaiwoma iŇča, ‚ÄúAmba maa val…®kaiwae ya ghan…®Ňčga. I viva wo ya utuŇča e ghemi budakai kaiwae menda ya menake.‚ÄĚ
\p Leiban i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKo u utugiyama weime len r…®ghena na menda u menakena.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúEibraham le rakakaiwo ghino.
\v 35 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewo lagh…®ye weya wo giyako Eibraham, na kaero i vwenyavwenya lagh…®ye moli. \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha na e le sip, kau, silva na gol lemoyo moli na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva le rakakaiwo gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau na le kamel na doŇč…®ki tembe lemoyova.
\v 36 Wo giyako levo kaero va i elagh…®sar…® ko amba i laghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru weiye na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye kaero i valawayawe.
\v 37 Menda wo giyako i vakathaŇčgo na ya tholo ne ya dagerawe ne ya ghambugha le renuwaŇčako. IŇča, ‚ÄėNe u ndetamwa naruŇčguke levo gheko, Kenan wanakauniyeke e t…®nenji.
\v 38 Ko iyemaeŇčge u njogha weŇčgiya bwebwe na mbe ghino lo bodaboda weŇčgi, na vo vaŇčgwa naruŇčguke levowe.‚Äô
\p 
\v 39 ‚ÄúAmba ya govaito yaŇča, ‚ÄėŇägoroŇčga ne yaŇča thoŇčgo wevoko ne i botewa ya njoghamake weiŇčgu?‚Äô
\p 
\v 40 ‚ÄúI gonjogha e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄėKo iyemaeŇčge \nd Giya Loi\nd* iya ghino mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ya ghambugha le renuwaŇča, tene i variyeya le nyao thovuye na wein na i vakatha len loŇčgana e uneune, na mbala val…®kaiwan u vaŇčgwa wevo eunda e wo uu t…®ne weŇčgiya lo bodaboda.
\v 41 Mbe bigi reghaeŇčge vara ne i vakathaŇčge na u meraŇčgi e len dagerawena iyana e t…®ne. ThoŇčgo u wa weŇčgiya lo bodaboda, na othembe maa th…® vatomwa wevo e ghen na ne u njoghama n…®man…®man wein len tholona ghen kaero u meraŇčgi e gura.‚Äô
\p 
\v 42 ‚ÄúMbaŇča ma vutha e mbwarowouko ghadidiye, ma naŇčgo na yaŇča, ‚ÄėAee, \nd Giya Loi\nd*, wo giyako Eibraham le Loi, thoŇčgo len renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye, u vakatha lo loŇčgake iyake emunjoru na e uneune.
\v 43 Kaero u thuweŇčgo ya ndeghath…® e mbwake iyake ghadidiye, thoŇčgo th…®nabwethubwethuru eunda i mena i guda mbwa na mbaŇča ne ya dagewe na yaŇča, ‚ÄúAee, ya muna ghan mbwana mun,‚ÄĚ
\v 44 na thoŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena u mun na va guda mbwa na ya vamun…®Ňčgiva len kamel…®na,‚ÄĚ u vatomwe e ghino menda va ya tutha elagh…®niye wo giyako Eibraham nariye levo.‚Äô
\p 
\v 45 ‚ÄúAmba muyai ya naŇčgovao e ghareŇčgu, Rebeka i vutha weiye mbwa variye e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le. I wa ve nja e mbwarowouko na ve guda mbwa na ya dagewe yaŇča, ‚ÄėAee, ghan mbwana mun ya mun.‚Äô
\p 
\v 46 ‚ÄúN…®mae i maya i th…®n…®njoŇča e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le na iŇča, ‚ÄėU mun na va vamun…®Ňčgiva len kamel…®ko.‚Äô Kaero ya mun na tembe ve vamun…®Ňčgiva kamel…®ko.
\p 
\v 47 ‚ÄúYa govaito yaŇča, ‚ÄėThela yawarumbuye ghen?‚Äô
\p ‚ÄúIŇča, ‚ÄėBetuwel yawarumbuya ghino, Neiho nariye weiye Milika.‚Äô
\p ‚ÄúAmba ya worawa mbothiye ghae na ya bigirawa n…®mae ghae e n…®man…®mae,
\v 48 amba ya ronja e ghegheŇčgu vuvuye na ya kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*. E mbaŇčako iyako ya taraweŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd*, wo giya Eibraham le Loi, kaiwae menda i vaŇčgugh…®dagh…®daŇčgo weya wo giyako ghaghae ghambae, na e gheuu t…®ne ya vaŇčgwa nariyeko levowe.
\v 49 E mbaŇčake iyake thoŇčgo emunjoru gharen i nja weya wo giyako, u utugiyama e ghino; thoŇčgo nandere, tembe u utu giyamava e ghino mbala elo ghareghare na ya vakatha budakai na ya njogha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 50 Leiban na Betuwel th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* menda i vakatha renuwaŇča iyana e ghen. Ma val…®kaiwame tembe wo utuŇčava bigi regha e ghen.
\v 51 Rebeka mbe iya. U vaŇčgu na wein hu wa, kaero wo vatomwe na ve vaŇčgwa ghan giyana nariye, Ňčgoreiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* le renuwaŇčana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 52 MbaŇča Eibraham le rakakaiwo i loŇčwe lenji renuwaŇčako i ronja e thelau vwatae na i vata ago weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.
\v 53 Amba rakakaiwoma i bigiraŇčgiya gol, silva, na kwamakwama na i giya weya Rebeka, na tembe i giyava bigibigi thovuthovuye weŇčgiya Rebeka louye na t…®nae.
\v 54 Ko amba Eibraham le rakakaiwoma na vavanava mendava weiyaŇčgima, thiya ghan…®Ňčga na th…® ghena gheko gougouko iyako.
\p MbaŇčambaŇčavena th…® thuweiru, kaero i dage weŇčgiya wevoko le bodaboda iŇča, ‚ÄúHu variyeime ma wo njoghava wo giyamawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 55 Ko Rebeka louye na t…®nae th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbala wo layaku weime gheneyaworo na e ghereiye, ko amba wein hu wa.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 56 Ko iyemaeŇčge i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava tembe hu laweghath…®imeva. Kaero \nd Giya Loi\nd* menda i vamboromboroŇča lo loŇčgake. Mbema hu viyathuŇčgo eŇčge na ya njogha weya wo giyako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 57 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo ra kulawe na ra vaito ŇčgoroŇčga elagh…®niye le renuwaŇča.‚ÄĚ
\v 58 Iya kaiwae th…® kulawe na th…® vaito th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare nuwaniya wein amalake iyake?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLo renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 59 Kaero le bodaboda th…® variyeyathu Rebeka weiye gharanjimbunjimbu eunda weinji Eibraham le rakakaiwo na ghaune vavanava, th…® rakanjogha Kenan.
\v 60 Th…® giya Rebeka ghadagemwaewo th…®Ňča,
\q1 ‚ÄúGhen, loume, nevole ghar…®ghar…® mbunja
\q2 ghalaghalamaŇčgo lenji elagh…® ghen!
\q1 Ghen orumburumbu nevole
\q2 th…® kivwalaŇčgiya ghanjith…®gh…®yaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 61 Rebeka na le rakakaiwo wanakau th…® tha e lenji kamel, kaero th…® wareri weinji Eibraham le rakakaiwo.
\p 
\v 62 Aisake va i ri Beya Lahai Roi\f + \fr 24:62 \ft Beya Lahai Roi gharumwaru ‚ÄúMbwako iyava Loi Yawayawaliye i thuweŇčgowe.‚ÄĚ\f* na mbaŇčako iyako i yaku Keinan e yaghalaniyeko e val…®vaŇčga idae Negev.
\v 63 Yegh…®yegh…®ye regha i raŇčgi na mbe i loŇčga weiye le rerenuwaŇča, na mbaŇča i tagath…®na marae, i thuweŇčgiya kamel, amba inanji bwagabwaga, th…® loŇčga gh…®dagh…®da.
\v 64 MbaŇča Rebeka i thuwe Aisake, mbema ghe na n…®maeŇčge, i nja ele kamel…®ma,
\v 65 na i vaitoya Eibraham le rakakaiwoma iŇča, ‚ÄúThela iya amalake iya i loŇčgagh…®dagh…®daindake?‚ÄĚ
\p Rakakaiwoma i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGiyama ya kaiwomawe.‚ÄĚ Rebeka i liya umbaliye ghayaboyabo na i yabo vulula ghamwae.
\p 
\v 66 Rakakaiwoma kaero i utuŇča bigibigi wolagh…®ye weya Aisake mendava th…® yomarawe ele loŇčgako t…®ne.
\v 67 Aisake i vaŇčgwa Rebeka na i vaŇčguruwo t…®nae Sera va ele yoŇčathowathowa t…®ne. Kaero i vaŇčgu na levo na vambe i gharethovuwe vara, ko ambama Aisake ghare i dinja t…®nae le mare na ghanuwathar…® kaiwae.
\c 25
\s1 Eibraham i vaŇčgwa Ketura
\p 
\v 1 Eibraham mbowo i vaŇčguva wevo eunda na levo, idae Ketura.
\v 2 I ghamb…® weiye Eibraham na le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Jimran, Joksan, Medan, Midiyan, Is…®bak na Sua.
\v 3 Joksan le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Siba na Didan. Didan orumburumbuyeŇčgiya Asur ghar…®ghar…®niye, Letus ghar…®ghar…®niye na Leyum ghar…®ghar…®niye.
\v 4 Midiyan le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya Epa, Ipa, Hanok, Abida na Elda. Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake Ketura orumburumbuyeŇčgi.
\p 
\v 5 Eibraham i valawe ghayayaoko lagh…®ye weya nariye Aisake.
\v 6 Eibraham vambe elaghalagha i giyava Sera ghaemaruwoŇčgiko lenji ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru ghanjimwaewo, na i variyeyathuŇčgi na th…® wa e boimako veth…® yakuwe na thava th…® yaku na regha weinji nariye Aisake.
\s1 Eibraham le mare utuutuniye
\p 
\v 7 Eibraham yawaliye va i molao. Ghatheghathegha vama i wo hothaŇčar…® hwepir…® na umbolima (175) amba i rumbo vuna ghand…®ghe.
\v 8 Vama i amalagh…®sar…® moli, amba i garalawa, Ňčgoreiye eŇčge orumburumbuyeko.
\v 9 Aisake na ghaghae Ismel th…® bekwa ramanji Eibraham e maŇčgavar…®ma Makpela e t…®ne, Memri ghadidiye. MaŇčgavar…®ko iyako ina e thelau regha Eibraham va i vamodo weya rara Het idae Eipron, Joha nariye.
\v 10 Eibraham vambe i bekwa levo Sera iya e maŇčgavar…®ko iyako.
\v 11 Eibraham le mare e ghereiye, Loi va i mwaewowe nariye Aisake. Na Aisake va i wa na ve yaku Beya Lahai Roi evasiwae.
\s1 Ismel orumburumbuye
\p 
\v 12 Iyake Eibraham nariye Ismel utuutuniye. Va i ghamb…® weiye Heiga t…®nan Ijipt, elagh…®niye Sera le rakakaiwobwaga.
\b
\p 
\v 13 Ismel le ŇčgaŇčga iya idaidanjiyake: Nebaiyot, iye vir…®viva, Keda, Ad…®bil, Mib…®sam,
\v 14 Mis…®ma, Dama, Mesa,
\v 15 Haded, Tema, Jetur…®, Nepis na Kedema.
\v 16 Wabwi theyaworo na theghewo orumburumbunjiŇčgiya thiyake, na idaidanji te vambe th…® ren…®va ghambaghambanjiko na lenji kiyamuŇčgi.
\v 17 Ismel yawaliye le molamolao theghathegha hothaŇčar…®, hweto na umbopir…® (137); ko amba i rumbo vuna ghand…®ghe, Ňčgoreiye eŇčge orumburumbuyeko.
\v 18 Orumburumbuye va th…® yaku Havila na Sur e ghanjilughawoghawo, Ijipt val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro e boimako, i ghembeghembe Asiriya. Mava th…® yaku na ghamwanji vanaora weinjiyaŇčgiya Eibraham orumburumbuye vavanava.
\s1 Iso na Jeikob lenji vir…® utuniye
\p 
\v 19 Utuutuke iyake Eibraham nariya Aisake utuniye.
\b
\p 
\v 20 Aisake ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwevar…® amba i ghe weiye Rebeka wevoko iyako Betuwel (rara Aram, Mesopoteimiya e t…®ne) yawarumbuye, na elagh…®niye Leiban louye.
\p 
\v 21 Kaiwae Rebeka va i kwama, le gh…®moru Aisake i naŇčgo weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* kaiwae. \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i vamboromboro le naŇčgoko na kaero i th…®n.
\v 22 Kaiwae va gamwaruwoŇčgi, gamagaiko th…® vevovewoŇčgi e Ňčgamoiye, iya kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, buda kaiwae gamagaike th…® vakatha kamwath…®ke iyake e ghino?‚ÄĚ IwaeŇčge ve tamweya gharumwaru weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*.
\p 
\v 23 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i dagewe iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúVanautuma theghewo inanji e Ňčgamoin…®na,
\q2 ghar…®ghar…®na theghewona ne u ghamb…®Ňčgi ne wabwi theghewoŇčgi
\q1 Nasiyeniyena le vur…®gheghe ne i kivwala lagh…®yeniyena,
\q2 Vir…®vivana ne i kaiwo weya vir…® reghambana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 MbaŇča Ňčgamoiye i njivun kaero i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamwaruworuwo gh…®mogh…®moruŇčgi.
\v 25 Vir…®viva va waranjaghanjagha na riwae vulivuliye Ňčgoreiya kwama udauda, iya kaiwae th…® rena idae Iso.\f + \fr 25:25 \ft Mbwata Iso gharumwaru ‚Äúriwae vulivuliye‚ÄĚ. Iso ida regha Idom, iya gharumwaru ‚Äúsosoro‚ÄĚ.\f*
\v 26 Theghewoniye i vir…®, ko iyemaeŇčge vambe i vinjimb…® vara vir…® vivako ghe daŇčavwa, iya kaiwae th…® rena idae Jeikob.\f + \fr 25:26 \ft Idake Jeikob ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiye ‚Äúghe daŇčavwa‚ÄĚ na tembe gharumwaruva ‚Äúrakwan‚ÄĚ.\f* Aisake ghatheghathegha vama i wo hwewona (60) na mbaŇča Rebeka i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagaiko theghewoko.
\p 
\v 27 Gamagaiko th…® tabo na kaero bobomaŇčgi, Iso iye ra wowoidi thovuye na masemburu na nuwanuwa woidi. Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob iye va riwouda na vambe rara vara thotho.
\v 28 Aisake va i gharethovu weya Iso, kaiwae nuwae va i ghaŇčgo weya thetheghan…®ko va ve gabogaboko, ko Rebeka va i gharethovu weya Jeikob.
\p 
\v 29 MbaŇča regha Jeikob vama i gaga ghileghilema na Iso ghe mbaŇča vara i vuthawe, i mena e njamnjam. Ghare vama i basi.
\v 30 I dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúN…®man i maya na u giyama bigina sosorona seiwo ya ghan.‚ÄĚ (Iya kaiwae va th…® rena idae Idom.) \fig ‚ÄúN…®man i maya na u giyama bigina sosorona seiwo ya ghan.‚ÄĚ|src="CO00674B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="25:30"\fig*
\p 
\v 31 Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya giya e ghen, thoŇčgo u vatomwa vir…®vivana ghe mbaro e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Iso iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u thuweŇčgo? MbaŇča nasiye ya marenjaŇčgu. Vir…® viva ghe mbaro ne i woveŇčgwa budakai?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúI viva wo u tholo na u dagerawe emunjoru ne u vatomwe vir…®vivana ghe mbaro e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p Iso kaero i tholo na i vatomwa vir…® vivama ghe mbaro weya Jeikob.
\v 34 Amba Jeikob i giya bred na ghileghilema weya Iso. I ghan…®Ňčga na i muna mbwa, ko amba i yondovir…® na i wa.
\p Iso mava i goru weya vir…® viva ghambaro.
\c 26
\s1 Aisake i yaku Gera
\p 
\v 1 Va e mbaŇčako iyako vunuvu regha i yomarava e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Eibraham va ghe mbaŇča. Aisake i wa weya Abimeleki, Pilistiya lenji kiŇč, Gera e t…®ne.
\v 2 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i yomara weya Aisake na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe u ndewa Ijipt; mbe u yaku vara e val…®vaŇčgana iyana e t…®ne Ňčgoreiya ya dagena e ghen.
\v 3 Mbe u yaku vara gheke na ghino mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen na ne ya mwaewo e ghen. Iya thivathivake iyake ne ya wogiya e ghen na orumburumbu weŇčgi. Ne ya vamboromboroŇča dagerawe va ya utura weya rama Eibraham.
\v 4 Nevole ya giya e ghen orumburumbu lemoyo, lemoyo moli, Ňčgoranjiya gh…®tara e buruburuko, na ne ya giya val…®vaŇčgake lagh…®ye iyake weŇčgi. Orumburumbu weŇčgi vanautumake wolagh…®ye ne th…® naŇčgo e ghino na ya mwaewo weŇčgi.
\v 5 Ne ya mwaewo e ghemi, kaiwae Eibraham va i ghambuŇčgo na i njimbukikiya lo mbaro na budakaiya va ya utu giyawe.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 Iya kaiwae Aisake va i yaku Gera.
\p 
\v 7 MbaŇča gh…®mogh…®moru e ghembako iyako th…® vaito levoko kaiwae, i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúElake iyake, iye louŇčgu.‚ÄĚ Ma val…®kaiwae va iŇča levo kaiwae va i mararu, ne iwaeŇčge gh…®mogh…®moru e ghembako iyako th…® un…®gha amalagh…®niye na th…® vaŇčgwa Rebeka. Elagh…®niye va wevo man…®une eunda.
\p 
\v 8 Aisake vama i yaku gheko mbaŇča molao, na mbaŇča regha KiŇč Abimeleki i gh…®maranja ele dedele amba i gh…®maralambo Aisake na Rebeka th…® vevanyamonaŇčgi.
\v 9 IwaeŇčge Abimeleki i kularuwo Aisake na iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mbema len wevo iyana! Buda kaiwae moŇčake loun?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMe lo renuwaŇča yaŇča mbwata hu un…®gh…®Ňčgo, thoŇčgo yaŇča lo wevo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 KiŇč Abimeleki i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMo vakatha budakai weime? ThoŇčgo gh…®moruke regha me ghena weiye len wevona, ghime mbala wo monjina lagh…®ye, ko lama vakatha vathar…®ke mbe r…®ghe vara ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Amba Abimeleki i th…®n…®vathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúThe lolothan i vakatha vathar…® weya amalake iyake o weya levoke, loloko iyako ne kaka.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Aisake i kaiwo gheko na i kabu umauma, na e theghatheghako iyako i uloulo na i vatha ghan…®Ňčga lemoya, lemoya moli, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* va i mwaewowe.
\v 13 Aisake i mban…®vathavathaŇčgiya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye na e le vakathako iyako ma i vwenyevwenye lagh…®ye moli.
\v 14 Kaiwae va e le sip, gout na kau lemoyo na le rakakaiwo lemoyo, Pilistiya ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yamwanja kaiwae.
\v 15 Iya kaiwae th…® t…®gh…® tomuŇčgiya mbwako wolagh…®ye ramae Eibraham vamba e yawayawaliye na le rakakaiwo th…® doŇčgi.
\p 
\v 16 IwaeŇčge Abimeleki i dage weya Aisake iŇča, ‚ÄúU iteteime! Kaero len bigibigi na len rakakaiwo lemoyo moli, na kaero u lagh…®ye kivwalaime.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Iya kaiwae Aisake i wareri na ve vakatha le ghamba yaku e malamo idae Gera, na mbowo i yaku gheko mbaŇča ubotu.
\v 18 Le rakakaiwo mbowo th…® t…®gh…® vair…®Ňčgiva, mbwaŇčgima ramae va i t…®gh…®Ňčgima vamba e yawayawaliyema na Pilistiya ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® t…®gh…® tomuŇčgima, mbaŇča Eibraham va i mare na e ghereiye. Aisake te vambe i ren…®va idanjiko iya ramae va i ren…®Ňčgiko.
\p 
\v 19 Aisake le rakakaiwo th…® t…®gha doda regha e malamoko iyako t…®ne na th…® t…®gh…® vaidiya mbwa.
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge sip gharanjimbunjimbuŇčgi Gera e t…®ne th…® wogaith…® weinjiyaŇčgiya Aisake le sip gharanjimbunjimbuŇčgi na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwake iyake ghimewe.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae Aisake i rena mbwako idae Esek, gharumwaru ‚ÄúWogaith…®‚ÄĚ.
\v 21 Aisake le rakakaiwo mbowo th…® t…®gh…®va regha, na mbowo th…® wogaith…®va kaiwae, iya kaiwae i ren idae Sitna, gharumwaru ‚ÄúTh…®gh…®ya‚ÄĚ.
\v 22 I roiteta iyako na mbowo i dova regha. Iyako mava e utuutuniye, iya kaiwae i ren idae Rehobot, gharumwaru ‚ÄúVanathero‚ÄĚ. IŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake iyake, \nd Giya Loi\nd* le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye na ne ra yaku e vanatheroke iyake, na ne ra madi moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 MbaŇča gheviyeŇčge e ghereiye Aisake i iteta val…®vaŇčgako iyako na kaero i wa Beyasiba.
\v 24 Gougouko iyako \nd Giya Loi\nd* i yomarawe na iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino rama Eibraham le Loi, iya va i kururuwe. Tha u mararu bigi regha, ghino mbe weiŇčgu vara ghen. Ne ya mwaewo e ghen na ya vakathaŇčgi orumburumbu lemoyo moli kaiwae kaero va ya dagera weya lo rakakaiwo Eibraham.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Iya kaiwae Aisake i vatada ghamba vowo gheko na i kururu weya \nd Giya Loi\nd*. Amba th…® vatadaŇčgi yoŇčathowathowa gheko, na le rakakaiwo th…® t…®gha mbwa regha gheko.
\s1 Aisake na Abimeleki th…® vetubwe weŇčgi
\p 
\v 26 MbaŇča th…® t…®gha mbwako, Abimeleki va i ri Gera weiye Ahusat, gharavanuwov…®r…® na Pikol, iye ragagaith…® lenji randeviva, th…® mena weya Aisake.
\v 27 Aisake i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mohu mena hu thuweŇčgo, kaerova hu botewoŇčgo, na hu vakathaŇčgo ya iteta lemi vanautumana?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake kaero wo ghareghare ghen wein \nd Giya Loi\nd*, na wo renuwaŇča val…®kaiwae ra vatad…® la renuwaŇča regha e ghanda lughawoghawoke. Nuwameiya u dagera weime,
\v 29 maa val…®kaiwae ne hu gaith…® wanaime. Ghime va ghareme e ghemi iya kaiwae va wo variyeyathuŇčga na hu wareri e numomal…®l…® t…®ne. Noroke kaero i manjamanjala weime, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewo na ghare e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30 Aisake i vakatha thaga lagh…®ye regha kaiwanji, na thiya ghan…®Ňčga na th…® munumu.
\v 31 Vambe mbaŇčambaŇča kaero regha iya i vakatha le dagerawe na i tholo. Aisake i ghaoleŇčgi na kaero th…® tabo na le v…®ghath…®Ňčgi.
\p 
\v 32 E mbaŇčako iyako Aisake le rakakaiwo, th…® rakamena na th…® utugiya mbwama meth…® doma utuniyewe. Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKaero mwo vaidiya mbwa.‚ÄĚ
\v 33 I rena mbwako iyako idae Siba, gharumwaru ‚ÄúTholo‚ÄĚ. Iya kaiwae ghaghad…® noroke ghembako ina e mbwako ghadidiyeko idae Beyasiba.\f + \fr 26:33 \ft Beyasiba gharumwaru ‚Äúmbwarowou iya va th…® tholokowe‚ÄĚ.\f*
\s1 Iso le ovo th…® mena mbe e vanautuma reghava
\p 
\v 34 MbaŇča Iso ghatheghathegha vama i wo ghwevar…®, i vaŇčguŇčgi Het wanakauniye theunyiwo ‚ÄĒ Judit, elagh…®niye Biri yawarumbuye, na Basimata, Elon yawarumbuye.
\v 35 Va th…® vakathaŇčgi Aisake na Rebeka maa th…® ndewarariŇčaŇčgi mun.
\c 27
\s1 Jeikob i wo Aisake le mwaewo kwan e t…®ne
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Aisake vama i amalagh…®sar…® na maramarae kaero th…® thar…® na maa val…®kaiwae i thuwe na thovuye, i variye utu weya nariye Iso we, iye vir…® viva, na i menawe, amba i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe ghinoke, bwebwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Ramae Aisake i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇčeŇčgo, kaero ya amalagh…®sar…® na lo mare maa i bwagabwaga.
\v 3 Iyake kaiwae, u wo len mbwenarana, u wa e njamnjam vo woidi na u un…®gha thetheghan regha kaiwaŇčgu.
\v 4 MbaŇča ne u wovutha, u vakatha ghan…®Ňčga thovuye regha kaiwaŇčgu, iya vara nuwaŇčguke nuwaiya moli, u th…®n…®mena e ghino na ya ghan. Ghan…®Ňčga ne ghereiye amba ya giya ghan…®mwaewona, ko amba muyai ya mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 MbaŇča Aisake i utuutu weya Iso, Rebeka mbe i ndevandeŇče eŇčge. MbaŇča Iso kaero i wareri kaiwae na e ghereiye,
\v 6 amba Rebeka i dage weya nariye Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u vandeŇčeŇčgo! Ma loŇčwevaidiya rama Aisake i utu weya ghagha Iso,
\v 7 meŇča, ‚ÄėVo un…®gha thetheghan regha e njamnjam, u vivatha ghan…®Ňčga thovuye regha kaiwaŇčgu na ya ghan, na e ghereiye \nd Giya Loi\nd* e marae, amba ya giya ghan…®mwaewona, ko amba muyai ne ya mare.‚Äô
\v 8 Iya kaiwae, naruŇčgu, u vandeŇče ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke na u vakatha Ňčgoreiya ya utuŇčake e ghen.
\v 9 U wa weŇčgiya la thetheghan…®ko na vo tuthiya gout tabwagha umboiwo, ghanjitabo vond…®vond…®. U bigi mena na ya vivatha ghan…®Ňčga thovuye regha, iya vara rama nuwaiyako moli.
\v 10 Mbala u yoth…®n weya rama na ve ghan, na e ghereiye, amba i giya ghan…®mwaewo, ko amba muyai ne i mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob i dage weya t…®nae Rebeka iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u ghareghare Iso iye riwae vata vulivuliye na ghino njimwaŇčguke i udauda.
\v 12 Mbwata ne bwebwe i vinoya riwaŇčguke na i ghareghare ya vakatha kwan…®we, iwaeŇčge tembe wombereghakeva ya womena wo gura na maa wo dagemwaewova.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 T…®nae i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, gurana iyana ne i nja e ghino, mbema u wa eŇčge na vo vakatha Ňčgoreiya maŇčama na u bigimena gout…®ko e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Ko amba Jeikob i wa, ve gaboŇčgiya gout…®ma, i bigimena weya t…®nae na i vakatha ghan…®Ňčgama iya ramae Aisake nuwaiyama moli.
\v 15 Amba Rebeka i mbana nariye lagh…®yeniye, Iso, ghaghavatha kwamaniye thovuthovuye moli vambe i mban…®rawe wagiyawe e Ňčgoloko t…®ne na i vanjimbo nariye nasiyeniye, Jeikob we.
\v 16 I bigiya gout…®ma njimwanji na i bigirawe Jeikob e n…®man…®mae na e numwe r…®ghe Ňčgoreiya ma vulivuliye i mbuthuwe.
\v 17 Kaero i th…®n…®giya ghan…®Ňčgama gham…®naema thovuye weiye bred, iya me vakathama Jeikob we.
\p 
\v 18 Jeikob kaero i wa ve ru weya ramae. I vutha iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe.‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga, na thela ghen naruŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino narun lagh…®yeniye Iso. Kaero ma vakatha Ňčgoreiya mo dagema e ghino. Ya naŇčgo e ghen u thuweiru na u yaku na u ghan…®Ňčga. U ghana thetheghan…®ma ma un…®gh…®ma mbun…®maniye, na mbala u giya womwaewona e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Ko iyemaeŇčge Aisake i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, me ŇčgoroŇčga na mbema ghen na n…®man eŇčge kaero u vaidiva thetheghan…®ko?‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* len Loi me thalavuŇčgo na ma vaidi iya ma maya e njoghamake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Aisake i dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúYa naŇčgo e ghen na wo u romena evasiwaŇčguke, na ya v…®ghath…®gha riwan…®na na val…®kaiwae ya ghareghare mbema emunjora Iso ghen.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 Jeikob i rotha amba ramae i bigirawe n…®man…®mae e riwae, i vino Ňčgolouya na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhal…®Ňčan…®na ghaloŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiya Jeikob, ko iyemaeŇčge n…®man…®man…®ke gham…®nae Ňčgoreiya Iso.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 Mava i ghareghare Jeikob iya amalagh…®niyeko, kaiwae n…®man…®maeko vata vulivuliye Ňčgoreiya Iso. Vama i munje ma i giya vara ghamwaewo,
\v 24 ko injana mbowo i vaitova iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjora Iso iya ghenake?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKo mbwana!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Aisake i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u th…®n…®ma ghan…®Ňčgama na wo ya ghan, ko amba muyai ya giya ghan mwaewo.‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i th…®n…®giyawe, na tembe i giyaweva waen na i mun.
\v 26 Amba ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, u romena e ghad…®d…®Ňčguke moli na u vandamoŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 MbaŇča i romena evasiwae na i vandamo, ramae Aisake i naeya ghakwamako butiye, amba i giya ghamwaewo iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúNaruŇčguke butiye thovuye Ňčgoreiya thelau regha
\q2 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha na veimaima na ndendewo.
\q1 
\v 28 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na ne i vakatha udubuya\f + \fr 27:28 \ft Idae reghava ‚Äúwayao‚ÄĚ.\f*
\q2 i njama e buruburu na i vakatha len umauma
\q2 th…® rau e ghan…®Ňčga thaŇčar…®ke, thovuthovuye na lemoyo moli;
\q2 na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva lemoyo wit na waen.
\q1 
\v 29 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na ne i vakatha vanautuma
\q2 vavana th…® kaiwo e ghen
\q2 na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva weŇčgiya orumburumbu ne muyaiko,
\q2 na ya naŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® vavana nevole th…® yavwatata wanaŇčge.
\q1 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na nevole
\q2 u tabo na giya weŇčgiya len bodaboda,
\q1 na t…®na le bodaboda
\q2 nevole th…® yavwatata wanaŇčge.
\q1 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na thavala nevole
\q2 th…® guraŇčge ne th…® vaidiya guraniye,
\q1 na thavala nevole th…® varemoliyaŇčge
\q2 ne th…® vaidiya ghanjithovuye.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Iso i naŇčgo weya Aisake na i giya ghamwaewo
\p 
\v 30 Aisake amba i giyavaoeŇčge nariye Jeikob ghamwaewo, na mbaŇčaniye amba i itete eŇčge ramae, ghaghae Iso kaero ve rovuthaweva ramanji, i njoghama e woidi r…®ghe.
\v 31 Tembe me vivathava ghan…®Ňčga gham…®nae thovuye moli na i th…®n…®mena weya ramae. I ronja evasiwae na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa naŇčgo e ghen, bwebwe, u thuweiru na u ghana ghan…®Ňčgake iya ma vakathake na ya th…®n…®menake e ghen, na mbala u giyama womwaewona.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Aisake i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúKo thela ghen?‚ÄĚ
\p IŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Iso, narun vir…®viva.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 MbaŇča Aisake i loŇčwetuthiya Iso ghal…®Ňčaeko, ghare i tagath…®n na riwaeko lagh…®ye i tage na i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúKo thelaeŇčge iya me un…®gha thetheghan…®ke na iya me th…®n…®menake e ghino? Amba ma ghan…®vao eŇčge ma iyava u yovuthake. Kaero ma giya mwaewo moumouniyewe, na maa val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya wov…®v…®. Emunjoru \nd Giya Loi\nd* ne i mwaewowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 MbaŇča Iso i loŇčwa utuutuko iyako weya ramae, i randa na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye moli weiye le gharev…®r…® lagh…®ye na i dage weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe, mbowo u giyamava iya mwaewona iyana e ghino!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 35 Aisake i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhagha Jeikob me mena na i yaroŇčgo. Kaero me mban…®vao ghan mwaewoma.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 Iso iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero mbaŇčaiwoniye vara iyake. Va i yaroŇčgokai na i wo weŇčgo vir…®vivake ghino lo ghamba ndeghath…®. I thovuye moli eŇčge idako Jeikob\f + \fr 27:36 \ft Jeikob gharumwaru ‚Äúrakwan‚ÄĚ.\f* inawe. Wo u thuwe mbaŇčake kaero me wo weŇčgova wo mwaewoma. Thare mo goworawa mwaewo regha ghino kaiwaŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Aisake i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ma vakatha na iye ne ghan giya, na le bodabodako wolagh…®ye le rakakaiwo. Kaero maŇča le umauma wit na waen ne veimaima na ndendewo. Ko tene ya utuŇčava budakai e ghen, naruŇčgu?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 38 Iso mbe i rorovur…®gheghe vara weya ramae: ‚ÄúThare mwaewo reghava mbe inawe kaiwaŇčgu, bwebwe? Mbowo u giyamava wo mwaewo, bwebwe!‚ÄĚ Injana mbowo i randava ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye.
\p 
\v 39 Amba Aisake i dagewe iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúMane udubuya i njama e buruburu kaiwan.
\q2 Mane thelau veimaima na ndendewo kaiwan.
\q1 
\v 40 Yawalin na len yakuyaku ghathovuye
\q2 mbene inavara e len gaith…®na ghaghalith…®.
\q2 Nevole ghaghako le rakakaiwo ghen.
\q1 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ne u goriwoyathu,
\q2 kaero u goghale le mbaro ghaghambu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 41 Iso i botewoyatho ghaghae Jeikob kaiwae ramanji kaerova i giya gha mwaewowe, iya kaiwae i renuwaŇča thuwole e ghare na iŇča, ‚ÄúRamanda le mare na nuwothar…®niye gha mbaŇča e ghereiye amba ya un…®gh…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 42 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča Rebeka i loŇčwevaidiya Iso le renuwaŇčako, i kulavatha Jeikob na iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčgu, u th…®na thegheniŇčguke. Ghagha Iso i rerenuwaŇča kaiwan na i munjeva ne i liya thoru e ghen.
\v 43 Iya kaiwae, naruŇčgu, u loŇčweghath…®gha ghal…®ŇčaŇčguke, na e mbaŇčake vara iyake u vogha na u wa weya louŇčgu Leiban, len ghai, Haran e t…®ne.
\v 44 Mbowo vo yaku gheko gheghad ghagha le ghatemuruko i morurunja,
\v 45 na i renuwaŇča vaghalaweya budakai va u vakathawe, ko amba ya variye lolo regha i ghaona i vaŇčgunjoghaŇčge. ŇägoroŇčga yawaliŇčguke ne ghathovuye thoŇčgo ya th…®vaiŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčgake mbe thenjighewoke vara e mbaŇča regha?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 46 Rebeka i dage weya Aisake iŇča, ‚ÄúRiwaŇčguke kaero i banewaŇčgiya Iso le ovoŇčgike. Thiye mbe vanautuma regha wanakauniyeŇčgi. ThoŇčgo Jeikob i vaŇčgwa Het wevoniye eunda, yawaliŇčguke ŇčgoroŇčga ne ghathovuye e ghino?‚ÄĚ
\c 28
\p 
\v 1 Aisake i kula weya Jeikob na i varemoliya na i dage vur…®gheghewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúNe u ndevaŇčgwa wevo eunda e val…®vaŇčgake iyake, Kenan e t…®ne.
\v 2 MbaŇčake vara u wareri na u wa Padan Aram. U wa weya rumbu Betuwel, na vo vaŇčgwa wevo eunda gheko, len ghai Leiban yawarumbuye eunda.
\v 3 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye na ne i mwaewowe len ghena, na i vakatha len ŇčgaŇčga lemoyo, na mbala u tabo na vanautuma lemoyo rumbunji.
\v 4 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na ne i dage mwaewo e ghen na weŇčgiya orumburumbu muyaiko Ňčgoreiya va i vakatha weya Eibraham. Mbala u mbaroŇča val…®vaŇčgake iyake, iya kaero u mebwabwarikewe. Loi kaerova i vatomwe weya Eibraham.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 Kaero Aisake i variye Jeikob na i wa Padan Aram, i wa weya Leiban, Betuwel nariye. Amalake iyake iye rara Aram na Rebeka louye, Jeikob na Iso t…®nanji.
\s1 Iso mbowo i vaŇčguva levo eunda
\p 
\v 6 Iso i loŇčwevaidiya Aisake kaerova i giya Jeikob ghamwaewo na i variye i wa Padan Aram na ve tamweya levowe. Na tembe i loŇčwevaidiva, mbaŇča Aisake i giya ghamwaewo, i dageten…®we na thava ne i vaŇčgwa t…®nan Kenan eunda na levo.
\v 7 Tevambe i loŇčwevaidiva, Jeikob i ghambugha t…®nae na ramae na kaerova i wareri, i wa Padan Aram.
\v 8 Iso va i ghareghare ramae Aisake mava le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya Kenan wanakauniye.
\v 9 Iya kaiwae i wa weya Ismel, Eibraham nariye, na mbowo ve vaŇčguva yawarumbuye idae Mahalat, Nebaiyot louye.
\s1 Jeikob i ghenelolo Betel e t…®ne
\p 
\v 10 Jeikob i iteta Beyasiba na kaero i loŇčgaloŇčgava Haran kaiwae.
\v 11 Vama i vutha e val…®vaŇčga regha, na varae vama ve ronja, iya kaiwae wo i laghena gheko. I wo eŇčge var…® regha na umbaliye gha bubuthe kaero i ghena.
\v 12 Gougouko iyako i ghenelolowa Ňčende regha i ndeghath…® e yambaneke, i tubwembele na ve wo buruburuko, na Loi le nyao thovuthovuye th…® rakarakavoro na th…® rakarakanjawe.
\v 13 Amba i vaidiya \nd Giya Loi\nd* i ndeghath…® e vwatae na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino \nd Giya Loi\nd*, Eibraham na Aisake lenji Loi. Thelauke iya u ghenakewe ne ya wogiya e ghen na orumburumbu tha muyaiko.
\v 14 Nevole lemoyo moliŇčgi Ňčgoranjiya yambaneke vughauye. Lenji ghamba mbaroke nevole th…® valagh…®yeŇča, i njaoko, i vorowoko, e ghaiwabuko na e yaghalako. Weya ghen na orumburumbu weŇčgi, ne ya mwaewo weŇčgiya vanautumake wolagh…®ye.
\v 15 Na u renuwaŇčakiki, ghino mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye. Ne ya njimbukikiŇčge e the val…®vaŇčga ne u wawe, tembene ya vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgeva e val…®vaŇčgake iyake. Mane mbaŇča regha ya roiteteŇčge na ne ya vakatha Ňčgoreiye budakai va ya dagerawe e ghen.‚ÄĚ \fig Loi le nyao thovuthovuye th…® rakarakavoro na th…® rakarakanjawe|src="CO00683b.tif" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="28:12"\fig*
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča Jeikob i thuweiru, amba iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru \nd Giya Loi\nd* ina gheke. Ina e val…®vaŇčgake iyake, ko iyemaeŇčge ghino maa ma ghareghare!‚ÄĚ
\v 17 Va weiye le mararu na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru val…®vaŇčgake iyake maramararuwae! Val…®vaŇčgake iyake Loi le ghamba yaku, na buruburu ghath…®n…®mba.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Jeikob i thuweiru e mbaŇčambaŇčako iyako, i wo var…®ma me umbaliyema ghabubuthe, i worawe na i ndevanavana na ghamba renuwaŇčakiki kaiwae, na i woraŇčgiya iyako val…®vaŇčga boboma. Amba i liŇčgiya bunama oliv…® e vwatae na i vabobomaŇča Loi kaiwae.
\v 19 Jeikob i uno val…®vaŇčgako iyako Betel.\f + \fr 28:19 \ft Betel gharumwaru ‚ÄúLoi le Ňčgolo‚ÄĚ.\f* (Ghemba va ina gheko idae Luji.)
\p 
\v 20 Amba Jeikob i vakatha dagerawe regha weya \nd Giya Loi\nd* na iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo ghen, \nd Giya Loi\nd*, mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen na u njimbukikiŇčgo elo loŇčgaloŇčgake e t…®ne, na u giya ghan…®Ňčga na kwama e ghino,
\v 21 na u vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgo weya bwebwe weiŇčgu lo vanevane, ko ghen emunjoru ne lo Loi.
\v 22 Iya renuwaŇčakikike gha var…® ma vamidike e val…®vaŇčgake iyake, nevole ghamba kururu e ghen. Bigibigike wolagh…®ye ne u giya e ghino, ne ya wonjogha e ghen wan ten…®t\f + \fr 28:22 \ft Ne i vakatha wabwiyaworo na i giya wabura weya Loi.\f* lo vowo.‚ÄĚ
\c 29
\s1 Jeikob i vutha Padan Aram
\p 
\v 1 Jeikob kaero i wareriva. I loŇčga na i ghemba boimako, Keinan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoroko. Ghemba regha e boimako ghar…®ghar…® th…® yaku gheko.
\v 2 MbaŇča regha mbe ele loŇčga t…®ne eŇčge, i vutha e val…®vaŇčga regha sip lenji ghamba ghan, mbwarowou regha inawe. I vutha vaidiŇčgiya sip wabwito th…® ghenegh…®liŇča mbwarowouko. Th…® roroghagha ghanjiranjimbunjimbu th…® mena th…® giya mbwa weŇčgi. Mbwako va ina bode na ghagumogumo var…® lagh…®ye regha.
\v 3 MbaŇča thetheghan ghanjiwabwiko wolagh…®ye th…® raka vuthavao, amba ranjimbunjimbuko th…® vabulale vakatha var…®ko e mbwarowouko ghae na th…® giya mbwa weŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko. MbaŇča th…® vamunvaoŇčgi kaero th…® vabulale njoghava var…®ko e mbwarowouko ghae.
\p 
\v 4 Jeikob i vaitoŇčgiya ranjimbunjimbu iŇča, ‚ÄúWouna, ghemi aŇčga hu rakamena?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo rakamena Haran.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare hu ghareghare Leiban iye Neiho rumbuye?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana. Wo ghareghare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Amba Jeikob i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúRiwae i thovuye eŇčge?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbwana. Wo u thuwe, yawarumbuye Reitiyel maiya vara, weiyaŇčgiya sip.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Jeikob i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe, amba raŇčgela th…® yo vara iyake.\f + \fr 29:7 \ft Ghararagh…®ye mboro.\f* Buda kaiwae mo vaŇčgumenaŇčgiya sip…®na? Ma u lagiya eŇčge mbwa weŇčgi kaero u vaŇčgu njoghaŇčgiva na mbowo vethiya ghana ghanjinana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbowo wo roghaghaŇčgiya ranjimbunjimbuko vavana na wo th…® raka vutha weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji sip…®ko, amba mbaŇčara wo vabulale vakatha var…®ko e mbwarowouko ghae na wo giya mbwa weŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 MbaŇča Jeikob amba i utuutu, Reitiyel kaero i vutha weiyaŇčgiya ramae le sip, kaiwae elagh…®niye ghakaiwo i njimbukikiŇčgiya ramae le thetheghan…®ko.
\v 10 MbaŇča Jeikob i thuwe le gh…®na Reitiyel na le ghai Leiban le sip…®ko, i wa e mbwarowouko ghadidiye, i vabulale vakatha var…®ko e mbwarowouko ghae amba i giya mbwa weŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko.
\v 11 I vakathavao i wa ve vandamo Reitiyel. Kaiwae va weiye le warari iwaeŇčge i randa ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye.
\v 12 I dage weya Reitiyel iŇča, ‚ÄúRebeka nariya ghino, ramana louye.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča Reitiyel i loŇčwe iyako i rukunjogha na ve dage weya ramae.
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča Leiban i loŇčwe ghabodo Jeikob utuniye me vutha gheko, i rukuwawe na ve thuwe. I vutha i thuwabo na i vandamo. I vaŇčgu weiye th…® wa e Ňčgolo, na gheko amba Jeikob i utugiya bigibigiko wolagh…®yewe.
\v 14 Leiban i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema emunjoru, mbun…®ma na madibena iya e ghen…®na iya e ghinoke.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jeikob i vaŇčguŇčgiya Leya na Reitiyel
\p Jeikob i yaku weiye Leiban na i thalavu. Manjala umbwara e ghereiye
\v 15 Leiban i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúOthembe raŇča lo boda ghen, thava u kaiwoke e ghino na maa e modamodan. U utu giyama e ghino, ne ŇčgoroŇčga na ya vamodoŇčge?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Leiban yawarumbuye theunyiwo, lagh…®yeniye idae Leya na nasiyeniye idae Reitiyel.
\v 17 Leya ghayamoyamo vambema wevo eŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge Reitiyel, elagh…®niye wevo man…®une moli.
\v 18 Reitiyel va i wo Jeikob nuwae na amalagh…®niye i gharethovuwe, iya kaiwae i dage weya Leiban iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya kaiwo theghathegha umbopir…® kaiwan na ne u vaŇčgu veŇčgwa yawarumbuna nasiyeniye Reitiyel ya vaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Leiban i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye eŇčge ne ya vaŇčgu veŇčge. Maa lo renuwaŇča na yaŇča ya vaŇčguveya lolo reghava. I thovuye eŇčge mbe ya yaku vara weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Iya kaiwae Jeikob va i kaiwo theghathegha umbopir…® mbala val…®kaiwae i vaŇčgwa Reitiyel. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčako molao iyako ghathuwathuwa weya Jeikob Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča mbe gheviye eŇčge kaiwae i gharethovu lagh…®ye moliwe.
\p 
\v 21 Theghathegha umbopir…®na e ghereiye Jeikob i dagewe Leiban iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčgu giyama lo wevona. Kaero mendava ya kaiwo theghathegha umbopir…® kaiwan, na kaero nuwaŇčguiya ya ghena weiŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Kaero Leiban i vivatha ghe ghathaga na i kula vathavathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne.
\v 23 Ko iyemaeŇčge gougouko iyako Leiban i vaŇčguruwo yawarumbuye Leya weya Jeikob na i ghena weiye (le renuwaŇča va iŇčaeŇčge Reitiyel).
\v 24 Gougouniyeko iyako Leiban i vaŇčgugiya le rakakaiwo eunda idae Silpa weya yawarumbuye na le rakakaiwo.
\p 
\v 25 Va igh…®viya thewo na i manjala, Jeikob i thuweiru na i thuwe Leya, ghare i yo. IwaeŇčge i dage weya Leiban iŇča, ‚ÄúBudakaiya mo vakathake e ghino? Mendava ya kaiwo voreŇča theghathegha umbopir…® e ghen Reitiyel kaiwae, Ňčgoreiye? Budakai kaiwae na mo yaroŇčgoke?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Ko iyemaeŇčge Leiban i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhama thanavu e val…®vaŇčgake iyake ma Ňčgoreiye na wevo nasiyeniye i ghekai lagh…®yeniye e ghamwae.
\v 27 IyemaeŇčge, thoŇčgo wo u vakathavao lemi gheke thaganiye wikike iyake, ko amba tembe wo vaŇčgu veŇčgeva yawarumbuŇčguke eundake e ghen theghathegha umbopir…®va.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Jeikob i vakatha Ňčgoreiye. I vakathavao le gheko weiye Leya thaganiye e wik…®ko umbwara t…®ne, ko amba Leiban i vaŇčgugiya yawarumbuye Reitiyel na levo.
\v 29 Leiban i vaŇčwa le rakakaiwo wevo eunda na i vaŇčgugiya weya Reitiyel na le rakakaiwo. Wevoko idae Bilha.
\v 30 E mbaŇčako iyako Jeikob i ghena weiye Reitiyel. Le gharethovu weya Reitiyel i lagh…®ye kivwala le gharethovu weya Leya, na iyake kaiwae mbowo i kaiwova theghathegha umbopir…® weya Leiban.
\s1 Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga
\p 
\v 31 MbaŇča \nd Giya Loi\nd* i thuwe Jeikob maa ghare weya Leya, i vakatha na i ghamb…® gamagai, iyemaeŇčge Reitiyel va i kwama.
\v 32 Leya va i marabo na i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru. I rena idae Rubin, na iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* i thuweŇčgo ya gharev…®r…® iya i woveŇčgwa Ňčgama gh…®moruke. Mbwata ne mbaŇčake amba ne lo gh…®moruko i gharethovuŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 MbaŇča gheviye eŇčge e ghereiye, Leya kaero i marabova na mbowo i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru, na iŇča, ‚Äú\nd Giya Loi\nd* kaero i loŇčwa lo gh…®moruke amba maa ghare weŇčgo iya mbowo i woveŇčgova Ňčgama gh…®moruke. Iya kaiwae ne ya rena idae Simiyon.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 MbaŇča seiwo eŇčge mbowo i marabova na i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru. IwaeŇčge Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúGh…®mogh…®moru kaero theghetoninji vara iyake ya ghamb…® weiŇčgu lo gh…®moruko. E mbaŇčake iyake ambane ghare vara weŇčgo. I rena idae Livai.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 35 Leya mbowo i marabova na mbaŇča i ghamb…® Ňčgama gh…®moruva, kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake ya tarawe \nd Giya Loi\nd*.‚ÄĚ I rena idae Juda. Iyako e ghereiye maa tembe i ghamb…®va.
\c 30
\s1 Reitiyel na Leya lenji rakakaiwo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Reitiyel i thuwe ghaghae Leya eŇčge i ghamb…® gamagai weiye Jeikob na elagh…®niye nandere, iwaeŇčge i yamwanja ghaghae kaiwae. I dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúU giyama gamagai weŇčgo? ThoŇčgo maa ra thiya gamagai, lo nuwathar…®ke kaiwae ne ya mareke!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob weiye le ghatemuru i dage iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha budakai? Mbe Loi eŇčge ghamberegha iya i vakathaeŇčge na maa u ghamb…®na, maa ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Amba i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vaŇčgu veŇčge lo rakakaiwoke Bilha. U ghamb…® wein na gamagaiko thiyako ghino kaiwaŇčgu na weya elagh…®niye wo uuke ne i mbuthuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Kaero Reitiyel i vaŇčgu giya le rakakaiwoko Bilha weya Jeikob na levo na i ghena weiye.
\v 5 Wevoko i marabo na i ghamba Ňčgama gh…®moru, Jeikob nariye.
\v 6 Amba Reitiyel iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi le vakathako i govambwara lo renuwaŇčako i thovuye. I ghareghare budakai va nuwaŇčguiya moli iya i wogiya Ňčgama gh…®moruke e ghino.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae i rena idae Den.
\p 
\v 7 Th…® yakuyakuva na Reitiyel le rakakaiwoko Bilha kaero i marabova na mbowo i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru weiye Jeikob.
\v 8 Amba Reitiyel iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema lo rovur…®gheghe eŇčge weiŇčgu ghaghaŇčguko Loi le mwaewoko kaiwae, na kaero ya vaidiya une.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae i rena Ňčgamako idae Nap…®talai (gha loŇčwaloŇčwa Ňčgoreiye Hibru utuniye gharumwaru rovur…®gheghe).
\p 
\v 9 MbaŇča Leya i thuwe kaero maa i ghamb…®va, iwaeŇčge i vaŇčgwa le rakakaiwoma, Silpa na i vaŇčgu giya weya Jeikob na levo.
\v 10 MbaŇča ubotu Silpa i ghamb…® weiye Jeikob nariye Ňčgama gh…®moru.
\v 11 Amba Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya mwaun.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae i rena Ňčgamako idae Gad.
\p 
\v 12 Theghathegha gheviyeŇčge e ghereiye Leya le rakakaiwoma Silpa mbowo i ghamb…®va gh…®moru regha weiye Jeikob.
\v 13 Amba Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake mbema ya warari vara. Wanakauke wolagh…®ye ne th…® utuŇčaŇčgo lo wararike kaiwae.‚ÄĚ I rena Ňčgamako idae Asa.
\p 
\v 14 Va mbaŇča regha wit ghambaŇča uloulo, Rubin i wa wit…®ko e ghanjiuma t…®ne. IwaeŇčge ve vaidiya nana tarira. Ghar…®ghar…® va e mbaŇčako iyako th…® renuwaŇča val…®kaiwae i thalavugha wevo i kwama na kaero i ghamb…®va. Rubin i mban…®mena weya t…®nae Leya. Reitiyel i dage weya Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, thare val…®kaiwae u giya nanako iya naruko me mban vavana e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Ko iyemaeŇčge Leya i gonjoghawe na iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ana amba maa val…®kaiwan iya mendava u vaŇčgwa weŇčgo lo gh…®moruke? Na injana mbowo nuwaniyava naruŇčguke le nanake.‚ÄĚ
\p Reitiyel i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye eŇčge, naruna le nanana modae, ya dagerawe noroke gougou u ghena wein Jeikob.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Vama yegh…®yegh…®ye moli na Jeikob kaero i njoghanjoghamava, Leya ve lavolevole e wit…®ko e ghanjiuma. Kaero i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke gougou ya ghena weiŇčgu ghen. Kaero ma vamodaŇčge weya Leya. Ma mbana naruŇčguko le nana na ya vamodaŇčgewe.‚ÄĚ Ko amba gougouko iyako Leya i ghena weiye.
\p 
\v 17 Loi kaero i wovatha Leya le renuwaŇčako na i vakatha kaero i marabova. Weiye Jeikob i ghamb…® Ňčgama gh…®moru, theghelimaninji.
\v 18 Amba Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi kaero i giya modaŇčgu kaiwae va ya vaŇčgugiya lo rakakaiwoko weya lo gh…®moruko.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae i rena nariyeko idae Isaka.
\p 
\v 19 Leya mbowo i marabova na i ghamba nariye theghewonaniye weiye Jeikob.
\v 20 Leya iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi mendava i wogiya wo ghevawarari thovuye moli. MbaŇčake lo gh…®moruko ne i yavwatata wanaŇčgo kaiwae gamagai gh…®mogh…®moru kaero theghewona vara ya ghamb…®Ňčgi weiŇčgu.‚ÄĚ I rena Ňčgamako iyako idae Sebulon.
\p 
\v 21 MbaŇča reghavena mbowo i marabova na i ghamb…® Ňčgama wevo. I rena idae Daina.
\p 
\v 22 Amba Loi i renuwaŇčakikiya Reitiyel. I loŇčwe le naŇčgoko na i vakatha val…®kaiwae i ghamb…®.
\v 23 Amba i marabo na i ghamb…® Ňčgama gh…®moru. Na iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi kaero i thouyatho lo monjinake kaiwae mbaŇčake val…®kaiwaŇčgu val…®kaiwae ya ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai.‚ÄĚ
\v 24 Reitiyel i rena nariyeko idae Josep, na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbala Loi mbowo i lawogiyava Ňčgama gh…®moru regha e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jeikob na Leiban th…® utuŇča lenji thetheghan kaiwae
\p 
\v 25 MbaŇča Reitiyel i ghamba Josep na i ghereiye, Jeikob i wa weya Leiban na ve dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae u vatomweŇčgo na ma ya njoghava e ghambaŇčgu, va ya rikowe?
\v 26 U vaŇčgugiyama lo ovoke na lo ŇčgaŇčgake, iyava ya kaiwo kaiwanji e ghen theghathegha hoyawora na umbovar…® e t…®nenji. MbaŇčake ma u vatomwe eŇčge kaero ya vaŇčguŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčgake na wo raka e vanar…®gheŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Leiban i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, amalana, thoŇčgo va ya vawarariŇčaŇčge, mbowo ra yaku gheke weiŇčgu ghen. Kaiwae kaero ya ghareghare kaiwae lo loiŇčgike th…® govwambwara e ghino, thovuye na mwaewo iya ya vaidike weya Loi, r…®ghethoru moli kaiwae ghen inan gheke.‚ÄĚ
\v 28 Na mbowa i gotubweva iŇča, ‚ÄúKo u utugiyama e ghino, mbala ŇčgoroŇčga modan le lagh…®lagh…®ye ya giya e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 Amba Jeikob i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u ghareghare mbaŇča le molomolao lo kaiwo na ghathovuye e ghen. Len thetheghan th…® yala na lemoyo moli ghino lo njimbukiki e t…®ne.
\v 30 Na amba muyai va ya vutha e ghen, len thetheghan…®ke vambe gheviye eŇčge. MbaŇčake len thetheghan…®ke th…® ghamb…® raka na ma wabwi lemoya eŇčge, na elo vakathake wolagh…®ye e t…®nenji Loi i mwaewo lagh…®ye e ghen. Ko ne the mbaŇča eŇčge amba ya vakatha budakai lo ŇčgamaŇčgamake kaiwanji?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Leiban i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya giya budakai e ghen?‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe u ndegiya bigi regha e ghino. Ko mbe bigi reghaeŇčge ne u vakatha. ThoŇčgo u vatomwe, mbowo ya njimbunjimbukikiŇčgi vara len thetheghan…®ko.
\v 32 Noroke wo u vatomwe e ghino na ya vaghetheŇčgiya len thetheghan…®ko. Ne ya vaghetheraŇčgiyaŇčgiya sip le ŇčgaŇčga bwedibwedi na sip na gout e ghanjithuwathuwa bwebwa. Thetheghan…®ke thiyake ne ya mban, modaŇčgu.
\v 33 MbaŇča muyaiko ne val…®kaiwan u ghethe vakatha thoŇčgo lo vakatha e ghen i thovuye na emunjoru. ThoŇčgo ne u thuwe gout ma e ghanjithuwathuwa na sip ma riwanji i bwedi, ne u ghareghare ma kaiv…® e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 Leiban i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúLo renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye. U vakatha Ňčgoreiya moŇčana.‚ÄĚ
\v 35 IyemaeŇčge tembe e mbaŇčaniyeva t…®ne Leiban i wa weŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko na ve vaghetheraŇčgiyaŇčgiya gout takedi wolagh…®ye e ghanjibwebwako, gout vavata wolagh…®ye e ghanjibwebwa, thiya ghanjibwebwako kakaleva na sip…®ko wolagh…®ye iya riwanji i bwedi. I vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya onanariye na th…® njimbukikiŇčgi.
\v 36 Amba Leiban na onanariye th…® takovaoŇčgiya lenji thetheghan…®Ňčgima na th…® wareriŇča val…®vaŇčga regha, na i vakatha e ghalughawoghawo weya Jeikob. Le bwagabwaga Ňčgoreiya mbaŇča thegheto loŇčganiye. Na Jeikob vambe i ronjimbughath…®Ňčgiya Leiban le thetheghan…®ko ghanji uneko wolagh…®ye.
\p 
\v 37 IyemaeŇčge Jeikob i wa ve mbana umbwaumbwa umboto idaidanji popula, almon, na plen, th…® mbuthu e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, yaŇčgayaŇčganji totogha. I thethe njimwanjimwanji vaŇčga iya ghanjibwebwa kakalevako inanji e umbwako i raŇčgi.
\v 38 Amba Jeikob i bigirawe umbwaumbwako yaŇčgayaŇčganji, iya me thethe vaŇčgako iya, e thetheghan…®ko lenji ghamba mun mbwa t…®ne. Jeikob va i ghareghare mbaŇča thetheghan…®ko ne th…® mena th…® muna mbwako, gout takediko ne th…® baba vavatako e vwatanji.
\v 39 MbaŇča th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na umbwaumbwako yaŇčgayaŇčganji nanasiye ina e ghamwanji, gout…®ko th…® ghamb…®Ňčgiya totogha e ghanjibwebwa, e ghanji ŇčginiŇčginit…®, na e ghanji gagaeton.
\v 40 Jeikob i ghethe vakatha gout…®ma lenji ŇčgaŇčga e ghanjibwebwama, na i vakathaŇčgiya sip takediko th…® baba vavatako e vwataŇči na yamwanji i ghemba gout…®ko lenji ŇčgaŇčga. I vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na i mbana le thetheghan na mbe i wabwi vakatha weya Leiban le thetheghan…®ko.
\v 41 MbaŇča thetheghan…®ko vur…®gheghe gh…®mogh…®moru th…® baba vavatako e vwatavwatanji, kaero Jeikob i wa ve bigirawa umbwaumbwako yaŇčgayaŇčgae e ghanji mbwako ghamba ghadidiye e ghamwanji. MbaŇča gh…®mogh…®moru th…® baba vavatako e vwatavwatanji, kaero th…® thuwe umbwaumbwa yaŇčgayaŇčganji.
\v 42 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob mava i bigirawa umbwaumbwako yaŇčgayaŇčganji thetheghan…®ko th…® njavovoko e yamwanji. E kamwath…®ko iyako Jeikob i mbana thetheghan iya th…® vur…®ghegheko na Leiban i mbana iya th…® njavovo.
\v 43 Ele vakathako iyako i vakatha i vwenyevwenye lagh…®ye moli. Le sip na gout lemoyo moli, le kamel na le doŇč…®ki tembe lemoyova, na le rakakaiwo gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.
\c 31
\s1 Jeikob i vo weya Leiban
\p 
\v 1 Jeikob i loŇčwevaidiya Leiban le ŇčgaŇčga th…® liliya ghautu. Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúJeikob kaero i mban…®vao bigibigiko wolagh…®ye weya ramanda Leiban. I mbana ramanda le bigibigiko na i vakaiwoŇča na i vakatha ghamberegha i vwenyevwenye.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, Jeikob i njimbuvaidi Leiban le vakathawe maa i mboromboro Ňčgora le vakathawe va i vivako.
\p 
\v 3 Amba Loi i dagewa Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúU njogha e ghamban moli, iyava u rimbun…®kowe, iya len bodaboda nanjikowe noroke, na ya dagerawe mbene weiŇčgu vara ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 4 Jeikob i variye toto weŇčgiya Reitiyel na Leya na veth…® thuwe e val…®vaŇčga amalagh…®niye va inawe weiyaŇčgiya thetheghan e lenji ghamba ghan nana.
\v 5 MbaŇča th…® vuthawe, amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero ya njimbuvaidiya ramami le vakatha e ghino, maa Ňčgoreiya va le vakatha e ghino mbaŇča va i vivako. Ko iyemaeŇčge maa ya mararu, kaiwae Loi, iye bwebwe i kururuwe, maa i roiteteŇčgo. Iye mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye mbe weiŇčgu vara.
\v 6 Ghemi kaero hu ghareghare va ya rovur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli ya kaiwo ramami kaiwae,
\v 7 ko iyemaeŇčge ramami le vakatha maa i emunjoru e ghino. I kwan…®yaroŇčgo na ma i vamodo vakathaŇčgo mbaŇča regha na regha. IyemaeŇčge Loi mava i vatomwewe na i vakatha vuyowo e ghino.
\v 8 ThoŇčgo Leiban va iŇča na ya mban…®Ňčgiya thetheghan…®ko e ghanjithuwathuwa na modaŇčgu, mbala thetheghan…®ko th…® ghamb…® mbe e ghanjithuwathuwa eŇčge. Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo va iŇča na ya mban…®Ňčgiya e ghanjigagaeton na modaŇčgu, thetheghan…®ko mbene th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi eŇčge e ghanjigagaeton na modaŇčgu.
\v 9 Kaero hu thuwe, Loi i mbana ramami le thetheghan…®ko na i giya e ghino.
\p 
\v 10 ‚ÄúMbaŇča regha mbaŇča thetheghan…®ko ghanjimbaŇča th…® vakatha gamagai, ya ghenelolawa ghenelolo regha. Bigiko va ya thuweko iyake. Mbe gout…®ko gh…®mogh…®moru eŇčge e ghanji gagaeton…®ko na bwebwebwako eŇčge th…® bababa thetheghan wanakauko e vwatanji.
\v 11 Gheneloloko e t…®ne Loi le nyao thovuye i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄėJeikob.‚Äô Ya gonjoghawe yaŇča, ‚ÄėMbe ghinoke.‚Äô
\v 12 Kaero iŇča, ‚ÄėWo u thuwe. Mbe gout…®na iya e ghanji gagaeton na e ghanjibwebwebwana eŇčge iya th…® bababa thetheghan wanakauna e vwatanji. Th…® vakatha iyake kaiwae kaero ya thuwevao Leiban le vakathako wolagh…®ye e ghen.
\v 13 Ghino Loi iyava ya yomarana e ghen Betel e t…®ne. Na gheko u liŇčgiya bunama oliv…® e var…® na u vamidi woyavwatata kaiwae. Na tembe u vakathava dagerawe na u kururu e ghino Loi womberegha. MbaŇčake u vivatha len bigibigina na u njogha e ghamban…®na iyava u rinawe.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Reitiyel na Leya th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThare the bigithan reghava ina ramameko e ghayayao t…®ne ghime kaiwame?
\v 15 Thare le vakathako weinda gham…®nae Ňčgoreiya eto ghar…®ghar…®niye ghinda? Kaiwae maa mbe i vakuneŇčainda eŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge kaero i ghan…®vao mani iya len kaiwoko une.
\v 16 Emunjoru bigibigike wolagh…®ye thiyake, iya Loi va i mban weya ramameko, kaero ghindawe na la ŇčgamaŇčgama kaiwanji. U vakatha budakaiya Loi i utugiyana e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17-18 Kaero Jeikob i vivatha na i wareri i njogha weya ramae Kenan e thivathivaniye. I takoŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko na le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va le yakuyaku Padan Aram e t…®ne na i mban vathavatha. Le ovo na le ŇčgamaŇčgama th…® rakatha e kamel vwatanji na amalagh…®niye i takoŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko na i viva e ghamwanji.
\p 
\v 19 MbaŇča Leiban kaero i wa na ve tena sip vulivuliye wul kaiwae, e ghereiye amba Reitiyel i kaiva Ňčgoloko mbe ghaloi vatavatad…®. Iyako mbe ramaewe.
\v 20 Jeikob i ravunyivunyi weya Leiban rara Aram na mava i utugiyawe le wareriko utuniye.
\v 21 Iya kaiwae weiyaŇčgiya le ovo, i vo bigiya le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. I lawa e walagh…®ta lagh…®ye Yupreitis na i loŇčgaŇča bobokulu thivathivaniye idae Giliyad.
\s1 Leiban i woreghamba weya Jeikob
\p 
\v 22 MbaŇča theghetoniye e t…®ne Leiban amba i loŇčwevaidi Jeikob kaero menda i vogha.
\v 23 I vaŇčguŇčgiya le bodaboda gh…®mogh…®moruko vavana na th…® woreghamba weya Jeikob. MbaŇča theghepir…® e ghereiye i vuthavaleŇčgi e bobokulu, Giliyad thivathivaniye ele val…®vaŇčga.
\v 24 Ko gougou eŇčge ghenelolo e t…®ne Loi i dage weya Leiban rara Aram iŇča, ‚ÄúYa vanuwov…®r…®Ňčge. Thava ne u utu vathar…® weya Jeikob.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Jeikob i vatad le yoŇčathowathowa e bobokulu vwatae Giliyad e t…®ne. Na gheko Leiban i vuthavalewe. WeiyaŇčgiya le wabwi th…® vatad lenji yoŇčathowathowa e val…®vaŇčga regha evasiwanjiko.
\v 26 Leiban i dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúMendava u vakatha budakai? Mendava u ravunyivunyi e ghino na u vovaŇčguŇčgiya yawarumbuŇčgu theunyiwo Ňčgoreiya wanakau th…® laweŇčgi gaith…® e t…®ne.
\v 27 Buda kaiwae mendava u ravunyivunyi e ghino na u vothuwole? Buda kaiwae maa mendava u dage e ghino, mbala val…®kaiwae ghino menda ya variyeŇčga weiye warari, wothuwothu na thilo laiye?
\v 28 Ma mendava u vatomwe e ghino na ya vandamo mwaewoŇčgiya orumburumbuŇčgu na ot…®nat…®nanji. Emunjoru len vakathako maa weiye len renuwaŇča thovuye.
\v 29 Elo vur…®gheghe na val…®kaiwae ma vakatha vuyowo e ghen, ko iyemaeŇčge me gougou rama le Loi i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgo, iŇča, ‚ÄėNe u ndeutuŇča utu regha weiye len ghare gaith…® Jeikob we.‚Äô
\v 30 I thovuye eŇčge kaero menda nuwan…®na nuwaiya u njogha e ghamban. Ko iyemaeŇčge buda kaiwae mendava u lakaiva lo loiŇčgike?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúVa weiŇčgu lo mararu kaiwae lo renuwaŇčake va yaŇčaeŇčgeva mbwata ne u vothaŇčaŇčgo na u vaŇčgu njoghaŇčgiya oyawarumbuke e ghino. Iyake kaiwae va ya warerithuwole.
\v 32 Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo u vaidiya the lolothan ina gheke mendava i mbana len loiŇčgina, ne yaŇča na i mare. La bodaboda e maranji mbowo u tamwe ghan…®mbereghana. The bigi u vaidi ghen…®we u mban.‚ÄĚ Jeikob mava i ghareghare Reitiyel va i lakaiva Leiban le loiŇčgiko.
\p 
\v 33 Kaero Leiban ve tamwe Jeikob ele yoŇčathowathowa na mbowo i wava we Leya le yoŇčathowathowa na i wa weŇčgiya le rakakaiwoma theunyiwoma, ko iyemaeŇčge maa i vaidiya le loiŇčgima. Amba i wava Reitiyel ele yoŇčathowathowako.
\v 34 Reitiyel kaero me mbanuwo Ňčgoloko ghaloiŇčgima na i bigimban e kamel…®ko gharathatha lenji ghamba yaku, na mbe i yaku e vwatae mbaŇča ramae i ruwe. MbaŇča Leiban i tamwe ghatharaŇča yoŇčathowathowako t…®ne, ma i vaidi bigi regha mun.
\p 
\v 35 Reitiyel i dage weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúWogiya lagh…®ye, thava gharen i gaith…® wanaŇčgo. Ma val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya ndeghath…® e maran; ya yaku e njamnjam.‚ÄĚ Leiban me rovur…®gheghe e tamwe ko iyemaeŇčge ma i vaidi mun le Ňčgoloma ghaloiŇčgi.
\p 
\v 36 Jeikob ghare i gaith…® iwaeŇčge i dage weya Leiban iŇča, ‚ÄúKo va ya vakatha vara the thar…®? Va ya rake the mbaro na i vatomwe e ghen iya u tamwe ghatharaŇčgoke?
\v 37 Kaiwae kaero mo tamweghatharaŇča lo bigibigike wolagh…®ye, na mo vaidiya the bigi i mena e len Ňčgoloma t…®ne? U woraŇčgiya gheke e ghamwandake, na ghen na ghino la ghar…®ghar…®ke th…® thuwe na th…® ghethe thaghewoke kaiwanda.
\p 
\v 38 ‚ÄúTheghathegha hoiwo ya yaku weiŇčgu ghen. Ya njimbukiki wagiyawe len sip na gout na lenji ghamb…® mbe i thovuye eŇčge vara. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ma mbaŇča regha ya un…®gha len gout gh…®moruna regha wo thalavu kaiwae.
\v 39 The mbaŇča thoŇčgo thetheghan mbwanjam regha i mena th…®vathar…® kaiwae, mbe womberegha vara ya vamboromboro iya th…® vathar…®ko iyako. IyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo i yomara Ňčgoreiyako, u vavothaŇčaŇčgo na ya vamodo budakaiya va i ghawe gougou o ghararagh…®ye.
\v 40 Yakuyakuke iyake va th…® yomara e ghino elo njimbukiki weŇčgiya len thetheghan…®ko. Ghararagh…®ye varae i tagavaŇčaŇčanyaŇčgo na gougou njigh…®njigh…® kaiwae mbe igh…®viya iya eŇčge e maraŇčgu.
\v 41 Theghathegha hoiwo e t…®ne vambe inanŇčgu vara elen Ňčgolona Ňčgoreiye narun…®na ghino. Theghathegha hoyaworo na umbovar…® e t…®ne ya kaiwo yawarumbuke theunyiwoke kaiwanji na theghathegha umbowona len thetheghan…®na weŇčgi. Ko othembe lo kaiwo va Ňčgoreiyako, u v…®v…®va modaŇčgu mbaŇča lemoyo.
\v 42 ThoŇčgo rumbuŇčgu Eibraham le Loi na Loiko iya bwebwe Aisake i kururukowe ma ina e ghino, emunjoru mbala menda u variye yathuŇčgo kokowaŇčgu. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi va i thuwe wovuyowoko na lo kaiwo vur…®ghegheko kaiwan, iya kaiwae me gougou Loi i worawa ghan mbaro.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Jeikob na Leiban th…® vakatha lenji dagerawe
\p 
\v 43 Leiban i thombeya Jeikob le utuutuko iŇča, ‚ÄúWanakauke thiyake ghino lo ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgi na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva gamagaike thiyake ghino orumburumbuŇčguŇčgi na thetheghan…®ke thiyake ghino lo thetheghan. Iya vara wolagh…®yeke u thuweŇčgike mbe ghinowe eŇčge. IyemaeŇčge e mbaŇčake noroke ne ya vakatha budakai weŇčgiya oyawarumbuŇčguŇčgike na gamagaike iyava th…® ghamb…®Ňčgike?
\v 44 NuwaŇčguiya e mbaŇčake iyake ghen na ghino ra vakatha dagerawe regha na Loi iye ghanda raghaghayawo e ghanda lughawoghawo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 45 Kaero Jeikob i wo var…® lagh…®ye regha na i vamidi na i tabo na nono, na i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgi lenji dageraweko kaiwae.
\v 46 Amba Jeikob i dage weŇčgiya le bodabodako iŇča, ‚ÄúHu mban…®vatha var…®var…® na hu wabwi na i voro.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča kaero th…® vakathavao, amba Leiban na Jeikob thiya yaku na regha na thiya ghan…®Ňčga.
\v 47 Leiban i rena wabwiko idae Jega Sahaduta (vaŇča Aram gharumwaru ‚Äúvanuwov…®r…® ghawabwi‚ÄĚ), na Jeikob i rena idae Galid (vaŇča Kenan gharumwaru ‚Äúvanuwov…®r…® ghawabwi‚ÄĚ).
\p 
\v 48 Leiban i dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúVar…®var…®ke ghawabwi iyake ne i vanuwov…®r…®inda dageraweke mara vakathake noroke.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae Jeikob i rena idae Galid.
\v 49 Vambe th…® ren…®va idae Mij…®pa, kaiwae Leiban va iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi mbe ghamberegha vara i njimbukikinda na ra renuwaŇčakikiya dageraweke iyake mbaŇča ne ra iteta val…®vaŇčgake iyake.
\v 50 ThoŇčgo ma u goru weŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčgana theunyiwona, o thoŇčgo u vaŇčguŇčgiva wanakau vavana weinjiyaŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčgana, othembe ma lolo regha i utugiya weŇčgo, wo u renuwaŇčakiki eŇčge Loi iye ghanda raghaghayawo e ghanda lughawoghawo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 51 Leiban tembe i dage weva Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u thuwe, var…®var…® wabwima iyake na var…®ma i ndeghath…®ma iyake. Kaero mara vakathaŇčgi e ghandalughawoghaweke.
\v 52 Iya var…®var…®ke wabwike na iya i ndeghath…®ke thiye ghandaraghaghayawo. Mane ya valaŇčaniya wabwike na var…®ke i ndeghath…®ke na ya ghaona e len val…®vaŇčgana na ya vakowanaŇčge, na ghen tembe mane u valaŇčaniyava wabwike na var…®ke iya i ndeghath…®ke na u mena e lo val…®vaŇčgake na u vakowanaŇčgo.
\v 53 Orumburumbunda lenji loiŇčgi tembene th…® ghethe thoŇčgo ra renuwaŇčakiki na ra vikikighath…®gha iya dageraweke iyake ghautuutuke wolagh…®ye: thiye Eibraham le Loi na Neiho le loi.‚ÄĚ
\p Kaero Jeikob i tholo weya Loi iya ramae Aisake i mararuke e idae.
\v 54 I vakatha vowo gheko e ouko vwatae amba i kula vathaŇčgiya le bodabodako na th…® ghana ghan…®Ňčgako iyako weinji. Ghan…®Ňčgako e ghereiye mbowo th…® ghenava gheko.
\p 
\v 55 MbaŇčambaŇča vena Leiban i thuweiru i vandamoŇčgiya orumburumbuyeko na oyawarumbuyeŇčgima na i mwaewo weŇčgi. Amba i wareri na i njogha e ghambae.
\c 32
\s1 Jeikob i vivatha na i lavolevola Iso
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Jeikob i loŇčgaloŇčga e kamwath…® mborowae, Loi le nyao thovuthovuye vavana th…® lavolevole.
\v 2 MbaŇča i thuweŇčgi kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúIyake Loi le ragagaith…® lenji kiyamu.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae Jeikob i rena ghembako idae Mahanaim.\f + \fr 32:2 \ft Mahanaim gharumwaru ‚Äúkiyamu theghewo‚ÄĚ. \f*
\p 
\v 3 Jeikob i variyeŇčgiya ghevarivariye th…® raka viva e ghamwae na veth…® thuwe ghaghae Iso. Iye va ina Seir e vanautuma Idom e t…®ne.
\v 4 Jeikob i dage weŇčgi na ne veth…® utu weya Iso Ňčgoreiyake: ‚ÄúWeya wogiya Iso. Len rakakaiwo Jeikob i variye utuutuke iyake e ghen. Vambe va yaku weya la ghai Leiban, na vambe va yaku vara gheko ghaghad noroke.
\v 5 MbaŇča inaŇčgu e val…®vaŇčgako iyako ya mban vathavathaŇčgiya thetheghan…®ke thiyake: burumwaka, doŇč…®ki, sip na gout. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyeke: rakakaiwo gh…®mogh…®moru na rakakaiwo wanakau. MbaŇčake ya variye utuutuke iyake i ghaona e ghen, Iso, ghen giya lagh…®ye, ya woraweŇčgo e ghamwan…®na, thoŇčgo u warari kaiwaŇčgu val…®kaiwae ne u vaŇčguvathaŇčgo mbaŇča ne ya vutha e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča ravarivariye va th…® raka njoghama weya Jeikob kaero th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMendava wo raka weya ghagha Iso, na mbaŇčake kaero ina e kamwath…® mborowa i loŇčgaloŇčga, i mena na i lavolevoleŇčge. Iye weiyaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru hoseriyevar…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 MbaŇča Jeikob i loŇčwe utuutuko iyako i vakatha na i mararu lagh…®ye. Le renuwaŇča iŇčaeŇčgeva mbwata ne i mena na i vakatha th…®gha va le vakathamawe. IwaeŇčge i wabwiya ghar…®ghar…®ko weiyaŇčgiko na wabwiwo, na le thetheghan…®ko, sip, gout, burumwaka na kamel, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.
\v 8 Le renuwaŇčako iŇčava, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo Iso i vutha weime na i gaith…®, mbala i gaboŇčgi eŇčge wabwi regha na wabwi regha th…® rakavo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Amba Jeikob i naŇčgo iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, \nd Giya Loi\nd*, ghen rumbuŇčgu Eibraham le Loi, na bwebwe Aisake le Loi. O \nd Giya Loi\nd*, ghen va u dage e ghino na uŇča, ‚ÄėU njogha e ghamban moli weŇčgiya len bodaboda,‚Äô na u dagerawe na bigibigike thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye ne th…® yomara e ghino.
\v 10 Mbe gharen vara e ghino. MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye mbe inan vara evasiwaŇčgu mbaŇča ne nuwaŇčguiyaŇčge. Othembe maa val…®kaiwaŇčgu u vamboromboro bigibigike thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye e ghino. MbaŇča va ya ri gheke na ya gheoko na e Walagh…®ta Jor…®dan vambe ya wo eŇčge pwasike, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ya njoghama, ya vwenyevwenye lagh…®ye moli na lo ŇčgaŇčga na thetheghan wabwi thegheiwo.
\v 11 Wo u thalavuŇčgo na u vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgo ghaghaŇčgu Iso e n…®mae ghare! Kaiwae ya mararu ne i mena i tagavamareŇčgo, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva lo ovoke na gamagaike.
\v 12 Ko iyemaeŇčge va u dagerawe e ghino na uŇča, ne i thovuye e ghino na orumburumbuŇčgu lemoyo Ňčgoreiya kerakera e njigh…®ko ghadidiye, iya maa val…®kaiwae lolo regha i vaonako.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Gougou i ghena gheko. MbaŇčambaŇčavena Jeikob i ghathe bigibigi vavana na ne i variye weya ghaghae Iso:
\v 14 gout wanakau hoseriyeiwo (200) na hoiwo gh…®mogh…®moru, hoseriyeiwo (200) sip wanakau na hoiwo gh…®mogh…®moru,
\v 15 ghweto kamel wanakau weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga, ghwevar…® burumwaka wanakau na hoyaworo gh…®mogh…®moru, na hoiwo doŇč…®ki wanakau na hoyaworo gh…®mogh…®moru.
\v 16 Jeikob i vaŇčguraweŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko e wabwi regha iya na le rakakaiwoko th…® njimbukikiŇčgi. Amba i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka viva e ghamwaŇčgu. Wabwi regha iya mbe lemi loŇčga na mbe e ghami lughawoghawo iya e lemi wabwina regha na regha.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Kaero Jeikob i dage weya rakakaiwoko iya ne i vivako iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ghaghaŇčgu Iso i lavolevoleŇčge na i vaitoŇčge na iŇča, ‚ÄėKo u mena weya the giyathan, aŇčga ghamwan i reŇča, na thela le thetheghan…®Ňčgiya wolagh…®ye thiyake?‚Äô
\v 18 na mbala u gonjoghawe na uŇča, ‚ÄėGhen ghan mwaewo, wo giyana. Th…® mena weya len rakakaiwo na val…®gharegharen ghagha Jeikob. Amalagh…®niye ghaamba. Mbe ina i rereghamba e ghereimeko.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Tembe i utugiyava utuutuma me utugiyama weya wabwima i vivama; i utugiya weŇčgiya wabwi theghewoniye, theghetoniye na wabwiko wolagh…®ye, iŇča, ‚ÄúTembene hu utuŇča Ňčgoreiyeva iya ma utuŇčakaiko weya Iso mbaŇča ne hu lavolevole.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Na Jeikob mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu renuwaŇčakiki na hu dagewe ‚Äėlen rakakaiwo val…®gharegharen Jeikob maiya i rereghamba e ghereimeko.‚Äô‚ÄĚ Jeikob va i rerenuwaŇča na iŇča, ‚ÄúMbala bigibigike thiyake th…® wo nuwae na mbaŇča ne va vuthawe, mbwatane i numotena lo vakatha vathar…®mawe na i vaŇčguvathaŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\v 21 Kaero Jeikob i variye mwaewoma e ghamwae, ko iyemaeŇčge amalagh…®niye mbowo i roghenava e kiyamuko.
\s1 Jeikob i lawelawe weiye Loi
\p 
\v 22 Va gougouko iyako Jeikob i thuweiru na i vaŇčguŇčgiya le ovo theunyiwoma, le rakakaiwo wanakau theunyiwoma na le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru theyaworo na regha na i variyeŇčgi na th…® rakalawa e walagh…®ta idae Jabok.
\v 23 Le vakathako iyako e ghereiye, Jeikob me mbana le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e kiyamuko na i variye weiyaŇčgiya le rakakaiwoko e walagh…®tako val…®vaŇčga,
\v 24 ko iyemaeŇčge mbe ghamberegha i reyaku e kiyamuko. Amba lolo regha i yomarawe na i gaith…® weiye. Th…® velawelaweŇčgi ghaghad i ghera buruburuko r…®ghe.
\v 25 MbaŇča loloko i thuwe maa tembe val…®kaiwaeva i kivwala Jeikob, iwaeŇčge i Ňčge na i vovu lemwa. Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob mbe i rovur…®gheghe vara na th…® lawelawe weiye.
\v 26 Amba loloma i dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúU viyathuŇčgo na ya wa, kaiwae kaero iya vara i gh…®viyake.‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMane ya viyathuŇčge ghaghad u giya wo mwaewo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 27 Loloko i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúIdan thela?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúJeikob.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Loloko i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae mo rovur…®gheghe wein Loi na weinaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, na mo ghataŇčaghath…® ghaghad le ghambako, mbaŇčake ya v…®va idan…®na. Idan togha Isirel.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 32:28 \ft Isirel gharumwaru ‚ÄúI rovur…®gheghe weiye Loi.‚ÄĚ \f*
\p 
\v 29 Jeikob i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake u unogiyama idan…®na e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae nuwaniya u ghareghare idaŇčgu?‚ÄĚ Amba i giya Jeikob ghamwaewa.
\p 
\v 30 Iya kaiwae Jeikob i rena val…®vaŇčgako iyako idae Peniyel iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae ma thuwe Loi na namoghawame weiŇčgu ko iyemaeŇčge mbe e yawayawaliŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Varae i yovoro Jeikob i iteta Peniyel, na i loŇčga vaŇčgeŇčge kaiwae loloma menda i vovuya le mwa.
\v 32 Iyake kaiwae, noroke Isirel orumburumbuye maa th…® ghana thetheghan mamandiye i v…®ghatha le mwako, kaiwae va e mamandiyeko iyako iyava loloko va i Ňčge Jeikob kowe.
\c 33
\s1 Jeikob i vutha weya Iso
\p 
\v 1 E lenji loŇčga e t…®ne Jeikob i tagath…®na marae na i thuwe e ghamwanjiko, Iso, amba i menamenako weiyaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru hoseriyevar…®. Kaero i wabwiŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga: Leya wabwira, Reitiyel wabwira na le rakakaiwo wanakau theunyiwoma wabwira.
\v 2 Jeikob i vaghetheŇčgiya wabwiko Ňčgoreiyake: le rakakaiwo wanakauma na lenji ŇčgaŇčga th…® raka viva, e ghereinji Leya na le ŇčgaŇčga, na muyai moli Reitiyel na nariye Josep.
\v 3 Jeikob ghamberegha i viva moli vara e ghamwanji na wo vevuthakai weya Iso. MbaŇča kaero i loŇčga thaiya Iso, i ronja e gheghe vuvuye i kururu na ghamwae i nja e thelauko vwatae mbaŇčapir…® mbaŇča i loŇčgaloŇčga thaiya ghaghae Iso.
\p 
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge Iso i ruku na i ghemba Jeikob, i thuwobod i bigiyatho n…®man…®mae e numwe na i vandamo. Lenji warari kaiwae th…® vethuweŇčgi na mbe theghewoko vara th…® randa kaiwae warari i riyevanjaraŇčgi.
\v 5 Iso i tagath…®na marae na i thuweŇčgiya wanakau na gamagai, kaero i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThavala iya ghar…®ghar…®ke weinaŇčgike?‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi va i thovuye moli e ghino, iyava i giya gamagaike thiyake e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Rakakaiwo wanakauma th…® raka vutha weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgamaŇčgama na th…® kururuwe,
\v 7 evasiwae Leya na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® raka mena na th…® kururuwe. Moumouniye Josep na Reitiyel th…® mena na th…® kururu weya Iso.
\p 
\v 8 Iso i vaito Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae menda u variyeŇčgiya thetheghan…®ko th…® raka viva e ghamwan iya menda ya lavolevoleŇčgiko?‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMenda ya variyeŇčgi e ghen, wogiya lagh…®ye, ghan…®mwaewo ne i vakatha na u warari kaiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge Iso i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero val…®kaiwaŇčgu, ghaghaŇčgu. Budakai menda u mban, mbe ghen…®we.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúAee ghaghaŇčgu, thava! ThoŇčgo gharen ma gaith…® wanaŇčgo, ko u mbana mwaewona menda ya variyena e ghen. Mbala ya ghareghare gharen i nja weŇčgo Ňčgoreiye Loi va i wovatha na ghare i nja weŇčgo.
\v 11 Ago lagh…®ye e ghen, mbema u wovatha eŇčge lo renuwaŇčake na u mbana bigibigina mendava ya variyena e ghen. Na kaiwae Loi vambe ghare vara e ghino i vakathaŇčgo lo bigibigi lemoyo na val…®kaiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ Jeikob i vavothaŇča ghaghae iya kaiwae Iso i wovatha na i mbana mwaewoko iyako.
\p 
\v 12 Iso i dage weya ghaghae Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ra wareri eŇčge mbaŇčake, na ghino ya viva e ghamwan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalana, u ghareghare gamagai maa val…®kaiwanji th…® maya e loŇčga Ňčgoreiya ghen len loŇčgana. Na tembe ya rerenuwaŇčava thetheghan th…® ghamb…® totogha kaiwanji. ThoŇčgo ya vakathaŇčgi th…® loŇčga vur…®gheghe, mbene mbaŇča reghaeŇčge e t…®ne, kaero thiya marevao.
\v 14 Iya kaiwae ya naŇčgo e ghen, amalana, u viva e ghamwaŇčgu. Tembene seiwoseiwo ya rereghamba na gamagaike na thetheghan…®ke ne th…® loŇčga lama loŇčga, ghaghad ne va vutha e ghen Seir.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 Iso i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye, thare ne ya iteteŇčgi eŇčge lo ghar…®ghar…®ke vavana na th…® thalavuŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúAgo lagh…®ye e ghen, wogiya lagh…®ye, kaero emunjoru mo vatomwe gharen e ghino na mo vaŇčguvathaŇčgo, na iyake mbe val…®kaiwaŇčgu eŇčge.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Iya kaiwae e mbaŇčako iyako Iso i wareri na i njogha Seir.
\v 17 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob ve vutha e ghemba regha idae Sakot. Gheko i vatada Ňčgolowe kaiwanji na yoŇčathowathowa thetheghan…®ko kaiwanji. Iya kaiwae ghembako iyako idae Sukot.
\p 
\v 18 Jeikob va i ri Padan Aram na le loŇčga e t…®ne mbaŇča eŇčge i ghaŇčgoghaŇčgo, na e mbaŇčake iyake i vutha ghemba lagh…®ye Sekem Kenan e t…®ne weiye le thovuye. Mbowo i lakiyamu eŇčge Sekem ghadidiye.
\v 19 Va i vamodo thelauko iyako weŇčgiya amala regha idae Heimo le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru. Modae le lagh…®lagh…®ye silva geth…®thaŇčar…®. Heimo nariye regha idae Sekem.
\v 20 Jeikob i vatad ghamba vowo gheko na i rena idae El Elohi Isirel.\f + \fr 33:20 \ft El Elohi Isirel gharumwaru ‚ÄúLoi iye Isirel le Loi‚ÄĚ.\f*
\c 34
\s1 Sekem i lawa Daina na i yathima weiye
\p 
\v 1 Va mbaŇča regha Daina, Jeikob na Leya yawarumbunji, i raŇčgi na i wa ve thuweŇčgiya Kenan wanakauniye vavana.
\v 2 MbaŇča Sekem, Heimo nariye, iye rara Hivi na val…®vaŇčgako iyako gharandeviva, i thuwe Daina na nuwaeko ma nuwaiya vara moli. IwaeŇčge i vaŇčgu na i vavur…®gheghe na i yathima weiye.
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge vakathako iyako e ghereiye Sekem vambe gharewe vara Daina na nuwaiya i vaŇčgu, iya kaiwae i utuwe weiye le gharethovu.
\v 4 Sekem i dage weya ramae Heimo iŇča, ‚ÄúWo u vanamwe wevoko utuutuniye kaiwaŇčgu na ya vaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 MbaŇča ubotu Jeikob i loŇčwevaidiya yawarumbuye Daina utuniye, Sekem i vavur…®ghegheŇča na i yathima weiye na i vakatha kaero i mbigh…®. IyemaeŇčge mbe i rokubaroŇča eŇčge, kaiwae le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru vambe inanji e val…®vaŇčga nana inawe th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya thetheghan.
\p 
\v 6 IwaeŇčge Heimo, Sekem ramae, i wa weya Jeikob na ve utuŇča Daina utuniye weiye.
\v 7 Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga th…® loŇčwe vakathako iyako utuniye mbaŇča th…® ri e val…®vaŇčgako iyako na th…® njogha weya ramanji. Gharenji i yo weinji ghatemuru na gaith…®, kaiwae Sekem i vakatha monjina weya Jeikob na le bodaboda mbaŇča i yathima weiye Daina. Vakathako iyako i thar…® na mbala thava i vakatha.
\p 
\v 8 MbaŇča Jeikob na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® mevathavatha, Heimo i vamanjamanjalaŇča le menako r…®ghe weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčguko Sekem gharewe vara wevoko iya yawarumbun…®ko, Daina. Aee, thare val…®kaiwae hu vatomwe na i vaŇčgu.
\v 9 Ghemi na ghime ra vanamwe ghe kaiwae noroke. ThoŇčgo hu vatomwa oyawarumbumina weŇčgiya ghama theghake na th…® vaŇčguŇčgi, tembene wo vatomweva oyawarumbumeko weŇčgiya ghami theghana th…® vaŇčguŇčgi.
\v 10 Val…®kaiwae hu yaku weime. The val…®vaŇčga nuwamiya hu yakuwe vo hu yakuwe. Hu kunewe na hu vamodo lemi ghamba yakuyakuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Amba Sekem i dage weŇčgiya Daina ramae na olouye iŇča, ‚ÄúAee, thoŇčgo hu wovatha lo renuwaŇčake ne ya giya e ghemi the bigiya nuwamiya e ghino.
\v 12 Val…®kaiwae hu worawa lemi vathavoko na ghami mwaewo, le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya lemi renuwaŇčana na ya mban…®mena. The bigithan hu naŇčgo ne ya wo mena. Mbema hu vaŇčgugiyama eŇčge wevoko na lo wevo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga mava th…® utu emunjoru weŇčgiya Sekem na ramae. Va nuwanjiya th…® lith…® weya Sekem budakaiya va le vakathako weya lounji Daina.
\v 14 Th…® dage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMaa val…®kaiwae wo vakatha Ňčgoreiyako. Mane wo vaŇčgugiya loumeko weya gh…®moru maa i wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye. Iyako ne i vakatha ghamba monjina weime.
\v 15 Mbe kamwath…® regha eŇčge na ne wo vatomwe e ghemi na gh…®mogh…®moru e lemi val…®vaŇčgana th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya wanakau e lama val…®vaŇčgake. Gh…®mogh…®moru e lemi val…®vaŇčgana wo th…® wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye na th…® tabo Ňčgoranjiya ghime.
\v 16 ThoŇčgo ne hu vakatha Ňčgoreiyako amba ne wo vatomwe e ghemi na hu vaŇčguŇčgiya wanakau weime na lemi ovo, na ghime tembe wo vaŇčguŇčgiva wanakau e lemi val…®vaŇčgana. Amba ne wo yaku weimaŇčgiya ghemi na ra tabo wabwi regha ghar…®ghar…®niye.
\v 17 Ko thoŇčgo gh…®mogh…®moruna maa th…® warariŇča th…® kiten…®yatho riwanji mbothiye njimwae, ne wo vaŇčgwa loumeko na wo iteta lemi val…®vaŇčgake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Heimo na nariye Sekem th…® warariŇča lenji utu vanamweko kaiwae.
\v 19 Na Sekem mbema ghe na n…®mae eŇčge kaero ve vakatha budakaiya Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga lenji woraŇčgiya weŇčgi, kaiwae va nuwaeko nuwaiya moli Jeikob yawarumbuye Daina. Amalagh…®niye vambe i viviva vara ramae Heimo ele renuwaŇčako e ghayayaoko t…®ne.
\v 20 Iya kaiwae Heimo na nariye Sekem th…® wa e lenji ghamba nivako, e ghembako ghaghambaru evasiwae na th…® utu weŇčgiya ghembako ghar…®ghar…®niye.
\v 21 Th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ke thiyake th…® thovuye moli na gharemal…®l…® ghar…®ghar…®niyeŇčgi. Val…®kaiwae ra vatomwe weŇčgi ra yaku weindaŇčgi e val…®vaŇčgake iyake na ra kune weindaŇčgi. Thelauko i lagh…®ye moli, val…®kaiwanda eŇčge. Gh…®mogh…®moru ela val…®vaŇčgake th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya wanakau weŇčgi, na gh…®mogh…®moru e lenji val…®vaŇčgako th…® vaŇčguŇčgiya wanakau ela val…®vaŇčgake.
\v 22 IyemaeŇčge, mbene th…® warariŇča eŇčge ra yaku weindaŇčgi na ra tabo na wabwi regha ghar…®ghar…®niyeŇčgi thoŇčgo gh…®mogh…®moru ela val…®vaŇčgake th…® wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye Ňčgoreiya thiye.
\v 23 ThoŇčgo ra varaeŇčna, lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye ne ghindawe; lenji thetheghan…®ko wolagh…®ye na the bigithan…®va ina weŇčgi. Ko mbema ra vakatha eŇčge lenji renuwaŇčako na ne th…® yaku e val…®vaŇčgake iyake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye iyava th…® raka iteta ghamba nivako th…® wovathovuthovuyeŇča Heimo na nariye Sekem lenji utuko na gh…®mogh…®moru wolagh…®ye e ghembako t…®ne th…® wo kiten…®yathu thanavuniye.
\p 
\v 25 MbaŇča theghetoniye e t…®ne, mbaŇča gh…®mogh…®moru e ghembako t…®ne riwanjiko mbothiye vamba th…® thighathigha, kaero Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga theghewo, Simiyon na Livai, Daina olouye, th…® mbana lenji gaith…® ghaghalith…®, veth…® ru e ghembako t…®ne; mbaŇčaniye ghembako maa e lenji ghareghare mun, na th…® gabovaoŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruko wolagh…®ye.
\v 26 Tembe th…® gaboŇčgiva Heimo na nariye Sekem, na th…® vaŇčgwa Daina Sekem ele Ňčgolo amba th…® njogha.
\v 27 Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčgama vavana th…® raka ru e ghembako t…®ne Ňčgora ramaremareko riwanji, th…® raka ru e ŇčgoloŇčgolo na th…® mbana bigibigiko wolagh…®ye. Lenji vakathako iyako th…® lith…®gha budakai Sekem va le vakatha raithar…® weya lounji Daina.
\v 28 Th…® takoŇčgiya lenji sip, gout, burumwaka na doŇč…®ki va inanji e ghembako t…®ne na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wolagh…®yeko inanji eto e lenji ghamba ghan.
\v 29 Th…® bigivao lenji vwenyevwenyeko bigibiginiye wolagh…®ye, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva wanakau na gamagai, na the bigiva inanji e ŇčgoloŇčgolo th…® bigivao na iko.
\p 
\v 30 Jeikob i dage weŇčgiya Simiyon na Livai iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake kaero u vaŇčguraweŇčgo e vuyowo t…®ne. Kenan ghar…®ghar…®niye na Perisi ghar…®ghar…®niye na the ghar…®ghar…®va inanji gheke ne th…® botewoyathuŇčgo. Na i ghao maa gh…®mogh…®moru lemoyo nanji e ghino. ThoŇčgo th…® loŇčwevaidiinda na th…® wabwi na regha, na th…® gaith…® weinda ne val…®kaiwanji th…® mukuwoinda.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa tembe wo warariva Sekem le vakatha weya loumeko, Ňčgoreiya wanakau th…® vakuneŇča riwanji yathima e thanavuniye, iya kaiwae wo lith…®we.‚ÄĚ
\c 35
\s1 Jeikob i njogha Betel
\p 
\v 1 Amba Loi i dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúU yondo vir…®. U wa Betel na vo vatada len kiyamu gheko, ne tembe vo vatad…®va ghamba vowo weya Loi, iyava i yomarama e ghen mbaŇča va u vogha weya ghagha Iso.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 2 Jeikob i dage weŇčgiya ghayayaoko ghar…®ghar…®niye na thavalava va weiyaŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu bigi raŇčgiya loi kwan…®kwan…®na wolagh…®ye iya hu kururuna weŇčgi. Hu mban vathaŇčgi na ra yathuŇčgi. Hu njimboŇčgiya kwama th…® th…®na na hu vivathaŇčga kururu kaiwae weya Loi.
\v 3 Hu vamayaŇča na ra raka Betel. Ne va vatada ghamba vowo gheko na ra kururu weya Loi, iye va i thalavuŇčgo e wo vuyowo t…®ne. Na amalagh…®niye vambe weiŇčgu vara the val…®vaŇčga va ya reŇčawe.‚ÄĚ
\v 4 Kaero th…® giya lenji loi kwan…®kwan…®ma weya Jeikob na yanayanawanji ghae. Amba Jeikob i bekuŇčgi e umbwa ouk raberabe Sekem ghadidiye.
\v 5 MbaŇča Jeikob na le ŇčgaŇčga thiya wareri, mararu lagh…®ye i ru weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e ghembaghemba evasiwanji na maa val…®kaiwanji th…® woreghamba na th…® gaith…® weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 6 Jeikob na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye weiyaŇčgiko th…® raka vutha Luji (mbaŇčake th…® uno idako Betel) Kenan thivathivaniye e t…®ne.
\v 7 Gheko i vatada ghamba vowo, na i rena idae El Betel kaiwae va gheko Loi i vatomwe ghamberegha weya Jeikob mbaŇča i vogha weya ghaghae Iso.
\p 
\v 8 MbaŇča vambe th…® yakuyaku Betel ghadidiye kaero Debora iye elagh…®sar…® moli, i mare. Elagh…®niye va Rebeka gharanjimbunjimbu mbaŇča iye vamba Ňčgama vara. Th…® beku e umbwa Alon e r…®ghe Betel na bode. Iya kaiwae th…® uno idae ‚ÄúUmbwa Ouk Randarandaniye.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 35:8 \ft Umbwa Ouk Randarandaniye ‚ÄúAlon Bakut‚ÄĚ vaŇča Hibru e t…®ne. \f*
\p 
\v 9 MbaŇča Jeikob vama i iteta Padan Aram na i njogha Betel, Loi mbowo i yomaraweva na i giya ghamwaewo.
\v 10 Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúIdan Jeikob, ko iyemaeŇčge ma tembene mbaŇča reghava th…® una idan Jeikob; ne idan Isirel.‚ÄĚ Ko amba th…® rena Jeikob idae ‚ÄúIsirel‚ÄĚ.
\p 
\v 11 Amba Loi i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Loi Vur…®ghegheniye. U ghamb…®rake na len ŇčgaŇčga lemoyo. Vanautuma ne th…® rimbun e ghen, na orumburumbu e t…®nenji nevole kiŇč th…® rakamenawe.
\v 12 Thelauko iyava ya dagerawe weya Eibraham na Aisake, tembe ya wogiyava e ghen. Tembene ya giyava iya thelauke iyake weŇčgiya orumburumbu tha muyaiko.‚ÄĚ
\v 13 MbaŇča Loi kaero i utuvao i roitete e val…®vaŇčgako iyako.
\p 
\v 14 E val…®vaŇčgako vara iyako iya Loi me utukowe, Jeikob i vamidiya var…®we. I liŇčgiya waen na bunama i mena e oliv…® e vwatae na i vabobomaŇča Loi kaiwae.
\v 15 I rena ghembako idae Betel.
\s1 Reitiyel i mare
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča gheviye e ghereiye Jeikob na le wabwi th…® roiteta Betel. Eprat maa vama i bwagabwaga moli weŇčgi, kaero Reitiyel Ňčgamoiye i njivun na i rovur…®gheghe.
\v 17 MbaŇča v…®r…®ko vama i vwe na i vwe, wevoko i thathalavukowe i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúTha u gharelagh…®lagh…®, mbowo ne u ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru regha.‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Reitiyel vama ghambaŇča i mare, ko iyemaeŇčge amba muyai yawaliye iko i larena nariyeko idae Ben-Oni.\f + \fr 35:18 \ft Ben-Oni gharumwaru ‚Äúwo vuyowo Ňčgamaniye‚ÄĚ.\f* Ko iyemaeŇčge ramae Jeikob te vambe i roren…®va idae Benjamin.\f + \fr 35:18 \ft Benjamin gharumwaru ‚Äún…®maŇčguke une Ňčgamaniye‚ÄĚ.\f*
\p 
\v 19 MbaŇča Reitiyel i mare th…® beku e kamwath…® i wa Eprat ghadidiye ‚ÄĒ noroke th…® uno Bet…®lehem.
\v 20 Jeikob i vamidiya var…® regha gheko na i tabo Reitiyel ghabubuyeko ghanono. Na var…®ko iyako mbe inawe noroke.
\p 
\v 21 Isirel (Jeikob idae togha Isirel) mbowo i loŇčgaova Mig…®dol Eda na seiwova, na gheko weiyaŇčgiya le wabwi th…® kiyamuwe.
\s1 Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga
\p 
\v 22 MbaŇča Isirel vamba ina e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, amba Rubin i ru na i ghena weiye Bilha, ramae le rakakaiwo na levo eunda. Isirel i loŇčwe vaidiya iyako na ghare i muru.
\b
\m Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga lenji ghanaghanagha theyaworo na theghewo.
\li1 
\v 23 Leya le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Rubin, Jeikob nariye vir…®viva,
\li2 Simiyon, Livai, Juda, Isaka na Sebulon.
\li1 
\v 24 Reitiyel le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Josep na Benjamin.
\li1 
\v 25 Reitiyel le rakakaiwo wevo, Bilha, le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Den na Nap…®talai.
\li1 
\v 26 Leya le rakakaiwo wevo, Silpa, le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Gad na Asa.
\p Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčgake thiyake va th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi mbaŇča vamba ina Padan Aram.
\s1 Aisake i mare
\p 
\v 27 Jeikob kaero i vutha weya ramae Aisake Memri e t…®ne Kiriyat Aba ghadidiye. MbaŇčake iyake th…® uno ghembako iyako idae Hebron. Eibraham na Aisake va th…® yaku e val…®vaŇčgako iyako.
\v 28-29 Aisake vama i amalagh…®sar…® moli ghatheghathegha va i wo hothaŇčar…® na ghwewa (180) amba i garalawa weŇčgiya orumburumbuye va th…® mare vivako. Le ŇčgaŇčga Iso na Jeikob va th…® beku.
\c 36
\s1 Iso orumburumbuye
\p 
\v 1 Iso orumburumbuye tha na tha utuutuninjiya iyake. Tembe idaeva Idom.
\pm 
\v 2 Iso le ovo thiye Kenan wanakauniye. Le ovo theuto: Ada, Oholibama na Basimata. Ada ramae iye Het loloniye regha idae Elon. Oholibama ramae idae Ana na rumbuye gh…®moru idae Sibiyon, iye Hivi loloniye.
\v 3 Basimata ramae idae Ismel na louye idae Nebaiyot.
\pm 
\v 4 Iso na le ovo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake. Ada i ghamba Elipas, Basimata i ghamba Riyuwel,
\v 5 na Oholibama i ghamb…®Ňčgiya Jeus, Jalam na Kora. Gamagaike thiyake le ovo th…® ghamb…®Ňčgi mbaŇča mbe inanji vara Kenan e t…®ne.
\pm 
\v 6 Iso i vaŇčguŇčgiya le ovo, le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau, na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye e ghayayaoko t…®ne, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva le sip na gout, burumwaka na doŇč…®ki na le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va i mban…®vathavatha Kenan e t…®ne. I iteta val…®vaŇčgako iyako na i wa e val…®vaŇčga regha seiwo i bwagabwaga weya ghaghae Jeikob.
\v 7 Iso na Jeikob lenji bigibigiko vama lemoyo moli na maa tembe val…®kaiwanjiva th…® yaku na regha. Lenji thetheghan…®ko va th…® ghanagha moli na thelauko va th…® yakuŇčako mava nana i pokuwe lenji thetheghan…®ko kaiwanji.
\v 8 Iya kaiwae Iso, mbowo va th…® unova idae Idom, ve yaku e bobokulu thivathivaniye idae Seir.
\s1 Iso orumburumbuye inanji Seir
\p 
\v 9 Iyake Iso orumburumbuye tha na tha utuutuninji. Amalagh…®niye Idom ghar…®ghar…®niye rumbunji, thiya yaku Seir, bobokulu thivathivaniye e t…®ne.
\b
\li1 
\v 10 Iso le ŇčgaŇčga idanji thiyake:
\li2 Elipas, Iso levo Ada nariye, na Riyuwel, Iso levo Basimata nariye.
\li1 
\v 11 Elipas le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Timan, Oma, Sepo, Gatam na Kenas.
\li2 
\v 12 Iso nariye Elipas vambe le rakakaiwo wevova idae Timna. Vambe i ghamb…®va weiye na nariye idae Amalek. Theghewonake thiyake Iso levo Ada orumburumbuyeŇčgi.
\li1 
\v 13 Iso nariye Riyuwel le ŇčgaŇčga theghevar…®:
\li2 Nahat, Sera, Sama na Misa. Thiyake Iso levo Basimata orumburumbuyeŇčgi.
\li1 
\v 14 Iso levo Oholibama, iye Ana yawarumbuye na iye tembe Sibiyon rumbuyeva. Va i ghamb…® weiye Iso le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya thiyake:
\li2 Jeus, Jalam na Kora.
\p 
\v 15-16 Idom ghar…®ghar…®niye na lenji randeviva thiya rimbun weya Iso thiyake:
\li1 E t…®nenji va Elipas, iye Iso nariye vir…®viva, orumburumbuyeŇčgi.
\li2 RandevivaŇčgike thiyake: Timan, Oma, Sepo, Kenas, Kora, Gatam na Amalek. Thiyake Iso levo Ada orumburumbuyeŇčgi.
\li1 
\v 17 Wabwike thiyake th…® rimbun weya Iso nariye Riyuwel:
\li2 Nahat, Sera, Sama na Misa. Thiye Iso levo Basimata orumburumbuyeŇčgi. Te vambe th…® yakuva Idom e t…®ne.
\li1 
\v 18 Wabwike thiyake, Jeus, Jalam na Kora, va th…® rimbun weya Iso levo Oholibama, iya t…®nae idae Ana.
\p 
\v 19 Thiyake va Iso onanariyeŇčgi na wabwi regha na regha va th…® rimbun weŇčgi.
\b
\p 
\v 20 Thiyake Seir orumburumbuyeŇčgi th…® mena wabwi Hor e t…®ne, thiya yakukai e val…®vaŇčgake iyake:
\li2 Lotan, Sobal, Sibiyon, Ana,
\v 21 Dison, Esa, na Disan. Iya Seir orumburumbuyeke thiyake inanji Idom na thiye Hor ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji randevivaŇčgi.
\li1 
\v 22 Lotan le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Hori na Homam. Na Lotan louye idae Timna.
\li1 
\v 23 Sobal le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Alvan, Manahat, Ibal, Sipo na Onam.
\li1 
\v 24 Sibiyon le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Aiya na Ana. Ana iye va i vaidiya mbwarowou i dayagha e vuruvuru vwatavwata e t…®ne mbaŇčaniye i njimbukikiŇčgiya ramae Sibiyon le doŇč…®ki.
\li1 
\v 25 Ana le ŇčgaŇčga thiyake:
\li2 Dison na Oholibama, elagh…®niye Ana yawarumbuye.
\li1 
\v 26 Dison le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Hemdan, Esban, It…®ran na Karan.
\li1 
\v 27 Esa le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Bilhan, Saavan na Akan.
\li1 
\v 28 Disan le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake:
\li2 Us na Aran.
\li1 
\v 29-30 Thiyake randevivaŇčgi Hor ghar…®ghar…®niye e t…®nenji:
\li2 Lotan, Sobal, Sibiyon, Ana, Dison, Esa, na Disan. Thiye va th…® mbaro weŇčgiya Hor ghar…®ghar…®niye Seir e t…®ne.
\s1 Rambarombaro Idom e t…®ne
\p 
\v 31 Amba muyai Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye va e lenji kiŇč, Idom e t…®ne kiŇč vama inanjiwe th…® mbaro. Iya idaidanjiyake:
\li1 
\v 32 Bela, iye Beor nariye. Va ina e ghemba Dinhaba na i mbaro Idom e t…®ne.
\li1 
\v 33 MbaŇča Bela i mare, Jobab iye Sera nariye i mena e ghemba idae Bosra kaero i roth…®gh…®va.
\li1 
\v 34 MbaŇča Jobab i mare, Husam iye i ri e val…®vaŇčga regha idae Timan kaero i roth…®gh…®va.
\li1 
\v 35 MbaŇča Husam i mare, Haded, iye Beded nariye kaero i tabona kiŇč…®va. Va i kivwalaŇčgiya Midiyan ghar…®ghar…®niye Mowab e t…®ne. Va i yaku e ghemba idae Avit na i mbarowe.
\li1 
\v 36 MbaŇča Haded i mare, Samla kaero i roth…®gh…®va. Iye i mena e ghemba regha idae Masreka.
\li1 
\v 37 MbaŇča Samla i mare, Saul kaero i roth…®gh…®va. Va i yaku e ghemba regha idae Rehobot ina e walagh…®ta\f + \fr 36:37 \ft Walagh…®take iyake mbwata idae Yupreitis.\f* ghadidiye.
\li1 
\v 38 MbaŇča Saul i mare, Baal-Hanan kaero i roth…®gh…®va. Iye Akba nariye.
\li1 
\v 39 MbaŇča Baal-Hanan, Akba nariye, i mare, Haded kaero i roth…®gh…®va na i tabo kiŇč. Va i yaku e ghemba regha idae Pau. Levo idae Mihitabel, Matred yawarumbuye na rumbuya Me-Saheb.
\b
\p 
\v 40-43 Wabwike thiyake ghanji riuriu r…®gheya Iso. Lenji randevivaŇčgi Timna, Alva, Jetet, Oholibama, Ela, Pinon, Kenas, Timan, Mib…®sa, Mag…®diyel na Iram. Thiyako th…® yaku Idom e t…®ne. Na ghambanji thivathivaniye idaidanji th…® mena weya lenji randeviva idaidanji.
\p Ghar…®ghar…®ke thiyake ghanjiwabwi r…®ghe Iso, Idom ghar…®ghar…®niye orumburumbunji.
\c 37
\s1 Josep le gheneloloŇčgi
\p 
\v 1 Jeikob vambe i yakuyaku vara Kenan e t…®ne Ňčgoreiye ramae va i yakukowe.
\p 
\v 2 Utuutuke iyake Jeikob riuriuniye.
\b
\p MbaŇča Josep ghatheghathegha vama i wo hoyaworo na umbopir…®, i wa ve njimbukikiŇčgiya sip na gout weiyaŇčgiya oghaghae, Bilha na Silpa lenji ŇčgaŇčga weinji ramae Jeikob. MbaŇča vavana Josep i utugiya weya ramanji, oghaghae lenji vakatha raithar…® utuniye.
\p 
\v 3 Isirel le gharethovu weya Josep i kivwala va le gharethovu weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčgako vavana, kaiwae Josep va i vir…® mbaŇčaniye amalagh…®niye kaero i amalagh…®sar…®. Iya kaiwae ramanji va i vakatha ghakwama thovuye moli, molao na n…®man…®ma tembe molamolaova.
\v 4 MbaŇča oghaghaema th…® thuwe ramanji mbe i gharethovuwe vara Josep na maa tembe reghava e t…®nenjiko, mbema th…® botewoyathu vara na maa tembe ghal…®Ňčanji i thovuye weva.
\p 
\v 5 Gougou regha Josep i ghenelolo, na mbaŇča i utugiya weŇčgiya oghaghaeko i vakathaŇčgi ma th…® botewayathu vara moli.
\v 6 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇče gheneloloke iya menda ya gheneloloŇčake.
\v 7 Mendava inanda wit e ghauma t…®ne, ra yavayavatha wit mbambara iya. IwaeŇčge wit…®ma mbambara iya ghino va ya yavathama i yondo vir…® na i ndevanavana ghamberegha. Ghemi lemi yavathama th…® rakagh…®liŇča ghinokowe na th…® kururuwe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Oghaghaeko th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKo uŇča eŇčge ne u tabo na kiŇč na u mbaroŇčainda?‚ÄĚ I vakatha weiye lenji gharegaith…® mbema th…® botewoyathu vara le gheneloloko na le utuutuko kaiwanji.
\p 
\v 9 Injana mbowa i gheneloloŇčava ghenelolo regha na i utugiya weŇčgiya oghaghaeko, iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu vandeŇčeŇčgo! Mbowa ma gheneloloŇčava ghenelolo regha. E mbaŇčako iyako varae, manjala na gh…®tara vogh…®yaworo na vogh…®ra th…® kururu e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Josep tembe i utugiyava le gheneloloko weya ramae, ko iyemaeŇčge ramae i govwara ghamwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúThe ghenelola iya u gheneloloŇčake? UŇča eŇčge t…®na, oghaghaeko na ghino ne wo kururu e ghen na wo vakatha ghan yavwatata?‚ÄĚ
\v 11 Josep oghaghae th…® yamwanja kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge ramae mbe i rerenuwaŇča vara gheneloloko kaiwae.
\s1 Josep oghaghae th…® vakuneŇča amalagh…®niye Ňčgoreiya rakakaiwobwaga
\p 
\v 12 MbaŇča regha Josep oghaghae vama th…® rakao th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya ramanji le sip na gout na vethiya ghan Sekem ghadidiye.
\v 13 Amba ramae i dage weya Josep, iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero u ghareghare, oghaghama th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya sip na gout na thiya ghan Sekem ghadidiye. Wo u vandeŇčeŇčgo, ya variyeŇčge na u wa weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúI thovuye moli.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Kaero ramae i dagewe, iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa na vo thuwe thoŇčgo riwanji mbe thovuye eŇčge na thoŇčgo sip na gout…®ko mbe th…® thovuye eŇčge. Amba u njoghama na u utugiya utuninji weŇčgo.‚ÄĚ Amba Josep i wareri Hebron malamoniye e t…®ne.
\p MbaŇča Josep ve vutha Sekem ele val…®vaŇčga,
\v 15 amala regha i vaidi i tamwetamwe loloŇčga oghaghae thetheghan…®ko e lenji ghamba ghan na i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúKo u tamweya budakai?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúYa tamwetamwe weŇčgiya oghaghaŇčguno. Th…® njimbukikiŇčgiya sip na gout thiya ghan. Thare u ghareghare aŇčga inanji?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amalama i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero mendava th…® roiteta iya val…®vaŇčgake iyake. Va ya loŇčwe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėRa raka Dotan.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p Josep i rereghamba weŇčgi oghaghaema na ve vaidiŇčgi Dotan ghadidiye.
\v 18 Ko mbaŇča th…® thuwe Josep i menamenako na amba e ghalughawoghawo weŇčgi, kaero th…® vona ghae na nuwanjiya th…® tagavamare.
\v 19 Kaero th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAhaa! Ragheneloloma maiya vara i menana.
\v 20 E mbaŇčake iyake ra tagavamare, na ra wokiyathumban e gogake iya ma mbwake inawe. Tene va rakwan na raŇča, ‚ÄėThetheghan mbwanjam menda i ghan.‚Äô Na wo ra thuweno budakai ne th…® yomara ele gheneloloŇčgiko.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 MbaŇča Rubin i loŇčwe utuutuko iyako i mando na i vamoru oghaghaeko e n…®manji ghare. I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava ra tagavamare.‚ÄĚ
\v 22 Mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThava madibe ina e n…®mamina. Mbema hu wokiyathunjoŇča eŇčge e gogake iya maa mbwake inawe na mbe i yakuwe na thava tembe n…®mami i waweva.‚ÄĚ Rubin i utu Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae va le renuwaŇča nuwaiya i vamoru e n…®manji na i vaŇčgunjogha weya ramae.
\p 
\v 23 MbaŇča Josep i vutha weŇčgi oghaghae th…® ndelawelawe e n…®manji, th…® thethe ghakwamama ghayaboyabo iya molaoma ramae va i vakatha wagiyawema na i njimbo.
\v 24 Kaero th…® wo na th…® dunjoŇča gogama iya maa mbwama inawe. \fig Kaero th…® wo na th…® dunjoŇča gogama iya maa mbwama inawe|src="CO00705B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="37:24"\fig*
\p 
\v 25 Oghaghaema kaero thiya ghan…®Ňčga. E lenji ghan…®Ňčgako t…®ne th…® tagath…®na maranji kaero th…® thuweŇčgiya Ismel ghar…®ghar…®niye vavana amba th…® menamenako e lenji kamel. Th…® rakamena Giliyad ele val…®vaŇčga. Kamel…®ko va th…® doweŇčgiya bigibigi butinji thovuye e vwatanji Ňčgoreiya gam, bal…®m na mer. Va veth…® vakuneŇčaŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 26 Amba Juda i dage weŇčgiya oghaghaeko iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ŇčgoroŇčga ghathovuyako weinda thoŇčgo ra tagavamara ghaghandako, ra wothuwole riwaeko na ra ravunyivunyiya le mareko utuniye?
\v 27 Ra vakuneŇča eŇčge weŇčgiya Ismel ghar…®ghar…®niye na thava tembe n…®manda i waweva. Wo hu thuwe mbe ghindake vara ghaghanda na mbun…®ma na madibeko iyako, iya weindake.‚ÄĚ Amba th…® varaeŇčna na th…® vakatha iyako.
\p 
\v 28 MbaŇča Midiya rakunekune vavana th…® mena evasiwanji, kaero veth…® momod…® voreŇča ghaghanji Josep e gogama t…®ne na th…® vaŇčgugiya weŇčgiya Ismel ghar…®ghar…®niyema. Amaamalako th…® giya modae le lagh…®lagh…®ye silva geth…®yeiwo. Amba th…® vaŇčgu na th…® wa Ijipt.
\p 
\v 29 Amba Rubin i njogha weŇčgi na i wa ve kela e gogama. Marae i nja Josep maa ina gheko. Ghatemuru kaiwae i mwanathethe ghakwama.
\v 30 I njogha weŇčgiya oghaghaema na iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägamama maa ina gheko? Ne ŇčgoroŇčga wo ghaŇčgoghaŇčgo?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Josep oghaghae th…® un…®gha gout gh…®moru umbwara, kaero th…® liya ghakwamama ghayaboyabo na th…® liutu gout…®ko e mad…®bae.
\v 32 Th…® liya kwamako ghayaboyabo na veth…® livatomwe weya ramanji. Kaero th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMo vaidiya kwamake iyake. Mbowo u thuwe. Mbwata naru lema Josep ghakwama ghayaboyabo o nandere?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 MbaŇča Jeikob i thuwe wagiyawe kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčguma Josep ghakwama ghayaboyabo iyake! Emunjora mbwanjam tagaith…® mendava i tagavamare na i ten…®ghan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 34 Weiye le nuwathar…® lagh…®ye i mwana thetheŇčgiya ghakwama, i njimbo kwama bwedibwedi e mborowae na i nuwathar…® lagh…®ye mbaŇča molao nariye Josep kaiwae.
\v 35 Le ŇčgaŇčgako wolagh…®ye th…® raka menawe na th…® munjeva th…® vakatha gharemal…®l…®we (th…® th…®n…®njoŇča ghare) na nuwathar…®ko iko. Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob i botewa na mbe i randaranda vara. I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbene weiŇčgu vara lo nuwathar…® na ya randaranda ghaghad ne ya mare na ya wa weŇčgiya ramaremare, iya naruŇčguko inawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 36 MbaŇča Midiya rakunekune veth…® raka vutha Ijipt, th…® vakuneŇča weya Potipa. Amalake iyake iye Pero le rakakaiwo lagh…®ye regha. Amalagh…®niye iye gharagat…®gat…® lenji randeviva.
\c 38
\s1 Juda na Tama
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča ubotu e ghereiye, Juda i iteteŇčgiya ogaghae na i nja ve yaku weiye amala regha idae Hira e ghemba idae Adulam.
\v 2 Gheko Juda i thuwe wevo eunda t…®nan Kenan ramae idae Sua. I vaŇčgu na i ghena weiye.
\v 3 Wevoko i marabo na i ghamb…® Ňčgama gh…®moru. I rena idae Er.
\v 4 Muyai mbowo i ghamb…®va, na tembe Ňčgama gh…®moruva. I rena idae Onan.
\v 5 Injana mbowo i marabova na tembe i ghamb…®va Ňčgama gh…®moru. I rena idae Sila. Ňägamake iyake va ve vir…® e ghemba regha idae Kesib.
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča Er kaero i thamatuwo, Juda nariye vir…®viva, kaero ramae i tuthiya levo, idae Tama.
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge Juda nariye vir…®viva le vakatha mbema thar…® eŇčge vara Loi e marae. Iya kaiwae Loi i vakatha na i mare.
\p 
\v 8 IwaeŇčge Juda i dage weya nariye Onan, Er ghaghae, iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčgwa ghaghako lagh…®yeniye ghembwiye na u vamboromboro ghanda thanavu me mena orumburumbunda weŇčgi. Kaiwae mbe ghagha levo, mbala u ghamb…® wein ghaghako kaiwae.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge Onan va i ghareghare gamagaiko ne th…® ghamb…®ko weiye maane amalagh…®niye idae ina weŇčgi; iya kaiwae mbaŇča i ghena weiye wambwiko riwaeko dimithiye i liŇčgiyathu eto mbala wambwiko maa i marabo na i ghamb…® gamagai ghaghaema kaiwae.
\v 10 Le vakathako kaiwae Loi maa i warari iya kaiwae tembe i vakatha na i mareva.
\p 
\v 11 Amba Juda i dage weya ghendiyae Tama iŇča, ‚ÄúU njogha weya rama na len bodaboda na wo vo yaku weinaŇčgi, ko thava ne u ghe, na naruŇčguke Sila wo i thamatuwo.‚ÄĚ Kaiwae le renuwaŇčako va iŇča, ‚ÄúNe iwaeŇčge mbowo i mareva Ňčgoreiya oghaghaeko.‚ÄĚ Tama i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Juda le renuwaŇčako.
\p 
\v 12 MbaŇča molao kaero iko na e ghereiye Juda levo iye Sua yawarumbuye, i mare. MbaŇča le nuwathar…®ko ghambaŇča kaero iko, amba i voro Tim…®na weŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru th…® tena le sip…®ko vulivulinji wul kaiwae. Hira, rara Adulam, Juda le n…®ma, vambe weiyeva.
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča lolo regha i dage weya Tama iŇča, ‚ÄúGhendiyae Juda i wareri i wa Tim…®na ve tena le sip…®ko vulivulinji wul kaiwae,‚ÄĚ
\v 14 iwaeŇčge i biginjoŇča wambwima kwamaniye, i liyabo riwae e kwama ulu ghayaboyabo na i wothuwole ghayamoyamo. Ko amba ve yaku e kamwath…® ruru Enain, e kamwath…® i voro Tim…®na. Kaiwae vama i thuwe Sila kaero i thamatuwo, ko iyemaeŇčge ghendiyae maa i vaŇčgugiyawe na le gh…®moru.
\p 
\v 15 MbaŇča Juda i thuwe le renuwaŇča iŇčaeŇčge wevo i vavakuneŇča riwae, kaiwae i yabo ghamwae.
\v 16 Kaiwae Juda mava ele ghareghare elako amalagh…®niye ghendiyae, iwaeŇčge i loŇčga ghembe e kamwath…®ko ghadidiye na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena e mbaŇčake iyake na ya ghena weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p Elako i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe u giya modaŇčgu budakai?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya variya gout nariye elo sip na gout…®ko t…®nenji.‚ÄĚ
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge elako i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae u giyama bigi regha e ghino na ne i vaemunjoruŇča dagerawena ne u variya gout…®na nariye e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Juda i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaniya ya woveŇčge budakai?‚ÄĚ
\p I gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNuwaŇčguiya ghan nonona weiye ghathiyona na pwasikena iya e n…®man…®na.‚ÄĚ Kaero i giyawe na i vamboromboro Juda le renuwaŇčako. E vakathako iyako Tama i marabo.
\v 19 E ghereiye Tama i njogha, i biginjoŇča ulu ghayaboyabo na kaero i njimbova wambwima kwamaniye.
\p 
\v 20 MbaŇča Juda ve vutha weŇčgiya rakakaiwoma, i tuthiya gout nariye tabwagha regha, kaero i variye weiye le n…®ma Hira na mbala ve biginjogha me le dagerawema i giya le bigibigima weya elama. Ko iyemaeŇčge le nima maa ve vaidi.
\v 21 IwaeŇčge i vaitoŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moru thiya yaku gheko iŇča, ‚ÄúAŇčga ina elama i vakuneŇča riwaema e yathima thanavuniye?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® thombenjoghawe, th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMa wevo i vakuneŇča riwae ina gheke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Kaero i njoghava weya Juda na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa ma vaidi mun. Gh…®mogh…®moru inanji e ghembako iyako meth…® dage e ghino th…®Ňča, ‚ÄėMa tembe wevo regha i vakuneŇča riwae iri gheke.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Juda i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúU viyathu na i mbana budakai menda ya giyanawe. Thava tembe ra tamwe mbeleva, ne iwaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® th…® loŇčwevaidi na th…® vav…®r…®inda. Kaero ma mando na ya vamboromboro le renuwaŇča na ma variye gout…®ma, ko iyemaeŇčge maa mo vaidi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 24 Manjala umboto e ghereiye lolo regha i utugiya weya Juda iŇča, ‚ÄúGhendiyae Tama mendava i vakatha yathima thanavuniye, na mbaŇčake kaero i marabo.‚ÄĚ
\p Juda iŇča, ‚ÄúHu vaŇčguraŇčgiyama etoke na ra Ňčambu vamare e nd…®ghe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča veth…® vaŇčguraŇčgiya kaero i variye totoke iyake weya ghendiyae iŇča, ‚ÄúGh…®moruke iya le bigibigiya thiyake iye va weiŇčgu, iya maraboniyake.‚ÄĚ Na i gotubweva iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowo u thuwe bigibigike thiyake. Thela le bigibigi? Ghanono weiye ghathiyo na pwasike.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 MbaŇča Juda i thuwe bigibigiko theghetoko na i ghareghare amalagh…®niyewe, iwaeŇčge iŇča, ‚ÄúTama le vakatha i emunjoru, ko iyemaeŇčge ghino lo thar…®, kaiwae mava ya vaŇčgugiya naruŇčguko Sila weya elagh…®niye na le gh…®moru.‚ÄĚ Na ande teva i ghenareva weiye Tama.
\p 
\v 27 MbaŇča kaero ghambaŇča ghamb…®, gh…®mogh…®moru theghewo gamwaruwoŇčgi va inanji e Ňčgamoiye.
\v 28 Tama ele ghamb…®ko t…®ne Ňčgamako regha i liraŇčgiya n…®mae regha, ravavaghamb…®ko eunda i li thiyo sosoro nasiye na i Ňčgar…® e n…®maeko amba iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägamake iyake ne i vir…®kai.‚ÄĚ
\v 29 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča i liruwo njogha n…®mae ghaghaeko i vir…®kai, iwaeŇčge ravavaghamb…® iŇča, ‚ÄúKo ana ghen u vir…®viva weva ghaghana!‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae th…® rena idae Peres.
\v 30 Amba ghaghaema thiyoma nasiye sosoro ina e n…®mae i vir…®, na th…® rena idae Sera.
\c 39
\s1 Josep na Potipa levo
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇčaniye Ismel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vamodo Josep kaero th…® vaŇčgu na veth…® vaŇčguvutha Ijipt e t…®ne. Gheko kaero veth…® vakuneŇčava weya giya regha, Pero e raberabe, idae Potipa. Iye lolo lagh…®ye regha. KiŇč Pero gharagat…®gat…® lenji randeviva.
\p 
\v 2 \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe weiye vara Josep na i vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye mbe i thovuye eŇčge vara ele vakathako t…®ne. Josep va i yaku na i kaiwo ghagiya Potipa e le Ňčgolo t…®ne.
\v 3 MbaŇča Josep ghagiyako kaero i njimbuvaidiya le vakathako wolagh…®ye e t…®ne mbe i thovuye eŇčge vara, i ghareghare \nd Giya Loi\nd* va weiye na i vakatha le kaiwoko i thovuye moli;
\v 4 i vakatha i warari lagh…®ye moli kaiwae na i worawe i tabo amalagh…®niye val…®n…®mae. Ghagiyako kaero i vatomwewe na i mbaroŇča bigibigiko wolagh…®ye ele Ňčgolo t…®ne na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e ghayayaoko.
\v 5 MbaŇčaniye vara Potipa i worawa Josep na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye thiya kaiwo ele Ňčgoloko na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye e ghayayaoko t…®ne, \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha amalako le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye thiya thovuye moli. \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewo weŇčgiya Potipa le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye inanji ele Ňčgoloko t…®ne, na le umaumako th…® madi.
\v 6 Potipa i viyatho le bigibigiko wolagh…®ye weya Josep i njimbukiki. Potipa maa tembe i rerenuwaŇčava bigi regha kaiwae, mbema ghan…®Ňčgako eŇčge vara iya i ghan…®ko.
\p Josep va thav…®ndondo wamandondo na ghayamoyamo i thovuye na man…®une.
\v 7 IwaeŇčge i tagawo Potipa levo nuwae. Ko maa mbaŇča bwagabwaga kaero i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena va ghena weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josep i botewa elako na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúWo giyako kaero menda i viyatho bigibigike wolagh…®ye ele Ňčgoloke t…®ne na ghino ya mbaroŇča. Menda i vareminjeŇčgo na ya njimbukikiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye iya amalagh…®niyekewe.
\v 9 Ma tembe lolo regha inava e Ňčgoloke t…®ne i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgo. Amalako maa menda tembe i ravaghava bigi regha e ghino; mbe ghen eŇčge vara, kaiwae levo ghen. Ne ŇčgoroŇčga na ya vakatha thanavu Ňčgoreiyako na ya thar…® Loi e marae?‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Elako mbe i vothaŇča vara Josep mbaŇča regha na regha e t…®ne, ko iyemaeŇčge i botewayatho le naŇčgokowe na maa i ghena weiye. I mando na i vaghaghaiŇča ghamberegha weya Potipa levo.
\p 
\v 11 Va mbaŇča regha Josep i ru e Ňčgoloko t…®ne na i vakatha ghakaiwowe. Le val…®rakakaiwo mava regha mun ina gheko.
\v 12 IwaeŇčge elako i laweghath…® e ghakwama na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU mena ya ghena weiŇčgu ghen.‚ÄĚ Ko iyemaeŇčge Josep i vogha raŇčgi eto na i vogha iteta elako, mbe i rondelili eŇčge ghakwama ghayaboyabo. \fig I vogha iteta elako, mbe i rondelili eŇčge ghakwama ghayaboyabo|src="CO00715B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="39:12"\fig*
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča i thuwe me iteta ghakwama ghayaboyabo na i voraŇčgi eto,
\v 14 kaero i kula weŇčgiya le Ňčgoloko gharakakaiwo na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe! Iya rara Hibruna iya lo gh…®moruke va i vaŇčgurawe e Ňčgoloke i vakatha monjina lagh…®ye weinda. Me mena i ru elo woluwoluke t…®ne na i munjeva i laweŇčgo na i vakatha le renuwaŇča e ghino, ko iyemaeŇčge ma mareŇčwanji lagh…®ye moli.
\v 15 MbaŇča me loŇčwe ma Ňčwanjiko, i vogha raŇčgi eto na i voiteta ghakwama ghayaboyabo evasiwaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Elako mbe i vikikighath…® vara kwamako ghaghad Josep ghagiyako i njoghama e Ňčgoloko.
\v 17 Amba i utugiya utuutumawe iŇča, ‚ÄúIya rara Hibru Ňčgoloke gharakakaiwo mendava u vaŇčgurawe e Ňčgoloke me vakatha monjina e ghino.
\v 18 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča ma mareŇčwanji i vogha raŇčgi eto na i iteta ghakwama ghayaboyabo evasiwaŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 MbaŇča amalako i loŇčwe utuutuko iyako weya levo, ghare i gaith…® lagh…®ye moli.
\v 20 Josep ghagiyako iŇča na veth…® vaŇčguruwo e thiyoko Ňčgora thavala th…® vakatha vathar…® weya kiŇč…®ko na veth…® ruwe.
\p Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča Josep ina e thiyo t…®ne,
\v 21 \nd Giya Loi\nd* i mwaewowe na i thalavu. Iyako i wo thiyoko gharambarombaro nuwae na i warari kaiwae.
\v 22 Iya kaiwae thiyoko gharambarombaro i worawa Josep na i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya thavala inanji e thiyoko t…®ne, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva e vakathako wolagh…®ye gheko.
\v 23 Thiyoko gharambarombaro mava tembe i rerenuwaŇčava the bigiya vama i vatomwe weya Josep na i njimbukiki, kaiwae \nd Giya Loi\nd* vambe weiye vara na ele vakathako wolagh…®ye \nd Giya Loi\nd* i vakatha na i emunjoru.
\c 40
\s1 Josep i vagh…®le raruru e thiyo lenji ghenelolo
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča vavana e ghereiye, Ijipt ghakiŇč le rakakaiwo theghewo, regha kiŇč…®ko ghawaen gharavivatha na regha bred gharaŇčambuŇčambu ‚ÄĒ th…® vakatha vathar…® bigi regha kiŇč…®ko e marae na i vakatha maa i warari.
\v 2 IwaeŇčge ghare i gaith…® wanaŇčgi
\v 3 na i dage weya gharagat…®gat…®ko lenji randeviva i vaŇčguruwoŇčgi e thiyo. Thiyoko iyako iya Josep va inakowe.
\v 4 KiŇč…®ko gharagat…®gat…® lenji randeviva i yovaŇčguŇčgi weya Josep na i dagewe i njimbukikiŇčgi e bigibigiko wolagh…®ye.
\p MbaŇča gheviye vama lenji yakuyaku gheko na e ghereiye,
\v 5 mbe theghewoko vara ‚ÄĒ kiŇč…®ko ghawaen gharavivatha na ghabred gharaŇčambuŇčambu th…® ghenelolo gougou mbe reghaeŇčge. Lenji gheneloloko mbe tomethi ghanjirumwaru.
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča Josep i mena weŇčgi mbaŇčambaŇčako iyako i thuweŇčgi th…® yawowo.
\v 7 I vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae ghamiyamoyamo i yawowo noroke?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúMbe thamaghewoke vara mo ghenelolo gougou, ko iyemaeŇčge maa lolo regha ina gheko na val…®kaiwae i vagh…®leŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p Amba Josep i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi mbe ghambereghaeŇčge val…®kaiwae i vaghagh…®leŇčgiya ghenelolo. Wo hu utu giyama e ghino mo hu thuweŇčgiya budakai.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Kaero waen…®ma gharavakatha i utugiya le gheneloloma weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúLo gheneloloko e t…®ne ma thuwe waen ghathiyo yaŇčgara e ghamwaŇčgu.
\v 10 Na e umbwarako iyako yaŇčgayaŇčga yaŇčgato. MbaŇča ndamwandamwaeko th…® voviya kaero th…® vunyenye, kaero vunyevunyeuyeko th…® dobu na uneune th…® yomara.
\v 11 Pero ghakomu mena e n…®maŇčgu. Ya mbana uneuneko kaero ya imb…® mban e komuko t…®ne na ya th…®n…®rawe Pero e n…®mae.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Josep i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúLen ghenelolona gharumwaru Ňčgoreiyake. YaŇčgayaŇčgaena yaŇčgatona gharumwaru mbaŇča thegheto.
\v 13 MbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne kiŇč…®ko ne iŇča na u raŇčgi na u wawe. Ne u njogha na tembe vo vakathava kaiwoma va u vakavakathama. Tembe ne u vivathava kiŇč…®ko ghawaen na u giyawe.
\v 14 Aee, wou, ago lagh…®ye e ghen, mbaŇča bigibigike wolagh…®ye ne ve thovuye e ghen, u renuwaŇčakikiŇčgo na gharen e ghino. Mbala vo govambwaraŇčgo weya kiŇč…®na na val…®kaiwae tembe ya raŇčgiva e thiyoke t…®ne.
\v 15 Wo u thuwe, ghar…®ghar…® va th…® vaŇčgu kav…®Ňčgo Hibru e lenji val…®vaŇčga na othembe gheke maa ya vakatha vathar…® mun bigi regha na val…®kaiwae th…® vaŇčgu ruwoŇčgo e thiyoke t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča bred…®ma gharaŇčambuŇčambu i loŇčwevaidi Josep le vagh…®le gheneloloko i thovuye, tembe i dageweva Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, menda ya ghenelolo. Elo gheneloloko t…®ne, ya bigiya nambonambo Ňčgamwato e umbal…®Ňčgu, bred inanjiwe.
\v 17 E vwatako vara tomethi ghan…®Ňčga ŇčambuŇčambu kiŇč…®ko kaiwae inanjiwe. Ko iyemaeŇčge maa th…® yonja na th…® ghan mbaŇča mbe ina e umbal…®Ňčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 18 Josep i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhenelolona iyana gharumwaru Ňčgoreiyake. Nambonambo Ňčgamwatona iye mbaŇča thegheto.
\v 19 MbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne Pero ne iŇča na th…® vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčge na th…® yovaŇčguŇčge weya amalagh…®niye. Amba ne iŇča na th…® kitena numon…®na na th…® wovakwata riwan…®na e umbwa, na maa th…® mena th…® ghana mbun…®manina.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 MbaŇča thegheto e ghereiye Pero le ghamb…® gharenuwaŇčakiki. I vakatha thaganiye na i kula vathavathaŇčgiya le rakakaiwoko wolagh…®ye th…® raka mena e thagako iyako t…®ne. KiŇč…®ko iŇča na th…® vaŇčgumena ghawaen gharavivatha na bred gharaŇčambuŇčambuma weya amalagh…®niye na le rakakaiwoko wolagh…®ye e maranji.
\v 21 I vaŇčgunjogha ghawaen…®ma gharavivatha ele ghamba kaiwoma na i njogha na tembe i vakathava kaiwoma va i vakavakathamawe,
\v 22 ko iyemaeŇčge iŇča na th…® wovakwata raŇčambuŇčambuma. Iyako va i yomara Ňčgoreiya Josep va le utuutu weŇčgi mbaŇča va i vagh…®le lenji gheneloloma.
\p 
\v 23 Ko iyemaeŇčge kiŇč…®ma ghawaen gharavivatha i renuwaŇča vaghalawe Josep. Mbema i renuwaŇča valawe vara.
\c 41
\s1 Pero le ghenelolo
\p 
\v 1 Theghathegha umboiwo vama th…®ko na e ghereiye amba Pero i ghenelolo ghenelolo regha. E gheneloloko t…®ne va i ndeghath…® e Walagh…®ta Nael ghadidiye.
\v 2 E mbaŇčako iyako burumwaka umbopir…®, ghanjitabo vond…®vond…® na riwanji vunevune, th…® raka voroma e walagh…®tako t…®ne kaero thiya ghana nana gheko.
\v 3 E ghereinji mbowo burumwaka umbopir…®va th…® raka voro e walagh…®tako t…®ne, ghanji tabo i nja na mbe ŇčgaŇčgainji eŇčge. Th…® raka mena na th…® ndeghath…® burumwakama vavanama evasiwanji e walagh…®tako ghadidiye.
\v 4 Kaero burumwakama iya ŇčgaŇčgainjima eŇčge th…® ghan…®Ňčgiya burumwakama ghanjitaboma vond…®vond…®. Amba Pero i thuweiru.
\p 
\v 5 Injana mbowo i ghenava na tembe i ghenelolova. E t…®ne i thuwe iyake: Wit siŇčwepir…®, ghanjiyamoyamo i thovuye moli na wok…®ninji mbe regha eŇčge.
\v 6 Iyako e ghereiye wit siŇčwepir…® mbe th…® th…®n…® raŇčgiyava ‚ÄĒ wak…®niye mbe nasiye na ndewendewe i mena e boimako i Ňčambwa ndamwandamwaeko.
\v 7 Wit…®ko wak…®niyeko nanasiye th…® mban…®voŇčguŇčgiya wit…®ma ghanjitaboma i thovuye na siŇčwe lagh…®lagh…®ye. Amba Pero i thuweiruva na e mbaŇčako iyako i ghareghare me ghenelolo.
\p 
\v 8 Igh…®viya Pero ghayamoyamo maa i warari mun. Kaero i variye utu weŇčgiya thavala man…®yeto na rathimbathimba Ijipt e t…®ne na th…® raka menawe. Pero i utugiya le gheneloloma weŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge maa tembe reghava val…®kaiwae i vagh…®lewe.
\p 
\v 9 Amba kiŇč…®ko ghawaen…®ma gharavivatha i dage weya Pero iŇča, ‚ÄúNoroke ya renuwaŇčakikiya lo thar…® regha.
\v 10 Va mbaŇča regha gharen i gaith…® wanaime weiŇčgu raŇčambuŇčambuma, iwaeŇčge u bigi ruwoime e thiyo ghan ragat…®gat…®ma lenji randeviva ele Ňčgolo.
\v 11 Gougou regha mbe thamaghewoko vara wo ghenelolo, na lama gheneloloko vambe tomethi ghanjirumwaru.
\v 12 Amala regha tabwagha va ina gheko. Iye Hibru loloniye, ghan…®ragat…®gat…®na lenji randeviva va le rakakaiwo. Va wo utugiyawa lama gheneloloko na i vagh…®la ghanjirumwaruko weime.
\v 13 Bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va i mboromboro Ňčgoreiya va le varumwaruko weime. Ghino u vaŇčgu njoghaŇčgo e wo kaiwoko na wouko uŇča na th…® kiten numwe na th…® wovakwate riwae e umbwa.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Pero i variya utu Josep kaiwae na mbema ghenji na n…®manji eŇčge veth…® vaŇčguraŇčgiya e thiyoko t…®ne. Ve kwe ghabath…® na i njimbo kwama thovuye, kaero i wa ve ndeghath…® Pero e marae.
\p 
\v 15 Pero i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúMendava ya ghenelola ghenelolo regha, na maa lolo regha i vagh…®le. Ko iyemaeŇčge mendava ya loŇčwevaidi ghen val…®kaiwan u vagh…®leŇčgi ghenelolo ghanjirumwaru, iya kaiwae ma variye utu kaiwan.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Josep i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino maa val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya vakatha, ko iyemaeŇčge Loi ne i giya vagh…®le thovuye e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amba Pero i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúElo gheneloloko t…®ne va ya ndeghath…® e walagh…®ta Nael ghadidiye,
\v 18 na e mbaŇčako iyako burumwaka umbopir…®, ghanjitabo vond…®vond…® na riwanji vunevune, th…® rakavoroma e walagh…®tako t…®ne na thiya ghana nana gheko.
\v 19 E ghereinji mbowo burumwaka umbopir…®va th…® raka voroma e walagh…®tako t…®ne, ghanjitabo i nja na mbe ŇčgaŇčgainji eŇčge. Maa tembe mbaŇča reghava ya thuweŇčgiya burumwaka ghanjiyamoyamo raithar…® moli Ňčgoreiyako Ijipt lagh…®yeko e t…®ne.
\v 20 Burumwakama ŇčgaŇčgainjima eŇčge th…® ghan…®Ňčgiya burumwakama umbopir…®ma iya ghanjitaboma vond…®vond…® iya meth…® rakavorokaima.
\v 21 Ko iyemaeŇčge othembe th…® ghan…®Ňčgiya vavanako ghanjitaboko mbe Ňčgoreiye vara iyako. E ghereiye amba ya thuweiru.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúKaero ya gheneva. Na injana mbowo ya ghenelolova. E gheneloloko iyako ya thuwe wit siŇčwepir…® ghanjiyamoyamo i thovuye moli na wak…®ninji mbe regha eŇčge.
\v 23 Iyako e ghereiye wit siŇčwepir…® mbowo th…® th…®n…® raŇčgiyava ‚ÄĒ wak…®niye me nasiye na ndewendewe i mena e boimako i Ňčambwa ndamwandamwaeko.
\v 24 Wit…®ko wok…®ninjiko nasiye th…® mban…®voŇčguŇčgiya wit…®ma ghanjitaboma i thovuye na siŇčwe lagh…®lagh…®ye. Ma utugiya weŇčgiya thavala man…®yetoŇčgi, ko iyemaeŇčge maa tembe reghava val…®kaiwae i vamanjamanjalaŇča e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Amba Josep i dage weya Pero iŇča, ‚ÄúPero, len ghenelolona theghewona ghanjirumwaru mbe regha eŇčge. Loi me vatomwe ghen budakai ne i vakatha.
\v 26 Iya burumwakana umbopir…®na ghanjitabo vond…®vond…®, iyana theghathegha umbopir…®. Na iya wit…®na siŇčwe lagh…®lagh…®yena na th…® thovuyena tembe theghathegha umbopir…®va; na ghanjirumwaru mbe regha eŇčge.
\v 27 Iya burumwakana umbopir…®na na ŇčgaŇčgainjina eŇčge na th…® rakavoro muyaina na wit…®na siŇčwepir…® wak…®ninji mbe nasiye na uneune mbe nanasiye ‚ÄĒ iya ndewendewe i mena e boimako i Ňčambu ndamwandamwaena ‚ÄĒ iyana theghathegha umbopir…® ne vunuvu ghambaŇča.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 ‚ÄúŇägora kaero ma utuma e ghen. Loi kaero me vatomwe e ghen budakaiya ne i vakatha.
\v 29 Theghathegha umbopir…® e t…®ne madi ne ghambaŇča Ijipt lagh…®yeke e t…®ne.
\v 30 Ko iyemaeŇčge ne e ghereiye theghathegha umbopir…® vunuvu ghambaŇča. Madi ghatheghathegha nevole gharerenuwaŇča i ghawe ghar…®ghar…® e nuwanji, kaiwae vunuvuko mbema ne i vakowana vara vanautumako lagh…®ye.
\v 31 Madima ghambaŇča nevole th…® renuwaŇča vaghalawe moli, kaiwae vunuvuko iya e ghereiyeko mbema ne i thar…® moli vara.
\v 32 Ghenelolona theghewo r…®ghe kaiwae Loi nuwaiya hu ghareghare iyake ne i yomara, na ne i vakatha, maiya vara ken…®.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae e mbaŇčake iyake, KiŇč Pero, u tuthiya amala regha nuwae i goi na i thimba, na u vaŇčgurawe i mbaroŇča Ijipt lagh…®yeke.
\v 34 Na tembe u tuthiŇčgiva giyagiya vavanava na th…® mbana wit weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ijipt lagh…®yeke e t…®ne mbaŇča madiko ghatheghathegha umbopir…® e t…®nenji. Wone th…® wabwi na wabwilima wit…®ko na th…® mbana wabura weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na th…® mban ghaghath…®.
\v 35 Ne u giya giyagiyako ghanjimbaro na th…® mban…® vatha ghan…®Ňčgako madiko e ghatheghathegha t…®nenji iya i menamenako. Ghen e idan th…® vathe wit e ghanjiŇčgoloŇčgolo e ghembaghemba regha na regha t…®ne na mbe maranjiwe vara.
\v 36 Ghan…®Ňčgako iyako mbala i tabona thaŇčwethaŇčwe unmariye vanautumake kaiwae. Iyako ne ra vakaiwoŇča vunuvuko ghatheghathegha umbopir…® e t…®ne iya ne i Ňčge Ijipt lagh…®yeke. E kamwath…®ke iyake amba ne ma bada i gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Josep i tabo gawana Ijipt e t…®ne
\p 
\v 37 RenuwaŇčako iyako ghathuwathuwa i thovuye weya Pero na le rakakaiwoko wolagh…®ye.
\v 38 Kaero Pero i vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare val…®kaiwae ne ra vaidiya lolo regha Ňčgoreiya amalake iyake, iya Loi uneke inawe?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 39 Amba Pero i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Loi i vakathaŇčge na u ghareghare iyake, maa tembe lolo reghava nuwae i goi na i thimba Ňčgoreiya ghen.
\v 40 Ne ya vaŇčguraweŇčge na u mbaroŇča lo vanautumake, na lo ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® ghambugha len mbarona. Len mbarona le vur…®gheghe i mena mbe ghino eŇčge e raberabeŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 41 Kaero Pero i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake ya vaŇčguraweŇčge na u tabo gawana Ijipt lagh…®yeke e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\v 42 Pero i woraŇčgiya n…®mae kikiye ghae ghamba mbaroko ghanono inawe, na i worawe Josep e n…®mae kikiye. I vanjimbo e kwama thovuye moli na i wokitho numwe ghae gol.
\v 43 I yambigiya weya Josep le sariyot theghewoniye i thawe na kiŇč…®ko gharagat…®gat…® th…® raka viva e ghamwae na th…® vakatha ghayavwatata na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúHu kururuwe! Hu kururuwe!‚ÄĚ Pero kaero i tuthiya Josep na iye i tabo gawana Ijipt lagh…®yeko t…®ne.
\p 
\v 44 Amba Pero i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Pero, Ijipt lenji kiŇč, ko iyemaeŇčge maa lolo regha Ijipt e t…®ne ne i vakatha bigi regha ma u vatomwewe.‚ÄĚ
\v 45 Pero i rena Ijipt idaniye, Sepanat Peniya, weya Josep na i vaŇčgugiya Asenat weya amalagh…®niye na levo. Elako iyako Potipa yawarumbuye, iye ghemba On lenji ravowovowo. Josep i vagh…®liya Ijipt lagh…®yeko.
\p 
\v 46 Josep ghatheghathegha vama i wo ghweto mbaŇčaniye i ru i kaiwo weya Pero, Ijipt lenji kiŇč. Kaiwo e t…®ne i roiteta Pero na i vagh…®liya Ijipt lagh…®yeko.
\v 47 Madi ghatheghathegha umbopir…® e t…®ne thelauko ghan…®Ňčganiye i rau lagh…®ye moli.
\v 48 Wolagh…®yeko iyako Josep i mban…® vathavatha na i vathe e ghembaghembako. E ghemba regha na regha t…®ne i vathe ghan…®Ňčga e val…®vaŇčgako iyako.
\v 49 Wit…®ko va i lagh…®ye na i ghanagha moli maa val…®kaiwae Josep tembe i r…®gh…®va Ňčgoreiya kerakera e njigh…®ko ghadidiye.
\p 
\v 50 Va e mbaŇčako iyako na amba muyai vunuvuko ghatheghathegha th…® mena, Josep le ŇčgaŇčga vama theghewo, th…® ghamb…® weya Asenat, Potipa yawarumbuye iye On lenji ravowovowo.
\v 51 Josep i rena nariye vir…®viva idae Manase. IŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Loi i vakathaŇčgo ya renuwaŇča vaghalawe wo vuyowoma wolagh…®ye na bwebwe le bodaboda.‚ÄĚ
\v 52 Nariye theghewoniye i rena idae Ip…®reim, na iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Loi i vakathaŇčgo ya ghamb…® e val…®vaŇčga ya vaidiya vuyowowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 53 Madima ghatheghathegha umbopir…®ma kaero iko vara iyake,
\v 54 na vunuvuma ghatheghathegha umbopir…® i worawe r…®ghe, Ňčgoreiya Josep va le utuutuma. Vunuvuko iyako vambe ve wova vanautuma vavana, ko iyemaeŇčge Ijipt lagh…®yeko e t…®ne ghan…®Ňčga vambe inawe.
\v 55 MbaŇča Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® gham…®noa vunuvuko gham…®na, veth…® goyawaru weya Pero ghan…®Ňčga kaiwae. I variyeŇčgi na th…® raka weya Josep na veth…® vakatha budakaiya ne i utuŇča weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 56 MbaŇča vunuvuko kaero i lagh…®ye moli na i wo vanautumako lagh…®ye, Josep kaero i vugh…®Ňčgiya ghan…®Ňčgama ghaŇčgoloŇčgolo na i vakuneŇča wit weŇčgiya Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye, kaiwae vunuvuko vama i vur…®gheghe moli Ijipt lagh…®yeko e t…®ne.
\v 57 Ghar…®ghar…® vambe th…® rakaraka menava e yambaneke lagh…®ye na th…® vamodo wit weya Josep, kaiwae vunuvuko vambe i vur…®gheghe e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye.
\c 42
\s1 Josep oghaghae th…® raka Ijipt na veth…® bayama wit
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Jeikob i loŇčwe vaidiya wit ina Ijipt, kaero i dage weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae mane hu vakatha bigi regha?
\v 2 Mendava ya loŇčwevaidiya wit utuniye ina Ijipt. Hu raka gheko na vohu vamodo vavana kaiwanda, na val…®kaiwae i ndewoinda na thava raya mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 IwaeŇčge Josep oghaghae theyaworoma thiya wareri, th…® raka Ijipt na veth…® bayama wit.
\v 4 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob mava i variye Benjamin, Josep ghaghae nasiyeniye, na weiyaŇčgi kaiwae ghare va i lagh…®lagh…®ye ne iwaeŇčge thar…® regha i yomarawe.
\v 5 Kaero Isirel le ŇčgaŇčgako thiya wareri weinjiyaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® vavana vethiya bayama wit, kaiwae vunuvuko vambe i wova Kenan.
\p 
\v 6 E mbaŇčako iyako Josep iye gawana Ijipt e t…®ne na amalagh…®niye iyava i vavakuneŇča wit weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e yambaneke lagh…®ye. Josep oghaghae th…® rakavuthana iwaeŇčge th…® mena th…® kururuwe na ghamwanji i nja e thelauko vwatae.
\v 7 MbaŇča Josep i thuweŇčgiya oghaghaeko na kaero i tuthiŇčgi, ko le vakathako eŇčge Ňčgoreiya mbe lolo regha. Le utuutuko va e gham…®nae weŇčgi. I vaitoŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúAŇčga hu rakamena?‚ÄĚ \fig Th…® mena th…® kururuwe na ghamwanji i nja e thelauko vwatae|src="CO00730B.TIF" size="col" copy="DCC" ref="42:6"\fig*
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúWo rakamena Kenan na wo mena wo bayama ghan…®Ňčga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Josep eŇčge kaero i tuthiŇčgi na i ghareghare gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake amalagh…®niye oghaghae, ko thiye eŇčge mava th…® tuthi thela amalagh…®niye.
\v 9 Amba i renuwaŇčakikiya le gheneloloŇčgima kaiwanji, na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhemi rakelakela ghemi! Menda hu mena na nuwamiya hu thuwe lama vanautumake le ghamba njavovo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNandere moli, amalana. Len rakakaiwo, menda wo mena wo bayama ghan…®Ňčga.
\v 11 Mbe amala regha eŇčge vara le ŇčgaŇčga ghime. Len rakakaiwo, wo utu emunjoru, na maa rakelakela Ňčgoreiye ghime.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Josep mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNandere! Menda hu mena na nuwamiya hu thuwe lama vanautumake le ghamba njavovo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLen rakakaiwo, lama ghanaghanagha theyawora theghewo, amala regha le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgi ghime, amalagh…®niye iyake e val…®vaŇčga idae Kenan. Nasiyenime mbe ina weiye ramame na regha kaero va i mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Josep i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúMbema Ňčgoreiye iya maŇčama weŇčga: Ghemi rakelakela!
\v 15 Ne ya vakatha kamwath…® regha e ghemi na i vaemunjoruŇča lemi utuutuke mbema emunjoru. KiŇč Pero e idae ya dage e ghemi, maa tembe ne hu iteteva Ijipt ghaghad ghaghami nasiyenimina i mena gheke.
\v 16 Ghemina regha i njogha na ve vaŇčguma. Taulagh…®na ghemi iya hu ronjoghana ne vohu yaku e thiyo t…®ne, na wo thuwe thoŇčgo lemi utuko i emunjoru. ThoŇčgo nandere, KiŇč Pero e idae, ghemi rakelakela.‚ÄĚ
\v 17 Josep kaero ve vaŇčguraweŇčgi e thiyo na veth…® yakuwe mbaŇča thegheto e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 18 MbaŇča theghetoniyeko e t…®ne Josep i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúKaiwae Loi ghamararu ina e ghino, hu vakatha renuwaŇčake iyake ambane maa th…® gaboŇčga.
\v 19 ThoŇčgo mbema emunjoru lemi utuutuke, hu vatomwe ghaghamina regha i ronjogha. Mbe i yaku vara e thiyoke t…®ne, na wolagh…®yena ghemi, hu raka njogha. Hu biginjogha wit…®ko weŇčgiya lemi bodaboda iya badana ne i gaboŇčgi.
\v 20 Ko mbaŇča ne hu njoghama hu vaŇčguma ghaghamina nasiyenimina e ghino. Iyake ne i vaemunjoruŇča lemi utuutuma i emunjoru amba ne maa val…®kaiwae hu mare.‚ÄĚ Th…® vamboromboro iya renuwaŇčako iyako.
\p 
\v 21 Kaero th…® vedage weŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúEmunjoru, ra vaidiya vuyowoke iyake r…®ghe moliya ghaghandama. Va ra thuwe ghavuyowoko na le naŇčgo weinda thalavu kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge mava ra wovatha le utuutuko, iya kaiwae ra vaidiya vuyowae e mbaŇča iyake budakaiya va la vakathawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 22 Rubin i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga va yaŇča e ghemi? Va yaŇča ne ra ndevakatha bigi reghawe, ko iyemaeŇčge mava nuwamiya hu vandeŇčeŇčgo. Na mbaŇčake budakaiya va la vakathawe ra vaidiya rereya.‚ÄĚ
\v 23 MbaŇča Josep i utu weŇčgi, lolo regha i vagh…®le iya kaiwae mava e lenji ghareghare mun Josep i loŇčwe na i ghareghare iya lenji utuutuko.
\p 
\v 24 I roiteteŇčgi na wo ve randa. MbaŇča i njogha kaero i tuthiya Simion, na iŇča na th…® Ňčgar…® e maranji.
\s1 Josep oghaghae th…® rakanjogha Kenan
\p 
\v 25 Josep kaero i dage weŇčgiya le rakakaiwoko th…® mbana wit e lenji begibegi na lenji manima tembe th…® bigi mban…®va regha na regha ele begi t…®ne, e vwatae moli. Tembe th…® giyava ghanji kamwath…® kaiwae. MbaŇča th…® vakathavao,
\v 26 kaero th…® doweya wit…®ko e doŇč…®kiko vwatanji na thiya wareri.
\p 
\v 27 E val…®vaŇčga regha va veth…® laghenawe, iwaeŇčge regha e t…®nenjiko i tateya le begi na i munje i mbana wit…®ko vavana na i Ňčamweya le doŇč…®kiko, iwaeŇčge i vaidiya le manima ele begiko t…®ne, e vwatae moli,
\v 28 kaero i dage weŇčgiya oghaghaema iŇča, ‚ÄúLo manima tembe meth…® biginjoghava e ghino. Iyake, mbe iya elo begike t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\p Gharenji i tage weinji lenji gharelagh…®lagh…® lagh…®ye na th…® vevaitoŇčgi th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúBudakai iya Loi menda i vakathake weinda?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 29 MbaŇča th…® vutha weya ramanji Jeikob Kenan e t…®ne, kaero th…® utugiya weya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va th…® yomara weŇčgi. Th…® dagewe th…®Ňča,
\v 30 ‚ÄúGawanako iya i mbaroko Ijipt e t…®ne, mbaŇča va i utuko weime ghal…®Ňčaeko e lar…®mb…®ya na i vakathaime raŇčaeŇčgeva ghime rakelakela e vanautumako t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\v 31 Ko iyemaeŇčge wo dagewe woŇča, ‚ÄúGhime emunjora iya wo utuŇčake, ghime maa rakelakela.
\v 32 Lama ghanaghanagha thamayaworo na thamaghewo, ramame mbe regha eŇčge. Ghaghame regha kaerova i mare na nasiyenime ina Kenan weiye ramame.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 Giyako i dage weime iŇča, ‚ÄúE kamwath…®ke iyake val…®kaiwae ne ya vaemunjoruŇča na ya ghareghare mbema emunjoru iya mohu utuŇčana. Ne hu roiteta ghaghamina regha gheke na wolagh…®yena ghemi hu biginjogha wit e ghambami weŇčgiya lemi bodabodana iya badana i ghar…®Ňčgi.
\v 34 Ko iyemaeŇčge ne hunde renuwaŇča vaghalawe hu vaŇčguma ghaghamina nasiyenimina, ne hu vaŇčgumena e ghino. Ne e kamwath…®ke iyake ya ghareghare ghemi maa rakelakela Ňčgoreiye, emunjoru rautuutu emunjoru ghemi. Ambane ya vaŇčgunjogha ghaghamike weŇčga, na val…®kaiwami hu kune e val…®vaŇčgake iyake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 35 MbaŇča th…® tara raŇčgiya lenji begibegiko uneunenji regha na regha th…® vaidi le manima weiye ghambaema. MbaŇča th…® thuwe iyako weinji ramanji Jeikob gharenji i lagh…®lagh…®ye moli kaiwae.
\v 36 Ramanji i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThare nuwamiya ya th…®vaivao lo ŇčgamaŇčgamake wolagh…®ye? Josep kaero nandere na Simiyon kaero nandere, na noroke kaero nuwamiyava hu vaŇčgwa Benjamin. Bigibigike wolagh…®ye kaero th…® roghereiye wanaŇčgo!‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 37 Amba Rubin i dage weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo maa ya vaŇčgunjoghama Benjamin e ghen, val…®kaiwae u gaboŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčga theghewona. U viyathu e n…®maŇčguke ghare, na tembene ya vaŇčgunjoghamava e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 38 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúNaruŇčguke mane hu wa weimi gheko, ghaghae kaero i mare na ma ghamberegha eŇčge e yawayawaliye. ThoŇčgo bigi regha i yomarawe e lemi loŇčgaloŇčgana t…®ne na i mare, kaiwae kaero ya amalagh…®sar…® moli, lemi vakathana ne i vakatha gharev…®r…® e ghino na i tagavamareŇčgo.‚ÄĚ
\c 43
\s1 Josep oghaghae th…® raka njogha Ijipt weinji Benjamin
\p 
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako vunuvuko vamba i vur…®gheghe vara Kenan e le val…®vaŇčga.
\v 2 Iya kaiwae mbaŇča kaero th…® ghan…®vao wit…®ma va veth…® vamodoma Ijipt, ramanji kaero i dage weŇčgiva iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowo hu njoghava na vohu vamodo ghanda seiwova.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge Juda i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAmalako mendava i utu vur…®gheghe weime iŇča, ‚ÄėMane tembe hu thuweva ghamwaŇčgu, thoŇčgo maa hu vaŇčgwa ghaghamina na weimi.‚Äô
\v 4 ThoŇčgo ne u variya Benjamin na weime, ne wo raka Ijipt na vo vamodo ghan…®Ňčga kaiwan.
\v 5 Ko thoŇčgo mane u variye na weime, mane wo raka kaiwae amalako va i dage weime na iŇča, ‚ÄėMaane tembe hu thuweva ghamwaŇčgu, thoŇčgo ma hu vaŇčgwa ghaghamina na weimi.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Jeikob i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBuda kaiwae hu vakatha vuyowo lagh…®ye e ghino na mendava hu dage weya amalako ghaghami regha mbe ina weva?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalako vambe i vaito gh…®dagh…®da vara ghime kaiwame na lama bodaboda iŇča, ‚ÄėRamami mbe e yawayawaliye? Thare ghaghami regha mbe inaweva?‚Äô Mbema wo thombe eŇčge iya le vaitoŇčgiko. ŇägoroŇčga mbala mendava woŇča na wo ghareghare ne iŇča, ‚ÄėHu vaŇčgumena ghaghamina gheke‚Äô?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Kaero Juda i dage weya ramae Isirel iŇča, ‚ÄúU variye Ňčgama weiŇčgu na wo wareri e mbaŇčake iyake; ambane val…®kaiwae ghime, ghen na la ŇčgamaŇčgamake mbe e yawayawalinji na mane raya mare.
\v 9 Ghino wombereghake ya dagerawe mane bigi regha mun i thar…®we. U worawa vuyowoke wolagh…®ye e ghino. ThoŇčgo mane ya vaŇčgunjoghama e ghen na ya vaŇčgurawe e maran, ghawonjoweko ghino ne ya wo ghaghad yawaliŇčgu.
\v 10 Wo u thuwe, thoŇčgo mava wo roroghagha, mbala kaero mendava wo raka na wo njoghamava mbaŇčaiwoniye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Amba ramanji Isirel i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo mbema Ňčgoreiya iyana, ko hu vakatha iyake: Hu bigiya thivathivake iyake une thovuthovuye vavana e lemi begibegiŇčgina na hu yobigi weya amalana Ňčgoreiya ghamwaewo ‚ÄĒ bal…®m, Ňčguyo, njambawo, mer, pistasiyo mbombouye, na almon.
\v 12 Hu mbana manima va hu mban…®njoghama, va ina e lemi begibegima t…®ne e vwatae na hu mban…®va vavana tembe le ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiyeva iyako, kaiwae manima iyava th…® bigimban e lemi begibegina tembe hu bigi njoghava. Iyana mbwatava lolo regha i mban njoghathavwi.
\v 13 Hu vaŇčgwa ghaghamina weimi na hu njogha weya amalana e mbaŇčake iyake.
\v 14 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi vur…®ghegheniye na i vakatha amalana ghare i nja weŇčga na i vatomwe ghaghamina Benjamin na ne hu njoghama weimi. Ko e ghino, thoŇčgo mbema emunjoru ya th…®vaiŇčgiya lo ŇčgaŇčgake, mbema ya th…®vaiŇčgi vara.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 15 IwaeŇčge amaamalako th…® mbana lenji mwaewoko thiyako na th…® bigiya manima va th…® mban njoghama na tembe val…®vagagava e vwatae. Na weinji Benjamin th…® raka Ijipt, na veth…® raka vuthawe vara Josep.
\v 16 MbaŇča Josep i thuwe Benjamin kaero i dage weya rakakaiwoko iya i mbaro ele Ňčgoloko iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčguŇčgiya gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake na u yovaŇčguŇčgi elo Ňčgoloko. Hu un…®gha thetheghan regha na hu vivatharawa ghan…®Ňčga. Ne ghararagh…®ye mboro ya ghan…®Ňčga weiŇčguyaŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Amalama i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Josep me dagemawe. I vaŇčguŇčgiya amaamalama na th…® wa e Ňčgolo.
\v 18 Amaamalama gharenji i lagh…®lagh…®ye mbaŇča th…® wa e Ňčgoloko. Lenji renuwaŇča th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúTh…® vaŇčguinda na ra mena gheke kaiwae va th…® bigimbanjogha manima ela begibegima. Nuwanjiya lenji vur…®gheghe i ghath…®inda kaero th…® laweinda na le rakakaiwo ghinda na i mban…®Ňčgiya la doŇč…®kike.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 MbaŇča veth…® vutha weya Josep le Ňčgoloko e ghaghambaru, kaero th…® dage weya Ňčgoloko gha ranjimbunjimbu, th…®Ňča,
\v 20 ‚ÄúWo vata ago e ghen amalana, mbaŇča va wo menakaima gheke na wo vamodo ghan…®Ňčga,
\v 21 na wo raka njogha, e kamwath…® mborowae i gou weime na wo laghena. Gougouko iyako wo tateŇčgiya lama begibegi na wo vaidiya manima iya mendava wo vamodo wit…®kowe. Mbe iya varake. Mbowo mo mban…®njoghamava,
\v 22 weiya vavanava e vwatae na wo vamodo ghan…®Ňčgawe. Maa tembe e lama ghareghareva va ŇčgoroŇčga na maniko tembe inanjiva e begibegiko t…®nenji.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 23 Rakakaiwoma iya i mbaro Josep ele Ňčgoloma i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTha hu rerenuwaŇča kaiwae. Tha hu gharelagh…®lagh…®. Lemi Loi, iye ramami le Loi mendava i giya manina iyana e ghemi, iya i bigimban e lemi begibegina. Lemi manima kaerova ya mban.‚ÄĚ Amba i vaŇčguraŇčgiya Simiyon na i vaŇčgugiya weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 24 Rakakaiwoma i vaŇčguruwoŇčgiya amaamalama Josep ele Ňčgoloke t…®ne, i giya mbwa na th…® thavwiya gheghenji na i ŇčamweŇčgiya lenji doŇč…®kiko.
\v 25 Kaero th…® vivatha lenji mwaewoma Josep kaiwaema na mbala th…® giyawe mbaŇča ne i njoghama ghararagh…®ye mboro kaiwae me giya yanawanji Josep ne i mena i ghan…®Ňčga weiyaŇčgi e lughawoghawoko iyako gheko.
\p 
\v 26 MbaŇča Josep i vutha weŇčgi e Ňčgoloko, th…® bigiya mwaewoma meth…® mban menama e Ňčgoloko na th…® kururu e thelauko vwatae e ghamwae.
\v 27 I vaitoŇčgi gham…®nanji kaiwae na iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ramami, mendava huŇčama kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli? Mbe inawe na amba e yawayawaliye?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúLen rakakaiwo ramame, mbe e yawayawaliye na riwae mbe thovuye eŇčge.‚ÄĚ Na mbowo th…® ronjava e ghenji vuvuye na th…® kururu e ghamwae.
\p 
\v 29 MbaŇča i thuwe ghaghae Benjamin kaero i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhaghamike nasiyenimike iyava hu utuŇča utuniyeko weŇčgo iya amalagh…®niyeke? Loi i dage mwaewo e ghen, naruŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\v 30 Josep weiye le ghare v…®r…® lagh…®ye mbaŇča i thuwe ghaghaeko, i ruku iteteŇčgi na i wa mbe amalagh…®niye vara ele woluwolu t…®ne na ve randawe.
\p 
\v 31 MbaŇča kaero me thavwiya ghamwae, i raŇčgi na mbe i mbaroŇča vara gham…®naeko, kaero iŇča, ‚ÄúHu theya ghan…®Ňčgana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 32 Ghan…®Ňčga ghambaŇča Josep mbe le ghamba ghan…®Ňčga, oghaghae mbe lenji ghamba ghan…®Ňčga na Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye mbe lenji ghamba ghan…®Ňčga, kaiwae Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® gh…®mara njoŇčanjoŇčaŇčgiya Hibru ghar…®ghar…®niye iya kaiwae maa th…® ghan…®Ňčga weinjiyaŇčgi.
\v 33 Amaamalako va th…® yaku na ghamwanji i ghemba Josep. Va th…® yaku na Ňčgoreiya ghanjitheghatheghako, i ri lagh…®yeninji ghaghad nasiyeninji. Lenji yakuyakuko kaiwae gharenji iyo na th…® vethuwethuweŇčgi.
\v 34 Ghanjiko va th…® the Josep ele ghamba ghan…®Ňčgako. MbaŇča th…® thembana ghan…®Ňčgako, Benjamin ghae i lagh…®ye moli ‚ÄĒ mbaŇčalima vara th…® themban na i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya ghauneko. Thiya ghan…®Ňčga na thiya munumu weinji Josep ghaghad…® thiya warari.
\c 44
\s1 Josep i yaroŇčgiya oghaghae
\p 
\v 1 Josep i dage weya le rakakaiwoko iya i mbaro ele Ňčgoloko iŇča, ‚ÄúU mbana ghan…®Ňčga amala regha na regha ele begi na val…®kaiwae ne i bigi. E begi regha na regha e t…®ne e vwatae moli u bigirawa regha na regha le mani.
\v 2 U wo wo komuna iya silvana na u womban iya nasiyeninjina ele begi e t…®ne weiye wit…®na ghamani.‚ÄĚ Kaero i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Josep me dagemawe.
\p 
\v 3 Igh…®viya rakerake le rakakaiwoŇčgi th…® variyeŇčgi amaamalama na thiya wareri weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji doŇč…®ki.
\v 4 Vama inanji e loŇčga mborowae, ko maa vamba bwagabwaga e ghembako t…®ne kaero Josep i dage weya le Ňčgoloko gharanjimbunjimbu iŇča, ‚ÄúHu rereghamba weŇčgiya amaamalama. MbaŇča ne vou vuthavaleŇčgi, hu dage weŇčgi, huŇča, ‚ÄėBuda kaiwae hu lith…®gha thovuye e thar…®?
\v 5 Buda kaiwae mohu wokav…® wo giyako ghakomu? Komuko iyako i vakaiwoŇča na i vaidiya bigibigi iya maa lolo regha i ghareghare vagh…®le ghenelolowe. Mbema mohu vakatha vara thanavu raithar…® moli.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 MbaŇča i vuthavaleŇčgi, i vathigiya Josep ghal…®Ňčaema weŇčgi.
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, len utuutuna Ňčgoreiyana ŇčgoroŇčga gharumwaru? Wo tholo e maran maa tembe val…®kaiwaeva wo vakatha vakatha Ňčgoreiyana.
\v 8 U ghareghare mendava wo mban njogha mani e lama begibegi t…®nenji e vwatae moli. Mbala buda kaiwae na wo kav…® silva o gol e ghan…®giyana ele Ňčgolo?
\v 9 Amalana, thoŇčgo ra vaidiya bigina iyana weya regha e t…®nemeke noroke i mare na taulagh…®ke ghime wo tabo len rakakaiwobwaga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ra vakatha Ňčgoreiya moŇčana. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbe thela eŇčge vara me wo komuko ne lo rakakaiwobwaga na taulagh…®na ghemi rakerakethu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 11 Mbe ghenji na n…®manji eŇčge th…® bigi njoŇča lenji begibegi bode na regha na regha tembe i tate le begi.
\v 12 Amba rakakaiwoko i tamwe, i ri weya vir…®vivako ghaghad nasiyeniyeko. Na komuko ve vaidi vara Benjamin ele begi t…®ne.
\v 13 Oghaghaeko wolagh…®ye th…® thetheŇčgiya ghanjikwamakwama gharev…®r…® kaiwae, kaero regha na regha i dowe njogha le doŇč…®ki na th…® raka njogha Ijipt.
\p 
\v 14 MbaŇča Juda na oghaghae th…® raka vutha Josep vamba ina ele Ňčgoloko. Taulagh…®ko th…® kururu na ghamwanji i nja e thelauko vwatae Josep e ghamwae.
\v 15 I dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúBudakai iya menda hu vakathake? Thare hu ghareghare lolo Ňčgoreiya ghinoke val…®kaiwaŇčgu ne ya vaidiya bigithan ma lolo reghava i ghareghare?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Juda i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ne woŇča e ghen, giya lagh…®ye? ŇägoroŇčga ne woŇča na wo vaemunjoruŇča e ghen mava wo vakatha vathar…® weŇčge? Loi tembe ghamberegha i woraŇčgiya lama thar…®ke. Iya kaiwae, amalana, taulagh…®ke ghime, na thela iya komuko mena ele begi t…®ne, len rakakaiwobwaga ghime.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa val…®kaiwae ya vakatha iyana! Mbe thela eŇčge vara komuko menawe, iye lo rakakaiwobwaga. Taulagh…®na ghemi hu raka njogha weya ramami weimi lemi gharemal…®l…®.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Juda i rovur…®gheghe Benjamin kaiwae
\p 
\v 18 Amba Juda i wa weya Josep na ve dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúAgo lagh…®ye e ghen, giyana. Wo u vatomwe e ghino na ya woraŇčgiya lo renuwaŇčake. Gharen ne i ndegaith…® wanaŇčgo. Ya ghareghare u mboromboro wein Pero.
\v 19 Giya lagh…®ye, va u vaitoime na uŇča, ‚ÄėThare e ramaramami o ghaghami reghava inawe?‚Äô
\v 20 Wo gonjogha e ghen na woŇča, ‚ÄėMbe e ramaramame, kaero i amalagh…®sar…®, na ghaghame nasiyenime, vama i amalagh…®sar…® amba i laghamb…®. Ňägamako ghaghae lagh…®yeniye kaero va i mare, t…®nanji regha. Ramae ghare mboro.‚Äô
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúInjana mbowo u dageva weime na uŇča, ‚ÄėWo vohu vaŇčguma na hu mena e ghino na wo ya thuwe.‚Äô
\v 22 Na wo dage e ghen, giyana, woŇča, ‚ÄėŇägamako maa val…®kaiwaeva tene i roiteta ramae. ThoŇčgo i vakatha Ňčgoreiye ramae ne i mare.‚Äô
\v 23 Ko iyemaeŇčge u dage weime uŇča, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo mane hu vaŇčgu mena ghaghamina iya nasiyenimina, ko mane tembe hu mena hu ndeghath…®va e maraŇčgu.‚Äô
\v 24 MbaŇča va wo njogha weya ramame wo utu giyawe budakai va u utugiya weime.
\p 
\v 25 ‚ÄúMbaŇča regha wo yakuyaku kaero ramame i dage weime iŇča, ‚ÄėHu raka njogha na mbowo vohu vamodova ghan…®Ňčga seiwo.‚Äô
\v 26 Ko iyemaeŇčge wo dagewe woŇča, ‚ÄėMane wo raka. ThoŇčgo mbe weime vara ghaghameko iya nasiyenimeko. Mane wo thuwe giyako ghamwae thoŇčgo maa weime.‚Äô
\p 
\v 27 ‚ÄúAmba bwebwe i dage weime iŇča, ‚ÄėKaero u ghareghare lo wevoko Reitiyel va i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai theghewo e ghino.
\v 28 Regha kaerova i roiteteŇčga na ya renuwaŇča thetheghan mbwanjam kaerova i ten…®ghan, kaiwae maa tembe ya ndevaidiva mun ghaghad noroke.
\v 29 Na mbaŇčake thoŇčgo hu vaŇčgwa ghaghaeke e ghino na vuyowo ve yomarawe, nuwathar…®niye ne i vakathaŇčgo ya mare.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 30-31 Juda i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúIya kaiwae, giyana, mbaŇča ne wo njogha weya ramame, thoŇčgo Ňčgamake maa weime, mbaŇča ne i thuwe Ňčgamake maa weime ne i mare. Yawaliye mboro iya Ňčgamake iyake. Na kaiwae kaero i amalagh…®sar…® moli gharev…®r…®ko ne wo vakathakowe ne i un…®gh…® emunjoru.
\v 32 Wo u thuwe, ghino wombereghake mendava ya dagerawa yawaliŇčguke weya bwebwe Ňčgamake modae. Va ya dagewe na yaŇča, ‚ÄėThoŇčgo maa ya vaŇčgu njoghama e ghen, vuyowoko wolagh…®ye, bwebwe, e maran ya wo ghaghad yawaliŇčgu.‚Äô
\p 
\v 33 ‚ÄúE mbaŇčake iyake, giyana, ghino eŇčge ya yaku na ya tabo len rakakaiwobwaga, ya roth…®gha Ňčgamake; na u viyathu i njogha weiyaŇčgiya oghaghae.
\v 34 Ne ŇčgoroŇčga na ya njogha weya bwebwe thoŇčgo maa weiŇčgu Ňčgamake? Maa tembe nuwaŇčguiya va thuwe vuyowoko ne i nja weya bwebweko.‚ÄĚ
\c 45
\s1 Josep i govambwara ghamberegha
\p 
\v 1 E mbaŇčako iyako Josep maa tembe val…®kaiwaeva i ghataŇčaghath…®gha gham…®naeko le rakakaiwoko wolagh…®ye e maranji, iwaeŇčge iŇča na th…® raka iteta amalagh…®niye. Maa tembe lolo reghava va ina gheko, vambema amalagh…®niye eŇčge na oghaghae, amba i govambwara thela amalagh…®niye weŇčgi.
\v 2 Amba i randa na ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye. Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niyeko th…® loŇčwe ghal…®Ňčae na utuniye tembe va vuthava kiŇč…®ko e ghayayao t…®ne.
\p 
\v 3 Kaero Josep i dage weŇčgiya oghaghaeko iŇča, ‚ÄúJosep ghino iyake. Bwebwe mbe e yawayawaliye?‚ÄĚ Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča oghaghaeko th…® loŇčwe iyako maa val…®kaiwanji th…® thombewe kaiwae gharenji va i tage lagh…®ye moli e marae.
\p 
\v 4 Amba Josep i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu raka mena evasiwaŇčguke.‚ÄĚ Th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiye na mbowo i dageva weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino ghaghamima Josep iyava hu vakuneŇčama na i mena Ijipt.
\v 5 MbaŇčake thava hu gharelagh…®lagh…® na thava hu vegaith…® wanaŇčga kaiwae va hu vakuneŇčaŇčgo gheke. Loi va le renuwaŇča e t…®ne na ya viva e ghamwami gheke na val…®kaiwae ya vamoru ghar…®ghar…® yawalinji.
\v 6 Kaero theghathegha umboiwo vara iyake, maa ghan…®Ňčga i ndembuthu mun e val…®vaŇčgake iyake. Theghathegha umbolima amba inawe na e t…®ne mane ghan…®Ňčga ghakabu o uloulo.
\v 7 Ko iyake kaiwae Loi va i variyeŇčgo e ghamwami gheke na val…®kaiwae orumburumbumi vavana mbe e yawayawalinji e yambaneke. Na i vamoru yawal…®mi e kamwath…®ke iya ghamba rotaeleke t…®ne.
\p 
\v 8 ‚ÄúIya kaiwae, ghemi mava hu variyeŇčgo gheke, ko iyemaeŇčge Loi va i variyeŇčgo. I vakathaŇčgo ghino Ňčgoreiye kiŇč…®ko ramae. I woraweŇčgo ya mbaroŇča le vanautumake iyake, na ya mbaro Ijipt lagh…®yeke.
\v 9 Hu vamayaŇča na hu njogha weya bwebwe na hu dagewe huŇča, ‚ÄėNaru Josep ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake: Loi kaerova i vakathaŇčgo giya lagh…®ye na ya mbaroŇča Ijipt lagh…®yeke; hu vamayaŇča na hu mena.
\v 10 Ne hu yaku e val…®vaŇčga idae Gosen, na ne inami evasiwaŇčgu, ghen, len ŇčgaŇčga, orumburumbu, len sip, len gout, len burumwaka, na len bigibigina wolagh…®ye.
\v 11 MbaŇča ne inami gheko, mbene ya njimbukikiŇčga vara. Kaiwae theghathegha umbolima amba inawe vunuvuke ne ve wo; na maa nuwaŇčguiya ghen, le ŇčgaŇčga na len bigibigina wolagh…®ye bada i gaboŇčga.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Josep i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúKaero hu thuwe taulagh…®na ghemi, na Benjamin, ghen tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, mbema emunjora ghino Josep.
\v 13 Vohu utu giya weya bwebwe ŇčgoroŇčga wo yavwatata le lagh…®lagh…®ye Ijipt e t…®ne, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva bigibigike wolagh…®ye iya kaero hu thuweŇčgike. Ko hu vamayaŇča eŇčge hu vaŇčgumena bwebwe gheke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Amba Josep i bigirawa n…®man…®mae Benjamin e vwatae na i randa; na Benjamin i thovuvu na tembe i randava.
\v 15 Josep tembe i vakathava Ňčgoreiyako weŇčgiya oghaghaeko regha na regha na i vandamoŇčgi. Iyako e ghereiye amba th…® utu weinji.
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča Josep oghaghaeko lenji vutha Ijipt utuutuniye kaero ve wo kiŇč…®ko ghayayao, i vakatha kiŇč…®ko na ghamband…®mband…® thiya warari.
\v 17 Pero i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúU dage weŇčgiya oghaghan…®na na th…® raka njogha Kenan.
\v 18 U dage weŇčgi na veth…® vaŇčguma ramanji na lenji bodabodako wolagh…®ye na th…® raka njoghama gheke. Ne ya wogiya the thivathiva regha thovuye Ijipt e t…®neke, na the bigiya nuwanjiya ne i mboromboro weŇčgi.
\p 
\v 19 ‚ÄúU dage weŇčgi na th…® momod…®Ňčgiya waŇčga momod vavana Ijipt e t…®neke lenji ovo na gamagai nanasiye kaiwanji; na tembe th…® vaŇčgu menava ramanji weinji.
\v 20 U dage weŇčgi ne th…® ndererenuwaŇča the bigibigiva kaiwanji. The bigibigi thovuthovuye inanji Ijipt e t…®ne ne ra giya weŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 Isirel le ŇčgaŇčga th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya me dagema weŇčgi. Josep i giya waŇčga momod vavana Ňčgoreiya kiŇč…®ko meŇčama, na ghan…®Ňčga kamwath…® kaiwae.
\v 22 Tembe i giyava kwama togha regha iya weŇčgi oghaghaeko, ko iyemaeŇčge i giya silva geth…®seriyeto weya Benjamin na kwamakwama totogha yaŇčgalima.
\v 23 I variya doŇč…®ki hoyawora, th…® dowa Ijipt bigibiginiye thovuthovuye na doŇč…®ki hoyaworo th…® dowa wit na bred na ghan…®Ňčga lenji njoghamake kamwath…® kaiwae.
\v 24 Kaero i variye yathuŇčgi oghaghaema na th…® raka, na i th…®n…®mbuleŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúNe hu ndegaith…® e kamwath…® mborowa.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Kaero th…® raka iteta Ijipt na th…® raka njogha weya ramanji Jeikob, Kenan e t…®ne.
\v 26 Th…® raka vutha kaero th…® dage weya ramanji th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúJosep mbe e yawayawaliye. Iye i mbaro Ijipt lagh…®yeko.‚ÄĚ Ramanji Jeikob ghare i yo lagh…®ye moli na maa i loŇčweghath…®Ňčgi.
\v 27 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča th…® utugiya bigibigiko wolagh…®yewe, iya Josep mendava i utugiyama weŇčgi, na mbaŇča i thuwe waŇčga momod…®Ňčgiko iya Josep va i variyeko na th…® dowewe, ko ambama ghare ve dinja.
\v 28 Na iŇča, ‚ÄúMeiye! Ko ana naruŇčguma Josep mbe e yawayawaliye! Wo ya wa na va thuwe amba muyai ya mare.‚ÄĚ
\c 46
\s1 Jeikob na le wabwi th…® raka Ijipt
\p 
\v 1 Jeikob kaero i wareriŇča Ijipt weiyaŇčgiya ghamband…®mband…®ko wolagh…®ye, na mbaŇča i vutha Beyasiba i lavakatha vowo weya ramae Aisake le Loi.
\p 
\v 2 Gougouniye Loi i utuwe e ghavatomwe t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúJeikob! Jeikob!‚ÄĚ
\p Jeikob i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbe ghinoke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 3 I dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino Loi, rama le Loi. Tha u mararu u wa Ijipt, ne ya vakathaŇčgiya orumburumbu tha muyaiko th…® tabo vanautuma lagh…®ye regha gheko.
\v 4 Ghino ne weiŇčgu ghen ra wa Ijipt, na tembene ya vaŇčgu njoghaŇčgiva orumburumbu tha muyaiko gheke. Josep ghamberegha e n…®mae ne i vuna maramaran mbaŇča ne u mare.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Amba Jeikob i wareriva Beyasiba e t…®ne. Le ŇčgaŇčga th…® vaŇčgu doweŇčgi weiyaŇčgiya lenji ŇčgaŇčga nanasiye na lenji ovo e waŇčga momod…®Ňčgina Pero va i variyeŇčgi Ijipt kaiwanji.
\v 6 Tevambe th…® vaŇčguŇčgiva lenji thetheghan…®ko na bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va th…® mban vathavatha Kenan e t…®ne na tembe orumburumbuyekova wolagh…®ye th…® raka Ijipt.
\v 7 Jeikob va i vaŇčguŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga, orumburumbuye gh…®mogh…®moru, le ŇčgaŇčga wanakau, na orumburumbuye wanakau.
\b
\p 
\v 8 Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčga na orumburumbuye va th…® ri Kenan na th…® raka Ijipt idaidanji thiyake:
\li1 Rubin, Jeikob nariye vir…®viva.
\li1 
\v 9 Rubin le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Hanok, Palu, Hesron na Kami.
\li1 
\v 10 Simiyon le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Jemuel, Jamin, Ohad, Jakin, Soha na Saul iye t…®nae t…®nan Kenan.
\li1 
\v 11 Livai le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Gereson, Kohat na Merari.
\li1 
\v 12 Juda le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Er, Onam, Sila, Peres na Sera. Ko iyemaeŇčge Er na Onan vambe th…® mare Kenan e t…®ne.
\li1 
\v 13 Isaka le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Tola, Pua, Jasub na Simiron.
\li1 
\v 14 Sebulon le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Sered, Elon na Jalil.
\p 
\v 15 Gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake Leya va i ghamb…®Ňčgi weiye Jeikob Padan Aram e t…®ne weinji lounji Daina. Le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru na wanakau lenji ghanaghanagha theto na thegheto.
\li1 
\v 16 Gad le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Sipon, Hagi, Suni, Esbon, Eri, Arodi na Areli.
\li1 
\v 17 Asa le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Imna, Isva, Isvi, na Beraiya.
\li2 Lounji Sera.
\li2 Beraiya le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li3 Heba na Mal…®kiyel.
\p 
\v 18 Gamagaike thiyake Silpa va i ghamb…®Ňčgi weiye Jeikob. Wevoke iyake Leiban va i vaŇčgugiya weya yawarumbuye Leya na le rakakaiwo. Lenji ghanaghanagha theyaworo na theghewona.
\b
\li1 
\v 19 Jeikob levo Reitiyel le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya thiyake:
\li2 Josep na Benjamin.
\v 20 Ijipt e t…®ne Josep ve ghamb…®Ňčgiya Manase na Epreim weiye Asenat, Potipa yawarumbuye. Amalake iyake ravowovowo On e t…®ne.
\li1 
\v 21 Benjamin le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya:
\li2 Bela, Beka, Asbel, Gera, Naaman, Ehi, Ros, Mapim, Hapim na Ad.
\p 
\v 22 Gh…®mogh…®moruke thiya Reitiyel va i ghamb…®Ňčgi weiye Jeikob. Lenji ghanaghanagha theyaworo na theghevar…®.
\li1 
\v 23 Den nariya iyake:
\li2 Hasim.
\li1 
\v 24 Nap…®talai le ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgiya thiyake:
\li2 Jasiyel, Guni, Jesa, na Silem.
\p 
\v 25 Gh…®mogh…®moruke thiyake Bilha va i ghamb…® weiye Jeikob. Leiban va i vaŇčgugiya wevoke iyake weya yawarumbuye Reitiyel. Lenji ghanaghanagha theghepir…®.
\b
\p 
\v 26 Ghar…®ghar…®ke vara wolagh…®ye thiyake iyava th…® rakake Ijipt weinji Jeikob mbe amalagh…®niye vara orumburumbuye moliŇčgi. Lenji ghanaghanagha thewona na theghewona. Iyake ma i vaonaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga lenji ovo.
\v 27 Josep va i ghamb…®Ňčgiya gamagai theghewo Ijipt e t…®ne, i vakatha Jeikob le bodaboda va inanji Ijipt lenji ghanaghanagha thepir…®.
\s1 Jeikob na le ŇčgaŇčga inanji Ijipt
\p 
\v 28 MbaŇča kaero th…® vur…®thaiya Ijipt, Jeikob i variye Juda e ghamwae na ve thuwe Josep mbala ve lavolevoleŇčgi Gosen. MbaŇča th…® rakavutha gheko,
\v 29 Josep kaero i thava ele waŇčga momod na i wa Gosen ve lavolevoleya ramaewe. MbaŇča th…® vethuwethuweŇčgi, Josep i bigiyatho n…®man…®mae ramae Isirel e Ňčg…®leŇčg…®le na i randa mbaŇča molao moli.
\p 
\v 30 Amba Isirel i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake kaero val…®kaiwaŇčgu ya mare. Kaero ya thuweŇčge na ya ghareghare amba e yawayawalin.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Josep i dage weŇčgiya oghaghae na ramae ghauuko ghar…®ghar…®niye iŇča, ‚ÄúWo ya wa Pero na va utuwe, vaŇča, ‚ÄėOghaghaŇčguma na bwebwe ghauuko ghar…®ghar…®niye, va thiya yakuma Kenan kaero meth…® raka vutha weŇčgo.
\v 32 Ne va utugiyawe ghemi sip gharanjimbunjimbu, na hu njimbukikiŇčgiya thetheghan ‚ÄĒ burumwaka, sip na gout lemoyo moli. Na menda hu vaŇčgu menaŇčgi ‚ÄĒ lemoyo moli weiye lemi bigibigiko wolagh…®ye.‚Äô
\v 33 MbaŇča Pero ne i kula vathaŇčga na i vaitoŇčga na iŇča, ‚ÄėGhemi ghamikaiwo budakai?‚Äô
\v 34 Mbala hu gonjoghawe na huŇča, ‚ÄėLen rakakaiwo, mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye wo njimbukikiŇčgiya burumwaka, sip na gout Ňčgoreiya va mbe orumburumbume tha na tha va th…® vakavakatha.‚Äô Ne e kamwath…®ke iyake ambane i vatomwe Gosen le val…®vaŇčga na hu yakuwe. Kaiwae Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® botewoŇčgiya sip gharanjimbunjimbu.‚ÄĚ
\c 47
\p 
\v 1 Josep i wa weya Pero na ve dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúBwebwe na oghaghaŇčgu weinjiyaŇčgiya lenji burumwaka, sip na gout na lenji bigibigiko wolagh…®ye kaero mendama th…® raka vutha, th…® ri Kenan na mbaŇčake inanji Gosen.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 I tuthiŇčgiya oghaghae theghelima na i vaŇčgu vamara weŇčgiya Pero.
\p 
\v 3 Kaero i vaitoŇčgi, ‚ÄúGhamikaiwo budakai?‚ÄĚ
\p Th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, ghime sip gharanjimbunjimbu, ŇčgorameŇčgiya orumburumbume tha na tha.
\v 4 Mendava wo mena na wo wo layaku gheke, kaiwae vunuvuke kaero i vakatha dagabora Kenan e t…®ne. Lama thetheghan…®ko kaero maa e ghanjinana, iya kaiwae wo vata ago e ghen na wo wo layaku Gosen.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Pero i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúRama na oghagha kaero meth…® vutha e ghen.
\v 6 Ijipt thivathivaniyeke lagh…®ye ina e n…®man ghare. U vaŇčguraweŇčgi Gosen ele val…®vaŇčga, thivathiva thovuye moli. Na thoŇčgo sip gharanjimbunjimbu thovuthovuye vavana inanji e t…®nenjina, u vaŇčguraweŇčgi na th…® njimbukikiya lo sip na lo burumwakana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Amba Josep i vaŇčgu menava ramae Jeikob na i vaŇčgurawe Pero e marae. Jeikob i giya Pero ghadagemwaewo
\v 8 na Pero i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúŇägoroŇčga ghan theghathegha le lagh…®lagh…®ye?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Jeikob i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúYawaliŇčguke ghayakuyaku mbe ya riye na ya nja eŇčge e ghemba na ghemba theghathegha hothaŇčar…® na ghweto (130). Maa i ghanagha moli ko vuyowo eŇčge va ina e t…®nenji. Maa Ňčgoreiya orumburumbuŇčgu ghanjitheghathegha me molao e lenji loŇčgaloŇčga t…®ne.‚ÄĚ
\v 10 Amba Jeikob mbowo i giyava Pero ghadagemwaewo na i itete.
\p 
\v 11 Ňägoreiya KiŇč Pero me dagemawe, Josep i vaŇčguraweŇčgiya ramae na oghaghaeko e thivathiva thovuye Ijipt e t…®ne e ghemba lagh…®ye Rameses ghadidiye.
\v 12 Josep i giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgiya ramae, oghaghaeko na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiye val…®kaiwanji.
\s1 Josep na vunuvuko
\p 
\v 13 Vunuvuko vama i wo mbaŇča molao moli na e val…®vaŇčgake wolagh…®ye kaero maa ghan…®Ňčga. Ghar…®ghar…® Ijipt na Kenan e t…®nenji bada kaiwae kaero maa e lenji vur…®gheghe.
\v 14 MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…® va th…® vavamodo wit, Josep i mbana maniko wolagh…®ye na i yomban Pero ele Ňčgoloko.
\v 15 MbaŇča mani kaero iko weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ijipt na Kenan e t…®nenji, Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® raka mena weya Josep na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúU giya ghan…®Ňčga weime. Lama mani kaero iko. Buda kaiwae ne woya mare e maran?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 16 Josep i gonjogha weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu bigima lemi thetheghan…®ma. Ne ya giya ghan…®Ňčga e ghemi na modae, kaiwae lemi mani kaero iko.‚ÄĚ
\v 17 Kaero th…® bigi menaŇčgiya lenji thetheghan weya Josep na i giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgi na modae. Th…® bigi mena lenji hos…®, sip, gout, burumwaka na doŇč…®ki. Theghatheghako iyako e t…®ne i giya ghan…®Ňčga weŇčgi lenji thetheghan…®ko modae.
\p 
\v 18 Theghatheghako iyako iko na umbwarava e ghamwanjiko mbowo th…® mena weva na th…® dagewe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúAmalana, mane val…®kaiwame wo wothuwola iya emunjoruke iyake e ghen. Lama mani kaero iko na lama thetheghan…®ma wolagh…®ye kaero ghen…®we. Maa tembe bigi reghava inawe na wo woveŇčge, ma riwameke eŇčge na lama thelau.
\v 19 Buda kaiwae ne woya mare e maran…®na, ghime na lama thelathelauke? U vamodoime na lama thelathelauko ghan…®Ňčga modae, na ghime weiye lama thelathelauko wo tabo rakakaiwobwaga weya Pero. U giya weiwo weime na wo kabu amba ne maa val…®kaiwae woya mare, na thelauko mbala maa i rorobwaga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 20 Josep i vamodovao thelauko wolagh…®ye Ijipt e t…®ne Pero kaiwae. Kaiwae vunuvuko vama i vakatha dagabora lagh…®ye i vakatha Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye th…® vakuneŇča lenji thelau. Na thelauko wolagh…®ye kaero i tabo Pero le bigi.
\v 21 Josep i vakathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ijipt e val…®vaŇčga na val…®vaŇčga th…® tabo rakakaiwobwaga.
\v 22 IyemaeŇčge ravowovowo lenji thelau mava i vamodoŇčgi, kaiwae Pero va i vamodoŇčgi lenji kaiwoko kaiwae, na lenji maniko val…®kaiwanji th…® vamodo ghanjiwe.
\p 
\v 23 Josep i dage weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko iŇča, ‚ÄúWo hu thuwe, noroke kaero ya vamodoŇčga ‚ÄĒ ghemi na lemi thelauna, Pero kaiwae. Noroke ya giya weiwo e ghemi na hu kabu e lemi umaumana.
\v 24 MbaŇča uloulo ghambaŇča, ne u wabwi na wabwilima. Wabwi regha i wa weya Pero na wabwi var…® weiwo togha kaiwae, ghan…®Ňčga ghemi kaiwami, len Ňčgolona ghar…®ghar…®niye kaiwanji na len ŇčgamaŇčgama kaiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 25 Ghar…®ghar…®ko th…® gonjoghawe th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúKaero menda u vamora yawal…®me. Na mendava u thovuye vara weime, amalana. Kaero wo tabo Pero le rakakaiwobwaga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Josep i vakatha iyako kaero i tabo na i mbaro Ijipt e t…®ne, va e mbaŇčako iyako ghaghad noroke: Wabwilimako wabwi regha e bigibigiko wolagh…®ye th…® raka mena e thelauko Pero kaiwae. Ravowovowo lenji thelau vara mava i tabo KiŇč Pero le bigi.
\s1 Jeikob i naŇčgorawe weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga riwae ghabeku kaiwae
\p 
\v 27 Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® yayaku Gosen ele val…®vaŇčga Ijipt e t…®ne. Kaero lenji bigibigi lemoyo moli na lenji ŇčgamaŇčgama lemoyo moli.
\p 
\v 28 Theghathegha hoyaworo na umbopir…® Jeikob i yaku Ijipt e t…®ne na ghatheghathegha kaero i wo theghathegha hoseriyethaŇčar…® ghwevar…® na umbopir…® (147).
\v 29 MbaŇča Isirel ghambaŇča mare kaero i gheneghenetha, kaero i kula weya nariye Josep na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU lirawa n…®man…®na e vavaŇčguke e raberabe na u dagerawe mane u bekuŇčgo Ijipt e t…®ne.
\v 30 MbaŇča ne ya garalawa weŇčgiya orumburumbuŇčgu, u woraŇčgiyaŇčgo Ijipt e t…®ne na vo bekuŇčgo thiye evasiwanji.‚ÄĚ
\p Josep i gonjoghawe iŇča, ‚ÄúNe ya vakatha Ňčgoreiya moŇčana.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 31 Jeikob i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU dagerawe e ghino.‚ÄĚ Josep i dagerawe e marae na ne i vakatha Ňčgoreiye. Amba Isirel i ghenevadede le pwasike na i kururu weya Loi.\f + \fr 47:31 \ft Kaiwae utuutuke ‚Äúghamba ghena‚ÄĚ na ‚Äúpwasike‚ÄĚ ghanji loŇčwaloŇčwa Hibru e t…®ne mbalama i mboromboro. Hu thuwe Hibru 11:21.\f*
\c 48
\s1 Jeikob i giya Manase na Ip…®reim ghanjimwaewo
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča ubotu e ghereiye Josep i loŇčwevaidiya ramae utuniye, i ghambwera. IwaeŇčge i vaŇčguŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčgako theghewoko, Manase na Ip…®reim, weiyaŇčgi th…® wa weya ramae Jeikob.
\v 2 MbaŇča Josep i vutha, lolo regha ve dage weya Jeikob iŇča, ‚ÄúNaru Josep kaero me vutha, i mena i thuweŇčge.‚ÄĚ Kaiwae vama amalagh…®sar…® i rovur…®gheghe i thuweiru na i yaku.
\p 
\v 3 Jeikob i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye va i yomara e ghino Luji e t…®ne Kenan ele val…®vaŇčga na i mwaewo e ghino.
\v 4 Na i dage e ghino iŇča, ‚ÄėNe ya vakathaŇčge na orumburumbu lemoyo na orumburumbuko thiyako nevole th…® tabo vanautuma lemoyo. Na nevole ya giya thivathivake iyake na i meghabana weŇčgi.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 5 Jeikob i gotubwe iŇča, ‚ÄúJosep, iya len ŇčgaŇčgana theghewona va th…® vir…®na Ijipt e t…®ne amba muyai ya menake, Ip…®reim na Manase, ne th…® tabo lo ŇčgaŇčga. Thiye ne Ňčgoronjiya Rubin na Simiyon lo ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgi moli.
\v 6 Ko thoŇčgo len ŇčgaŇčga vavanava th…® roghamb…® e ghereinji, ghen len ŇčgaŇčga. Ko the val…®vaŇčga Ip…®reim na Manase ne veth…® yakuwe thiye ne inanjiwe.
\v 7 MbaŇča vama ya njoghanjoghama, ya ri Padan Aram, kaero iname Kenan ele val…®vaŇčga, iwaeŇčge Reitiyel i mare. E mbaŇčako iyako wo loŇčga na ghamwame i ghemba Eprat. Reitiyel le mareko kaiwae ghareŇčgu i v…®r…® lagh…®ye moli. Eprat e ghakamwath…® ghadidiye ya bekuwe.‚ÄĚ (Noroke Eprat idae Bet…®lehem.)
\p 
\v 8 MbaŇča Isirel i thuweŇčgiya Josep le ŇčgaŇčgako kaero i vaito iŇča, ‚ÄúThavalaŇčgiya gamagaike thiyake?‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 9 Josep i gonjogha weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino lo ŇčgaŇčgaŇčgi. Loi va i giya e ghino gheke, Ijipt e t…®neke.‚ÄĚ
\p Amba Isirel i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU vaŇčgu menaŇčgi e ghino na ya giya ghanjimwaewo.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 10 Va e mbaŇčako iyako Isirel maramarae kaero th…® thar…® kaiwae vama i amalagh…®sar…®. IwaeŇčge Josep i vaŇčgu menaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčgama theghewoma evasiwae. Isirel i vandamoŇčgi na i livatharaŇčgwa n…®man…®mae e mborowanji.
\v 11 Isirel i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúLo renuwaŇča va yaŇča eŇčge mane te mbaŇča reghava ya thuweŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake Loi menda i vatomwe e ghino na ya thuweŇčgiya len ŇčgaŇčgake.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 12 Amba Josep i vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčgi le ŇčgaŇčga ramae Isirel e gheghe na i kururu ghamwae i nja e thelauko vwatae weya ramae.
\v 13 Josep i vaŇčgurawa nariye Ip…®reim Isirel e moiyeko na Manase e uneko.
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge Isirel i mban vagaghala n…®man…®mae na n…®mae uneko i lirawe Ip…®reim e umbaliye, othembe raŇčama iye vir…® reghamba na n…®mae moiyeko i lirawe Manase e umbaliye, amalagh…®niye vir…®viva.
\p 
\v 15 Amba i giya Josep le ŇčgaŇčgako ghanjimwaewo iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúRumbuŇčgu Eibraham na ramaŇčgu Aisake
\q2 va th…® loŇčgaloŇčga Loi e ghamwae Ňčgoreiye le renuwaŇča,
\q1 na ghaghada mbaŇčake noroke vara Loi i viva e ghino
\q2 Ňčgoreiye sip gharanjimbunjimbu i vaŇčguŇčgiya le sip.
\q1 
\v 16 Nyaoko thovuye iya Loi va i variyeko,
\q2 i njaŇčanjaŇča e ghino na maava thar…® regha i vakowanaŇčgo.
\q1 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na i giya
\q2 gamagaike thiyake ghanji mwaewo.
\q1 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® renuwaŇčakikiŇčgo kaiwae,
\q2 Loi le vakathaŇčgiko kaiwanji.
\q1 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi ne i vakatha lenji ŇčgaŇčga lemoyo
\q2 na orumburumbunji lemoya e yambaneke lagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 17 MbaŇča Josep i thuwe ramae i lirawa n…®mae uneko Ip…®reim e umbaliye ghare i muruwana, iwaeŇčge i liya ramae n…®maeko Ip…®reim e umbaliye na i lirawe Manase e umbaliye.
\v 18 Josep i dage weya ramae iŇča, ‚ÄúMaa Ňčgoreiyana, bwebwe. Manase iye vir…®viva. U lira unen…®na e umbaliye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Ko iyemaeŇčge ramae i botewo na iŇča, ‚ÄúYa ghareghare, naruŇčgu, ya ghareghare budakaiya ya vakavakatha. Manase orumburumbuye tha muyaiko nevole th…® tabo vanautuma lagh…®ye regha. Ko iyemaeŇčge ghaghae nasiyeniyeko nevole i lagh…®ye kivwala amalagh…®niye, na orumburumbuye tha muyaiko nevole th…® tabo vanautuma lagh…®lagh…®yeŇčgi.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Kaero i giya ghanjimwaewo e mbaŇčako iyako, iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúMbaŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye ne th…® vegiya ghanjimwaewo ne th…®Ňča:
\q2 ‚ÄėLoi val…®kaiwae i vakathaŇčga Ňčgoreiya Ip…®reim na Manase.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\m E kamwath…®ko iyako i vakatha Ip…®reim i lagh…®ye kivwala Manase.
\p 
\v 21 Amba Isirel i dage weya Josep iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ma nasiye eŇčge kaero ya mare. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi ne weiye ghemi na ne i vaŇčgu njoghaŇčga e val…®vaŇčgako iya orumburumbumi va th…® rikowe.
\v 22 E ghen eŇčge, maa oghaghaŇčgina, kaero ya vatomwe thivathiva i thovuye moli, idae Sekem. Thivathivako iyako va ya wo weŇčgiya Amori ghar…®ghar…®niye elo gaith…® ghaghalith…® na mbwenara.‚ÄĚ
\c 49
\s1 Jeikob i giya le ŇčgaŇčga ghanjimwaewo
\p 
\v 1 Amba Jeikob i kula vathavathaŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga na i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúHu rogh…®liŇčaŇčgo na wo ya utu e ghemi nevole the bigithan i yomara e ghemi mbaŇča muyaiko.
\q1 
\v 2 Wo hu rakamena na hu vandeŇče.
\q2 Ghino ramami Isirel.
\q1 
\v 3 Rubin, ghen naruŇčgu vir…®viva,
\q2 ghen lo vur…®gheghe. Na naruŇčgwa ghen mbaŇča vamba tabwagha vara ghino.
\q2 Ghen u mevoro moli lo ŇčgaŇčgake wolagh…®ye e t…®nenji.
\q2 Ghen u vur…®gheghe lagh…®ye moli.
\q1 
\v 4 Ghen Ňčgorana ŇčgonuŇčgo vorughala. Ko iyemaeŇčge maane vole lolo lagh…®ye moliya ghen.
\q2 Kaiwae va u vanaŇča rama ghandiye na maa u yavwatatawana rama le ghamba ghena.
\q2 Iyake ghamba monjina lagh…®ye e ghino.
\q1 
\v 5 Simiyon na ghaghae Livai,
\q2 va th…® vakaiwoŇča lenji gaith…® ghaghalith…® na th…® gabowe.
\q1 
\v 6 Maane ya ru e lenji utu thuwoleko.
\q2 Maane ya metha weiŇčguyaŇčgi e lenji nivako.
\q1 Kaiwae lenji gatemuru e t…®ne th…® gaboŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®
\q2 na th…® vuŇčgi ok…®s ghegheŇčji vuvuye mwadiwo kaiwae.
\q1 
\v 7 Ya naŇčgo weya Loi na i gura lenji gaith…®ko,
\q2 kaiwae lenji gaith…®ko i maramararu moli.
\q1 Ne ya rake orumburumbunjiko
\q2 na veth…® yayaku Jeikob orumburumbuyeŇčgi e t…®nenji.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Juda, oghaghaeke nevole th…® taraweŇčge.
\q2 Ne u laweŇčgiya ghan th…®gh…®ya e numonji.
\q2 Oghaghana nevole th…® kururu e ghen.
\q1 
\v 9 Juda iye Ňčgoreiya laiyon nariye.
\q2 I un…®gha ghae na i njogha e ghambae.
\q1 I vamomoya gheghe na i ghena.
\q2 Maa lolo regha val…®kaiwae i vakaravoya riwae.
\q1 
\v 10 Juda ghauu gh…®mogh…®moruniye ne th…® tabo kiŇč.
\q2 Na orumburumbuye tha na tha nevole mbe th…® mbarombaro vara.
\q1 Vanautuma na vanautuma ne th…® mwaewowe
\q2 na th…® kururuwe na th…® ghambu.
\q1 
\v 11 I Ňčgara le doŇč…®ki e vaen
\q2 Na e yaŇčgaeko thovuye moli i Ňčgara doŇč…®kiko nariyewe.
\q1 Ne i thavwiya ghakwamakwama e waen sosoro.
\q1 
\v 12 Maramarae th…® bwedi kivwala waen,
\q2 ŇčiŇčiye th…® kaleva kivwala mil…®k.
\b
\q1 
\v 13 Sebulon ne i yakuŇča njigh…® ghadidiye
\q2 na ne i tabo vwaruvwaruru thovuye waŇčgawaŇčga kaiwanji.
\q2 Le ghamba mbaro ne ve wo Saidon.
\q1 
\v 14 Isaka iye i vur…®gheghe Ňčgoreiya doŇč…®ki.
\q2 MbaŇča riwae i bane ne i gheneth…®na ghaghadoweko.
\q1 
\v 15 MbaŇča i thuwe le ghamba towoko i thovuye,
\q2 na thelauko le thovuthovuye,
\q1 amba i vathawo wak…®yeko na i th…®na ghabigiko.
\q2 Th…® vavur…®ghegheŇča na i kaiwo Ňčgoreiya rakakaiwobwaga.
\q1 
\v 16 Den ne i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®
\q2 Ňčgoreiya iye wabwi regha Isirel e t…®ne.
\q1 
\v 17 Den iye Ňčgoreiye mwata mamate
\q2 e kamwath…® ghadidiye.
\q1 Iya i ghara hos…®ko gheghe,
\q2 na hos…®ko i wokiyatho rathathako e ghereiye.
\q1 
\v 18 O \nd Giya Loi\nd*, ya roroghagha len vamoru kaiwae.
\b
\q1 
\v 19 Ramban bwagabwaga ne th…® laweya Gad.
\q2 Ko iyemaeŇčge Gad ne i kivwalaŇčgi na i vambeleyathuŇčgi.
\b
\q1 
\v 20 Asa le thelau ne i rau na une i thovuye.
\q2 Ne i thovuye moli na val…®kaiwae i mban na kiŇč ghae.
\q1 
\v 21 Nap…®talai iye Ňčgoreiya diya wevo rakerakethu i ruku.
\q2 I ghamb…®Ňčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga thovuthovuye na man…®une.
\b
\q1 
\v 22 Josep iye Ňčgoreiya vaen i rau wagiyawe.
\q2 Iye Ňčgoreiya vaen i ndeghath…® e mbwarowou ghadidiye.
\q2 Iye Ňčgoreiya vaen yaŇčgayaŇčgae i mbuthu valaŇčaniye baba.
\q1 
\v 23 Ghanji th…®gh…®ya th…® gaith…®wana weinji lenji ghatemuru.
\q2 Th…® ighaighaŇča e mbwenara na kinkin.
\q1 
\v 24 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josep i du wagiyawe le kinko na mbwenarako.
\q2 N…®man…®maeko th…® vur…®gheghe.
\q1 Le vur…®ghegheko i wo weya Jeikob le Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye.
\q2 Le vur…®ghegheko i wo weya Sip gharanjimbunjimbu,
\q2 iye Isirel Var…®niye.
\q1 
\v 25 Rama le Loi i thalavuŇčge.
\q2 Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye i mwaewo e ghen.
\q1 I mwaewo e ghen e uye i njama e buruburu.
\q2 I mwaewo e ghen e mbwa i voroma e thelauke t…®ne.
\q2 I mwaewo e ghen e thetheghan lemoyo na e gamagai.
\q1 
\v 26 Mwaewo i mena weya rama i kivwala
\q2 mwaewo i mena e ouou teteuye.
\q2 Th…® kivwalaŇčgiya bigibigi thovuthovuye th…® mena e bobokulu th…® meghabana.
\q1 Val…®kaiwae mwaewoke thiyake th…® yayaku Josep e umbaliye.
\q2 Val…®kaiwae th…® yaku loloko iya i meghaghath…®
\q2 weŇčgiya oghaghaeko e ghamwae.
\q1 
\v 27 Benjamin Ňčgoreiya mbugha njamnjam tagaith…®.
\q2 MbaŇčambaŇča i ghana budakai me un…®gh…®.
\q2 Gougou i giya budakaiya me mban.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 28 Thiyake Isirel wabwiniyeŇčgi. Lenji ghanaghanagha theyaworo na theghewo. Iyake ghal…®Ňčae weŇčgi mbaŇča i giya le ŇčgaŇčga regha na regha ghanjigomwaewa Ňčgoreiya regha iya val…®kaiwae.
\s1 Jeikob le mare na ghabeku utuniye
\p 
\v 29 Amba Jeikob i dage weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ne ya garalawa na ya wa weŇčgiya lo bodaboda kaerova thiya mare, tembene vohu bekuŇčgova Ňčgora bwebwe na oramae th…® ghenawe. Ina e maŇčgavar…®, Eipron, iye rara Het le val…®vaŇčga,
\v 30 ina Makpela, Memri e boimaniyeko, Kenan e t…®ne. Eibraham va i vamodo maŇčgavar…®ko iyako weya Eipron na le ghabubu.
\v 31 Va th…® bekuŇčgiya Eibraham na levo Sera, Aisake na levo Rebeka, na vambe ya bekuva Leya iya e val…®vaŇčgako iyako.
\v 32 Thelauko iyako na maŇčgavar…®ko, va th…® vamodo weya rara Het. Ne vohu bekuŇčgowe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 33 MbaŇča Jeikob i giyavao le ŇčgaŇčgako ghanjimbaro, kaero i ghenava na e mbaŇčako iyako i liya le waŇčga.
\c 50
\p 
\v 1 MbaŇča Jeikob i mare Josep i ghenevala ramae e ghare vwatae na i randa na i vandamo ramae.
\v 2 I dage weŇčgiya kaka riwae gharavivatha th…® varuvwa kaka e bunama iya val…®kaiwae i vakatha na thava i vwatha mbaŇča molao.
\v 3 Iya vakathako iyako va i wo mbaŇčaevar…® (40), mbe ghambaŇča le molamolao vara. Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® nuwathar…® voreŇča mbaŇčaepir…® (70).
\p 
\v 4 MbaŇča nuwathar…®ko ghambaŇča iko, Josep i dage weŇčgiya Pero le rakakaiwo lagh…®lagh…®ye iŇča, ‚ÄúAgo lagh…®ye e ghemi, thoŇčgo hu warariŇča lo renuwaŇčake, vohu dage weya Pero kaiwaŇčgu huŇča,
\v 5 ‚ÄėAmba muyai Jeikob i mare, iŇča na Josep i dagerawe e marae na mbaŇča ramae ne i mare tembene i wova riwaeko na ve beku e maŇčgavar…® va i vivatharawe Kenan e t…®ne. Ya vata ago lagh…®ye e ghemi hu vatomweŇčgo ya wa va bekwa bwebwe amba ya njoghamava.‚Äô‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 6 Pero iŇča, ‚ÄúU wa na vo vakatha Ňčgoreiya va len dagerawenawe.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 7 Josep kaero i wa na ve bekwa ramae. Pero le rakakaiwoko lagh…®lagh…®yeko wolagh…®ye, giyagiya moli na randeviva vavanava Ijipt e t…®ne th…® ghambugha Josep.
\v 8 Josep le Ňčgoloko ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye na oghaghae vambe th…® rakawava weinji. Ramae ghayayaoko ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye vambe th…® rakawava. Va th…® raka iteteŇčgi mbe lenji ŇčgaŇčga eŇčge, lenji sip, burumwaka na gout na thetheghan vavanava Gosen e t…®ne.
\v 9 WaŇčga momod…® na hos…® vambe weinjiyaŇčgiva. Wabwi va lagh…®ye moliŇčgi.
\p 
\v 10 MbaŇča th…® raka vutha Ňčgora th…® ghatheghathe wit…®kowe idae Atad, Jor…®dan val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro, thiya randa na ghal…®Ňčanji lagh…®ye mbaŇča molao. Na gheko Josep mbowo i wova mbaŇča mbaŇčapir…® i nuwathar…® ramae Jeikob kaiwae.
\v 11 MbaŇča Kenan ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® thuwe Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niyeko th…® nuwathar…® Atad e t…®ne, kaero th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhar…®ghar…®ko thiyako mbema th…® nuwathar…® vara lagh…®ye moli.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae val…®vaŇčgako iyako th…® rena idae Eibol Misraim (gha rumwaru Ijipt ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® nuwathar…®).
\p 
\v 12 E kamwath…®ko iyako Jeikob le ŇčgaŇčgako th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya va le utuko weŇčgi.
\v 13 Kaero th…® wo ramanji riwaeko na th…® raka Kenan. Veth…® beku e maŇčgavar…® regha ina Makpela, Memri val…®vaŇčga i vorovoro. Thelauko iyako Eibraham va i vamodo weya Eipron, iye rara Het, na le ghabubu.
\v 14 MbaŇča Josep kaero i bekuvao ramae, kaero i njoghava Ijipt weiyaŇčgiya oghaghae na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye iyava weiyaŇčgiko ramae ghabekuko kaiwae.
\s1 Josep i vanuwov…®r…®Ňčgiya oghaghae mane i lith…®gha lenji vakatha vathar…®kowe
\p 
\v 15 Jeikob le mare e ghereiye, Josep oghaghae th…® vatada renuwaŇča regha th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúNe ŇčgoroŇčga ra vakatha na raŇča thoŇčgo Josep ne i botewoyathuinda na nuwaiya i lith…® weinda thar…®ko wolagh…®ye va ra vakathakowe?‚ÄĚ
\v 16 IwaeŇčge th…® variye utu weya Josep th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúRama va i lauturawa utuutuke thiyake weime amba muyai i mare:
\v 17 Va i lautu weime, iya kaiwae wo naŇčgo e ghen, thare val…®kaiwae u numoyatho lama thar…® na vuyowoko wolagh…®ye va wo vakatha e ghen. MbaŇčake u numotena rama le Loi le rakakaiwoŇčgi.‚ÄĚ MbaŇča lenji utuutuko iyako ve vutha weya Josep, i randa.
\p 
\v 18 Amba oghaghaeko th…® raka menawe na th…® kururu e ghamwae na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhime len rakakaiwobwaga.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 19 Ko iyemaeŇčge Josep i dage weŇčgi iŇča, ‚ÄúTha hu mararu. Val…®kaiwaŇčgu ne ya vakatha budakai iya, mbe Loi eŇčge val…®kaiwae i vakatha.
\v 20 Lemi renuwaŇča va huŇča hu vakatha vathar…® e ghino. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi i v…®v…® e thovuye, na i vamboromboro budakaiya noroke i yomara. I vamoruŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo.
\v 21 Iya kaiwae tha weiye lemi gharelagh…®lagh…®. Ghino ne ya njimbukikiŇčga na lemi ŇčgaŇčgana tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.‚ÄĚ Kaero i vagharematuwoŇčgi na e ghal…®Ňčae udauda i utu weŇčgi.
\s1 Josep le mare
\p 
\v 22 Josep va le yakuyaku Ijipt e t…®ne weiyaŇčgiya ramae ghayayaoko ghar…®ghar…®niye mbaŇča molao. Ghatheghathegha kaero i wo hothaŇčar…® na hoyaworo (110) amba i mare.
\v 23 Josep va i thuweŇčgiya Ip…®reim le ŇčgaŇčga na lenji ŇčgaŇčgava. Na tembe i thuweŇčgiva Maki, Manase nariye, le ŇčgaŇčga th…® tabo amalagh…®niye le bodaboda gamagainiye.
\p 
\v 24 Josep i dage weŇčgiya oghaghaeko iŇča, ‚ÄúWo mbaŇča mare maiya vara. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi mbene i njimbukikiŇčga vara. Amalagh…®niye ne i vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčga e val…®vaŇčgake iyake na hu raka njogha e val…®vaŇčga va i dagerawe weŇčgiya Eibraham, Aisake na Jeikob.‚ÄĚ
\v 25 Amba Josep i vakathaŇčgiya oghaghae, Isirel le ŇčgaŇčga, na th…® tholo. IŇča, ‚ÄúHu dagerawe e ghino, mbaŇča Loi ne i vaŇčguraŇčgiyaŇčga na hu raka njogha e val…®vaŇčgako iyako, ne hu bigiya wak…®wak…®niŇčguke.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 26 Josep i mare Ijipt e t…®ne na ghatheghathegha hothaŇčar…® na hoyaworo (110). Kaka riwae gharavivatha th…® vivatha riwae beku kaiwae na th…® woruwo kakako riwae e bogis t…®ne gheko. 
